\id 1SA - Mbula 
\h 1 Samuyila 
\toc3 1Sam 
\toc2 1 Samu 
\toc1 1 Samuyila 
\mt1 SAMUYILA MƏDƏMBE 
\imt1 MƏNCAU 
\im Malǝmce mǝnia a tunǝi ama \k Samuyila mǝdǝmbe\k* ka bangcau mala nggaɗi a Isǝrayila twal a bàkú mala akasǝla aban ká mala amurǝma. Nggaɗi mǝnia aɓa do-yilǝmu mala nzali Isǝrayila ka, kàrìkì-rǝì aban aburana tàrú: Samuyila, masǝlǝata ɓwa atà akaɓa kasǝla; Sawul, murǝm mǝdǝmbe mala Isǝrayila; andǝ Dauda, mǝnana agya male andǝ agir mǝnana kum ɓamurì aɓalǝia sǝ yi eauwe a buno-murǝm ngga, à taɓǝli aɓalǝarǝia andǝ acau mala adoyilǝmu mala Samuyila andǝ Sawul. 
\ip Múrcau mala malǝmce mǝnia, kǝla mala acili acau-ɓaraɓara mǝnana à gilǝia aɓa Kùrcau Mǝ'e ka, nda mǝnana ama domǝsǝcau aban Ɓakuli ka kǝ yinǝ lidǝmba, sǝ mgbikiru ka kǝ yinǝ gir'murmwana. Mǝnia ka à bangŋi bwāng aɓa cau mala Yahweh aban Eli pǝris mǝnana ama: <<Mǝ nǝ gusǝlǝ aɓwana mǝnana à gusǝlǝam ngga, sǝ aɓwana mǝnana à ɓǝsǝkiam ngga, mǝ nǝ pàkcea-ɓa.>> (\xt 1Sam 2:30.)\xt* 
\ip Aɓa mǝnia yì malǝmce ka, à lǝmdǝa sǝm anzongcau mala gingnǝ do ma'sǝm ani: (1) Ɓakuli ka pà nǝ̀ vwakibuì arǝ aɓwana male ɗàng; ko ɓǝ̀ agir swárkiô, kǝla mǝnana pǎ a nza mala Eli andǝ amuna-burana male ka, Ɓakuli kǝ yinǝ tsǝkɓalǝu, kǝla mǝnana pè nǝ ɓǝl Samuyila ka. (2) Ɓakuli ka à pà nǝ̀ gandǝ tsǝie púp, ko à nǝ̀ swárí aɓa kutan ɓǝ̀ kpata agir mǝnana sǝm earkiyice ka ɗàng, sǝama yì ka nǝ̀ bwali aɓwana mǝnana à gūlì arǝì sǝ à kǝ alta pàk nê male ka. (3) Nggearǝ peri ma'sǝm aban Ɓakuli ka pànǝ ɓoaro ɗàng ɓǝ̀ sǝm kpapì andǝ okiru raka. (4) Lǝmdǝa mala ɓwa a nza ka, kǝgìr na aban Ɓakuli ɗang; gìr mǝnana Ɓakuli earkiyice ka nda ɓabum mǝnana dàrrì arǝ túró male ka. (5) Aɓwana mǝnana à ɗeki mɓali ɓǝ̀ gingnǝ do malea ka, à nǝ̀ pakkî ɓamúrià mǝɓane mana kútì mǝɓane mǝnana à nǝ̀ pàkkî ɓià ɓwapǝndǝa ka. 
\iot Agir mǝnana a ɓalǝi ka 
\io1 Lo mala Samuyila kǝla kasǝla mala Isǝrayila \ior 1:1--3:1-21\ior* 
\io1 Amǝ'Filisti bwal Akwati Kùrcau sǝ à nyesǝì \ior 4:1--6:20\ior* 
\io1 Samuyila yálmúr Isǝrayila sǝ à ɗice murǝm \ior 7:1--8:22\ior* 3 
\io1 Sawul, murǝm mǝdǝmbe mala Isǝrayila \ior 9:1--11:15\ior* 
\io1 A'lwa mala Sawul andǝ mgbikiru male \ior 13:1--15:35\ior* 
\io1 Lo mala Dauda kǝla murǝm Isǝrayila \ior 16:1--17:58\ior* 
\io1 Sawul pàk mɓali sǝ alte nǝ̀ wal-lú Dauda \ior 18:1--24:22\ior* 
\io1 Lú mala Sawul andǝ amuni \ior 31:1-13\ior* 
\c 1  
\s1 Elkana andǝ amǝ'ɓala male a Shilo 
\p  
\v 1 Ɓè ɓwabura nakam lullǝì ama Elkana. Tárrí nda Jeroham, kè-mǝɓwabure nda Elihu, sǝ tár-kè-mǝ-ɓwabure ka nda Tohu, a nggurkwar mala Zuf, ɓwa'Efǝrat. Yì ka do a Rama, ɓè nggea-là aɓa nzali múr ankono mala Ifǝrem.  
\v 2 Ndanǝ amamǝna ɓari, Hana andǝ Penina. Penina ka ndanǝ amuna, sǝ Hana ka pànǝ kǝ muna ɗang. 
\p  
\v 3 Ɓwabura mǝnia ka kǝ pur a nggea-là male koya pǝlǝa ace ká peri andǝ pà gir'nkila aban Yahweh, Mǝtala Abangŋo, a Shilo. Hofni andǝ Finehas, amuna-burana ɓari mala Eli ka, à nda ka apǝris mala Yahweh kano.  
\v 4 Koya pwari sǝ Elkana nǝ̀ pà gir'nkila ka, kǝ pê māmí Penina andǝ koyan atà amuni amuna-burana andǝ amuna-mamǝna kāmbe mala nyama.  
\v 5 Sǝ Hana ka kǝ pe wi akāmbe ɓari,\f + \fr 1:5 \fq akāmbe ɓari \ft Aɓea malǝmce gilǝ ama kāmbe mwashat, sǝ aɓea ka ama kāmbe mǝɓoarne mwashat.\f* acemǝnana kǝ earce Hana, kat andǝ amani ama Yahweh pè wi ɓǝlmuna raka.  
\v 6 Pàk ka ɓimama kǝ altacau arǝì, nǝ̀ lulbumi acemǝnana Yahweh pè wi ɓǝlmuna raka.  
\v 7 Anggo sǝ gìrnî lidǝmba pǝlǝa anzǝm pǝlǝa. Ɓǝ̀ kusǝ shen sǝ wari a ɓala mala Yahweh ka, anggo gbal sǝ ɓimama nǝ̀ nggǝ lulbumi. Acemani ka, Hana nǝ̀ nggǝ ɓua sǝ pà nǝ̀ li girlina ɗang.  
\v 8 Sǝ Elkana burí ka banggi wi ama, <<Hana, palang sǝ a kǝ ɓua? Sǝ palang sǝ a kǝ li girlina ɗang? Sǝ palang sǝ a pàk bumkiɗikea? Ən kútì amuna-burana lum a bano re?>> 
\p  
\v 9-10 A ɓè pwari anzǝm mana à malna li girlina sǝ à nuna gìr a Shilo ka, Hana lo. Nda aɓa bumpina mǝlime, sǝ pakhiwi aban Yahweh nǝ sukkimǝrǝm kǝ̀rkǝ́r. Aɓa mǝno anggo ka, Eli pǝris ka, nda aban do a buno male a nkanggari kpangbang-kunkurǝm mala ndà mala Yahweh.  
\v 11 Pǝlǝa Hana pàcau nǝ-shambum ama, <<We Yahweh mana a Karban Kat nǝ Gulo ka,\f + \fr 1:11 \fq Yahweh mana a Karban Kat nǝ Gulo ka \ft ko <<Yahweh mǝ'sàrǝ̀ amǝ'lwa mala kuli>>\f* ɓǝ̀ aɓa mǝsǝcau awu nǝ sǝn tanni mem, mim guro mò, sǝ awu nǝ ɗenyinǝ mim, ɓalǝo pà nǝ̀ lorǝǎm, mim guro mò ɗàng, sǝ awu nǝ pàm, mim guro mò, muna-ɓwabura ka, mǝ nǝ nyesǝi mǝ nǝ po wi we Yahweh, aɓalǝ anonggio mala do-yilǝmu male kat, sǝ kǝ nkembu pa nǝ̀ je múrí ɗàng.>> 
\p  
\v 12 Lang lidǝmba nǝ pakhiwi aɓadǝm Yahweh ka, Eli soa mǝsǝi kǝ sǝn kúni.  
\v 13 Hana na aban nacau a ɓabumi; kǝ amburkuni na à kǝ dǝurǝ ka, sǝ gì ka à oè ɗàng. Acemani ka, Eli twali ama mba-walì nǝ walo.  
\v 14 Sǝ Eli banggi wi ama, <<Nǝ̀ sau lang sǝ awu nǝ ueo aɓa walo-mba? Nying nu mùr-anap mò.>> 
\p  
\v 15 Sǝ Hana ka eari wi ama, <<Awo, ɓwamǝgule mem, Mǝ nda ɓwama mǝnana yilǝmem na aɓa zunggǝli ka. Ən nu kǝ mùr-anap ko mba ɗàng. Mǝ nda rǝ ú bumam a ɓadǝm Yahweh.  
\v 16 Kǝa twalam, mim guro mò kǝla ɓwama mǝɓane ɗàng; ǝn mal pwari yi pur ado mǝ ndaban lǝmdǝ ɓuanǝbum andǝ bumkiɗikea mǝgule mem aɓa hiwi.>> 
\p  
\v 17 Pǝlǝa Eli pà eare ama, <<Kyane aɓa rǝpwala, sǝ ɓǝ̀ Ɓakuli mala Isǝrayila po zǝmba mô mǝnana a alte a baní ka.>> 
\p  
\v 18 Pǝlǝa Hana bang ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ guro mò kum earmúrú a mǝsǝo.>> Pǝlǝa ɓwame oa o male sǝ kya lili sǝ ɓamǝsǝi panzǝa. 
\p  
\v 19 Pǝlǝa à lo nǝ dǝmbari ɗiɗyal sǝ à peri aɓadǝm Yahweh; sǝ à nyar a ɓala malea a Rama. Elkana yi súrǝ̀ māmí Hana, sǝ Yahweh ɗenyinǝ Hana.  
\v 20 Lang anonggio yi karna ka, muna kpa a bum Hana sǝ ɓǝl muna-ɓwabura, sǝ tsǝki wi lullǝu ama Samuyila, acemǝnana bang ama, <<Ən zǝmbì aban Yahweh.>> 
\s1 Hana pà Samuyila aban Ɓakuli 
\p  
\v 21 Lang ɓè bàkú kàrna ka, ɓwabura man, yì Elkana ka wari andǝ ɓala male kat ace pà gìr'nkila mala koya pǝlǝa, sǝ ace lùmsǝ pàcau nǝ-shambum male aban Yahweh.  
\v 22 Sǝama Hana ka wari ɗang. Banggi burí ama, <<Anzǝm mǝnana ǝn kasǝna muna a kiura ka, sǝ mǝ nǝ kánǝi, mǝ nǝ lǝmdǝí aɓadǝm Yahweh, sǝ yì ka nǝ̀ ue kano ba do-yilǝmu male kat.>>\f + \fr 1:22 \fq nǝ̀ ue kano ba do-yilǝmu male kat. \ft Amalǝmce-nggú mala amǝ Ibǝru tsǝì ama: \fqa Ən panì ɓǝ̀ duk ɓwa Nazir aɓalǝ anonggio mala do-yilǝmu male kat. \f* 
\p  
\v 23 Burí Elkana banggi wi ama, <<Pàk gìr mǝnana ɓoaro kutibani a bano ka; kúndǝô sheɓǝ̀ a kasǝni a kiura ka; ɓǝ̀ Yahweh tsǝk cau male ɓǝ̀ yi lumsǝo.>> Nda ɓwame ueo sǝ lǝsǝ muni she lang kasǝni a kiura ka. 
\p  
\v 24 Sǝ lang kasǝni a kiura ka, twali atè, atārǝia andǝ muna-jamnda mǝnana mbule tàrú ka, andǝ tyang lum mala muku alkama, andǝ sambǝram mana lùmsǝì nǝ mùr-anap ka. Sǝ twal Samuyila aɓa kyauwe male yinǝi a ɓala mala Yahweh a Shilo.  
\v 25 Pǝlǝa à pwanmyal muna-jamndè, sǝ à yinǝ mune aban Eli.  
\v 26 Pǝlǝa Hana bang ama, <<Ida, ɓwamǝgule mem, kǝla mǝnana a ndakam nǝyilǝmu ka, mǝ nda ɓwama mǝnana ǝn cam kani aɓadǝmbo, aban pakhiwi aban Yahweh ka.  
\v 27 Ən pakhiwi ace muna mǝnia ka, sǝ Yahweh panam zǝmba mem mǝnana ǝn warinǝi a baní ka.  
\v 28 Acemani ka, ǝn panì Yahweh. Aɓa do-yilǝmu male kat ka, ǝn nyingŋǝ́nì Yahweh.>> 
\p Pǝlǝa à peri aban Yahweh a banì. 
\c 2  
\s1 Hiwi ɓwangsǝban mala Hana 
\m  
\v 1 Sǝ Hana pakhiwi ama: 
\q1 Ɓabumam pàk banɓoarnado kǝ̀rkǝ́r aban Yahweh! 
\q2 Njawe\f + \fr 2:1 \fq Njawe \ft ko <<Rǝcandǝa>>\f* mem kumǝna loasǝ́bân atàcau mala Yahweh! 
\q1 Kunam nǝ̀ nacau nǝ mǝsǝkàng-kàngŋa arǝ aɓiam-mǝbura, 
\q2 acemǝnana ǝn nggǝ pàk-banɓoarnado aɓa amsǝban mô. 
\q1  
\v 2 Kǝɓwa pà kàm mǝfele kǝla Yahweh ɗàng! 
\q1 Kǝɓè pà kàm ɗàng she we! 
\q2 Sǝ kǝ Tali pa kàm kǝla Ɓakuli ma'sǝm ɗàng. 
\q1  
\v 3 Kǝa wu hatǝki nacau twàlɓamúrû kǝ̀rkǝ́r ɗàng, 
\q2 sǝ kǝa ɗeki acau gusǝlǝ-múrû pur a kuno ɗàng! 
\q1 Acemǝnana Yahweh ka Ɓakuli mala sǝlǝe na, 
\q1 sǝ nǝbani sǝ à kǝ karǝki atúró mala aɓwana. 
\q1  
\v 4 À ɓungina anta mala akanggǝrang-ɓwa, 
\q2 sǝ amǝ'tanggigya ka à marǝia nǝ rǝcandǝa. 
\q1  
\v 5 Aɓwana mǝnana à ɗǝm ɗiɗyal ka, 
\q2 à mak ɓamuria ace nɗǝmo bǝtikulyak, 
\q1 sǝ aɓwana mana nzala walia ka, 
\q2 à ɗwanyi ɗǝm ɗàng. 
\q1 Nggearǝ nkombi ka, ɓǝlna amuna tongno-nong-ɓari, 
\q2 sǝ ɓwama mǝnana ndanǝ amuna pas ka, 
\q2 dumǝna-pwari'pwari.\f + \fr 2:5 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Isha 54:1\ft .\f* 
\q1  
\v 6 Yahweh kǝ wal-lú sǝ kǝ pa yilǝmu; 
\q2 kǝ sulǝ ɓwa a Shewol\f + \fr 2:6 \fq Shewol \ft ko <<ɓembe, ko ban mala alú>>\f* sǝ kǝ loasǝ ɓwa. 
\q1  
\v 7 Yahweh kǝ tsǝk ɓwa a tǝ̀r, sǝ kǝ tsǝk ɓwa ɓǝ̀ duk mǝkume; 
\q2 kǝ kyauwiki ɓwa, sǝ kǝ gusǝlǝ ɓwa. 
\q1  
\v 8 Kǝ loasǝ amǝ'tǝ̀r ɓǝà purî ɓá tú, 
\q2 sǝ amǝtapwasǝa ka kǝ pusǝia aɓa gìgí, 
\q2 ace tsǝia ɓǝà do andǝ amǝgulo, 
\q2 sǝ ɓǝà kum liɓala mala buno ɓoarɓwa. 
\q1 Akusǝɓa mala ɓanza ka à mala Yahweh na; 
\q2 amúria sǝ tamsǝ ɓanza. 
\q1  
\v 9 Kǝ yál kusǝ amǝ'do-mǝsǝcau male, 
\q2 sǝ amǝ'ɓealɓikea ka nǝ̀ tsǝa kunia nǝ̀ pwal aɓa pǝndǝa. 
\q1 Pà nǝ rǝcandǝa sǝ ɓwa nǝ̀ duk-gbani ɗang. 
\q1  
\v 10 Amǝ'ɓinǝcau arǝ Yahweh ka, à nǝ̀ arkia gucik-gucik; 
\q2 nǝ̀ ìm arǝia a kuli. 
\q1 Yahweh nǝ̀ ɓashì ɓanza kat; 
\q2 nǝ̀ pè murǝm male rǝcandǝa; 
\q1 nǝ̀ loasǝ bù ɓwa male mǝnana tàrì ka. 
\m  
\v 11 Pǝlǝa Elkana nyar a là a Rama. Sǝ muna ka ueo ace pàkkî Yahweh túró aɓadǝm Eli pǝris. 
\s1 Cauɓikea mala amuna-burana mala Eli 
\p  
\v 12 Amuna-burana mala Eli ka, aɓwana mǝɓane na. À súrǝ̀ Yahweh ɗàng  
\v 13 sǝ à tsǝkiria arǝ anggurcau amur agir mǝnana ɓoaro apǝris nǝ̀ ɗice aban aɓwana ka ɗàng. A kún mani ka, lang ɓwa na aban pà gir'nkila ka, mǝtúró-ɓala mala pǝris nǝ̀ yiu nǝ shokali-soa-nyama. Lang nyama narǝ ɓǝla a bǝsa ka,  
\v 14 nǝ̀ yia zuɓi shokali-soa-nyama aɓa nkenye, ko muna-nkwaring, ko kwangiri, ko nggea-nkwaring. Gìr mǝnana kat shokali-soa-nyama loasǝi ka, pǝris nǝ̀ twali ace ɓamurì. Mǝnia ka nda gìr mǝnana à kǝ pakki amǝ'Isǝrayila mǝnana kat à yiua pà gìr'nkila a Shilo ka.  
\v 15 Amur mǝno ka, \f + \fr 2:15 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Pǝris 3:5,16; 7:23,25,31\f*kaniama à nǝ̀ pisǝ mùrú-nyama ka, mǝtúró-ɓala mala pǝris nǝ̀ yiu sǝ nǝ̀ banggi ɓwa mǝnana pàkiyi gir'nkila ka ama, <<Pà nyama mǝnana à nǝ̀ twani ace pǝris ka, acemǝnana pà nǝ̀ ak nyama mǝnana à lambǝni ka ɗàng she mǝpwale.>> 
\p  
\v 16 Sǝ ɓǝ̀ ɓwê banggi wi ama, <<Kúndǝô ɓǝà pisǝ mùruí peatu, sǝ awu nǝ̀ twal gìr mǝnana a earce ka,>> nǝ̀ bang ama, <<Awo, dumǝna púp awu nǝ pà adyan! Ɓǝ̀ a pa raka, mǝ nǝ twali nǝ rǝcandǝa.>> 
\p  
\v 17 Mǝnia yì cauɓikea mala alaggana mǝnia ka gul kǝ̀rkǝ́r a mǝsǝ Yahweh, acemǝnana pàgir aban Yahweh ka à pàkce-ɓà. 
\s1 Samuyila a Shilo 
\p  
\v 18 A bàkú mǝno ka Samuyila yì muna ka lidǝmba nǝ̀ pàkki Yahweh túró, kǝ oasǝ efot mala nggubyau linǝn.\f + \fr 2:18 \fq efot mala nggubyau linǝn \ft ko <<adaura pǝris>>\f* 
\v 19 Koya pǝlǝa ka nggè nǝ̀ pàkki wi muna daura-múrɓì sǝ nǝ̀ yinǝi wi nǝi lang yiu atà burí ace pà gir'nkila mala koya pǝlǝa ka.  
\v 20 Pǝlǝa Eli nǝ̀ tsǝki Elkana andǝ māmí bù sǝ nǝ̀ bang ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh loasǝò amuna nǝ bù ɓwama man a kúnì mǝnana zǝmba ace aban Yahweh ka.>> Anzǝm mǝno ka sǝ à nǝ̀ o a là. 
\p  
\v 21 Mǝsǝcau Yahweh ɓwamur Hana, sǝ kum ɓǝlmuna sǝ ɓǝl amuna-burana tàrú andǝ amuna-mamǝna ɓari. Sǝ muna yì Samuyila ka gulo a ɓadǝm Yahweh. 
\s1 Eli nunkir amuna-burana male 
\p  
\v 22 A bàkú mǝno ka Eli ena kutsuk, sǝ camarǝ ok cau mala gìr mǝnana kat amuna-burana male kǝ pakki Isǝrayila kat, andǝ mǝnana ama à kǝ nongginǝ amamǝna mana à kǝ yiu a pàktúró a kún Tara ban-kpapí ka.  
\v 23 Sǝ banggi amuna-burana male ama, <<Palang sǝ wu kǝ pakki agir kǝla amǝnia ka? Ən nggǝ oe a kún aɓwana mǝnia kat acau mala agir mǝɓike mǝnana wu kǝ pea ka.  
\v 24 Awo, amunem; cau mǝnana ǝn nggǝ oè kǝ mesǝe aɓalǝ aɓwana mala Yahweh ka, mǝɓoarne na ɗang.  
\v 25 Ɓǝ̀ ɓwa pàkkî ɓì cauɓikea ka, Ɓakuli nǝ̀ kùtí anrea ace gilǝki càu, sǝama ɓǝ̀ ɓwa pàkkî Yahweh cauɓikea ka, yana ɓwê nǝ̀ pwanzali aceì?>> Sǝ yià ka, à ginǝ kwakikiria arǝ cau mala tárria, acemǝnana kàne mala Yahweh na nǝ̀ wal-luia. 
\p  
\v 26 Aɓa mǝno anggo ka, muna yì Samuyila ka lidǝmba nǝ gulo aɓa nggūrǝu, sǝ aɓa earmúrú aban Yahweh andǝ aɓwana. 
\p  
\v 27 Pǝlǝa ɓè ɓwa mala Ɓakuli yiu aban Eli sǝ banggi wi ama, <<Mǝnia ka nda cau mala Yahweh, <Ən lǝmdǝ ɓamúràm bwāng aban ɓala mala keò, lang à nda a Masar aɓata Firona ka re?  
\v 28 Ən tárì aɓalǝ atau mala Isǝrayila kat ɓǝ̀ duk pǝris mem, ace eauwe amur gyangŋan mem, ace paɓoro mala pisǝ muku-gìr loasǝ yele mǝ'rǝmɓoarne, sǝ ɓǝ̀ oasǝ efot aɓadǝmbam ngga re? Ən pê ɓala mala keò apagir kat mala bǝsa, mǝnana amǝ Isǝrayila kǝ yinǝia abanam ngga.  
\v 29 Sǝ palang sǝ wun kat wu ɓǝsǝkice agir'nkila mem andǝ apagir mem mǝnana ǝn tsǝk nzongcau nǝma ɓǝà yinǝia a mǝnia yì bando mem ngga? A gusǝlǝce amunio amuram nǝ earia wia ɓǝà twal amǝɓoarne kat aɓalǝ akoya pàgir mǝnana aɓwana mem amǝ Isǝrayila yinǝia ka, ace lǝsǝ ɓamuria ɓǝà nyange?> 
\p  
\v 30 <<Acemani ka, Yahweh, Ɓakuli mala Isǝrayila kǝ bang ama: <Ən pacau nǝma ɓala mò andǝ nggurkwar mò ɓǝà lidǝmba nǝ kutio andǝ puro aɓadǝmbam tàtǝ́k.> Sǝama, adyan ngga Yahweh kǝ na ama: <Pà mǝ nǝ ɗeki ɓǝ̀ pàk anggo ɗǝm ɗàng. A kún mani ka, mǝ nǝ gusǝlǝ aɓwana mǝnana à gusǝlǝam ngga, sǝ aɓwana mǝnana à ɓǝsǝkiam ngga, mǝ nǝ pàkcea-ɓa.  
\v 31 Kwakikiro, anonggio na kǝ yiu mǝnana aɓalǝia ka, mǝ nǝ wal-lú koya lo-ɓwa muna-ɓwabura a ɓala mò andǝ nggurkwar mò, mǝnana nǝ̀ tsǝa à pà nǝ̀ kum jamgula ɗǝm a ɓala mò raka.  
\v 32 Sǝ mǝsǝo nǝ̀ sǝn tanni mǝkwanbanì mala ɓala peri mem. Mǝɓoarne nǝ̀ yiu amur Isǝrayila, sǝ a ɓala mò ka, kǝ ɓwa pà nǝ̀ bik apǝlǝa mala ě ɗǝm ɗàng, arǝ anza kat.  
\v 33 Ɓwa mwashat atà amǝkeo mǝnana mǝ nǝ ɗeki ɓǝ̀ lidǝmba nǝ túró pǝris amur gyangŋan mem ngga, nǝ̀ duk nte sǝ do male nǝ̀ pà aɓa tímúrû. Amǝkeo kat nǝ̀ wǔ a lo-ɓwa malea.  
\v 34 Sǝ mǝnia yì gìr mǝnana nǝ̀ kum amuna-burana mô ɓari, yia Hofni andǝ Finehas ka, nǝ̀ dupô gìr'lǝmdǝa: yià kǝm à nǝ̀ wǔ aɓa pwari mǝ'mwashati. 
\p  
\v 35 << <Sǝ mǝ nǝ loasǝì ɓamúràm pǝris mǝ'mǝsǝcaunì, mǝnana nǝ̀ pàk gìr kǝla mana nda a bumam andǝ ɗenyicau mem ngga. Mǝ nǝ tamsǝ ɓala-pǝris male kàngkàng,\f + \fr 2:35 \fq tamsǝ ɓala-pǝris male kàngkàng \ft ko <<mǝ nǝ eari wi ɓǝ̀ kum amuna andǝ amǝ'kau mǝnana à nǝ̀ duk apǝris ka>>\f* sǝ nǝ̀ pàk túró-pǝris aɓadǝm ɓwa mem mana ǝn tárì ka tàtǝ́k.\f + \fr 2:35 \fq ɓwa mem mana ǝn tárì ka tàtǝ́k; \ft ɓalli aɓa: \xt 2Sam 22:51; Ang 18:50; 89:20\ft .\f* 
\v 36 Sǝ ɓwa mǝnana kat ueo nǝyilǝmu a nggurkwar mò ka, nǝ̀ ká aban pǝris mǝno ka ace zǝmbi wi gbatali bolo-azǝrfa andǝ ɗurǝo nɗǝmo, sǝ nǝ̀ bang ama: Ida, twalam a ɓè bantúró pǝris ace mǝnana mǝ kum girlina mana mǝ nǝ lì ka.> >> 
\c 3  
\s1 Yahweh tunǝ Samuyila 
\p  
\v 1 Adyan ngga muna, yì Samuyila ka, ndarǝ pakkì Yahweh túró a ɓadǝm Eli. \f + \fr 3:1 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Ang 74:9; Amo 8:11\ft .\f*Arǝ abákú mǝno ka, Yahweh kǝ nacau nǝ aɓwana tùtù ɗang; sǝ sǝna ka làkkì ɗàng. 
\p  
\v 2 A ɓè dù, Eli mǝnana amǝsǝì kǝ sǝnban ɗǝm pepè raka, ndaban nongŋo a ban mǝnana nonggiyi kam ngga,  
\v 3 sǝ pitǝla mala Ɓakuli ka,\f + \fr 3:3 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Pur 27:21\ft .\f* à malaká limi ɗàng. Sǝ Samuyila ka, ndaban nongŋo a ndà mala Yahweh, a ban mǝnana Akwati mala Ɓakuli pàk kàm ngga. 
\p  
\v 4 Pǝlǝa Yahweh tunǝ Samuyila, sǝ Samuyila ear ama, <<Mǝ ndya ka!>> 
\p  
\v 5 Pǝlǝa ɓangŋa wari aban Eli sǝ ne wi ama, <<Mǝ ndya ka, a tunǝam.>> 
\p Sǝ Eli banggi wi ama, <<Ən tunǝo ɗàng. Nyare kya nongnǝ-nongŋo.>> Nda nyare nongnǝ-nongŋo ka. 
\p  
\v 6 Yahweh nyare tunǝban ama, <<Samuyila!>> Sǝ Samuyila lo wari aban Eli sǝ ne wi ama, <<Mǝ ndya ka, a tunǝam.>> 
\p Sǝ Eli banggi wi ama, <<Ən tunǝo ɗàng, munem; nyare kya nongnǝ-nongŋo.>> 
\p  
\v 7 Samuyila ka sǝlǝ ama Yahweh na kǝ tunǝi ka ɗàng, acemǝnana cau mala Yahweh malaká yiu a baní akǝ fara anggo ɗàng. 
\p  
\v 8 Pǝlǝa Yahweh tunǝ Samuyila ɗǝm tàruia tunǝban. Samuyila lo wari aban Eli sǝ ne wi ama, <<Mǝ ndya ka, a tunǝam!>> 
\p Nda Eli yi sǝlǝa ama Yahweh na kǝ tunǝ mune ka.  
\v 9 Acemani ka, Eli banggi Samuyila ama, <<Nyare kya nongnǝ-nongŋo, sǝ ɓǝ̀ tunǝno ɗǝm ngga, ne wi ama, <Nacau, Yahweh, guro mò na kǝ ueo ka.> >> Nda Samuyila nyare wario kya nongnǝ-nongŋo a ban nongŋo male ka. 
\p  
\v 10 Sǝ Yahweh yiu yi came, sǝ tunǝban kǝla mana a dǝmbe ka, ama, <<Samuyila! Samuyila!>> 
\p Samuyila pǝlǝa ear ama, <<Nacau, guro mò na kǝ ueo ka!>> 
\p  
\v 11 Pǝlǝa Yahweh banggi Samuyila ama, <<Sǝni, Mǝ ndo mǝ nǝ pàk ɓegìr a Isǝrayila; ɓwa mana kat okce ka, nǝ̀ gǝggǝli.  
\v 12 A pwari mǝno ka, mǝ nǝ̀ lùmsǝ cau mǝnana ǝn ne amúr Eli andǝ ɓala male ka, twal a tite aban ká masǝlǝate.  
\v 13 Ən bangŋǝni wi nǝma mǝ ndo mǝ nǝ ɓashì ɓala male tàtǝ́k, ace cauɓikea mǝnana sǝlǝce ka, acemǝnana amuni \f + \fr 3:13 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Mat 12:31-32; Luk 12:10\ft .\f*bang caukyauwikiban amur Ɓakuli, sǝ gimbia ɗàng.  
\v 14 Acemani ka, ǝn kángìr aban ɓala mala Eli ama, <Cauɓikea mala ɓala mala Eli ka, à pa nǝ̀ shawuɗi nǝ gìr'nkila ko pàɓoro ɗàng tàtǝ́k.> >> 
\p  
\v 15 Nda Samuyila nongŋo bà dǝmbari. Pǝlǝa mǝngi akúnda mala ɓala mala Yahweh. Sǝ Samuyila ka ɓangciu pàkki wi arǝ ne Eli mǝno yì sǝna ka.  
\v 16 Sǝ Eli tunǝ Samuyila ama, <<Samuyila, munem!>> 
\p Sǝ Samuyila eari wi ama, <<Mǝ ndya ka.>> 
\p  
\v 17 Eli ɗì ama, <<Mana Yahweh banggo? Ida, kǝa sǝmbǝ́rǝàmì ɗàng. Ɓakuli nǝ̀ ɓashio kǝ̀rkǝ́r yi mǝnana ɓǝ̀ a sǝmbǝ́rǝàm kǝcau mana banggo ka!>>  
\v 18 Nda Samuyila ne wi cê kat ka. Sǝmbǝrǝi wi kǝ cau ɗàng. Eli pǝlǝa bang ama, <<Yì nda Yahweh. Ɓǝ̀ pàk gìr mǝnana sǝni nda mǝɓoarne a mǝsǝì ka.>> 
\p  
\v 19 Samuyila lidǝmba nǝ̀ gulo, sǝ Yahweh na atè. Kǝ cau male kpa a nzali ɗàng.  
\v 20 Amǝ Isǝrayila puppup, twal a Dan aban ká Biyasheba yi sǝlǝa ama, Samuyila ka, mǝɓangnǝa mala Yahweh na nǝ mǝsǝcau.  
\v 21 Yahweh lidǝmba nǝ pusǝrǝi a Shilo; lǝmdǝrǝì a Shilo aban Samuyila nǝ cau male. 
\c 4  
\s1 Amǝ'Filisti ak Akwati Kùrcau 
\p  
\v 1 Sǝ cau mala [Yahweh nǝ kún] Samuyila yiu aban amǝ Isǝrayila kat. A bàkú mǝno ka, amǝ'Isǝrayila wari a munǝo arǝ amǝ'Filisti. À kya tsǝk kàttì malea a Ebeneza, sǝ amǝ'Filisti tsǝk kàttì malea a Afek.  
\v 2 Amǝ'Filisti tsaɗi a kúnarǝia a nzong ban-je munǝo ace ká arǝ Isǝrayila. Lang munǝo candǝ ka, amǝ'Filisti gandǝ amǝ'Isǝrayila, à wal-lú aburana mala amǝ'Isǝrayila kǝla aɓwana á-ine a ɓawan lwa. 
\p  
\v 3 Lang amǝ'lwa nyarǝna a kàttì ka, aɓwana-mǝgule mala Isǝrayila bang ama, <<Palang sǝ Yahweh eari amǝ'Filisti sǝ à li sǝm a munǝo yalung? Ɓǝ̀ sǝm kyane ɓǝ̀ sǝm twal Akwati Kùrcau mala Yahweh a Shilo, ɓǝ̀ sǝm yinǝi kani, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ pà atà sǝm, sǝ ɓǝ̀ amsǝ sǝm a ɓabù aɓisǝm amǝbura.>> 
\p  
\v 4 Nda à tùr aburana a Shilo, sǝ à kya twal Akwati Kùrcau mala Yahweh Mǝtala Abangŋo, mǝnana do a buno-murǝm a nre ka \f + \fr 4:4 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pur 25:22; 2Sam 6:2; Ang 80:1; 99:1\ft .\f*acerup ka. Amuna-burana ɓari mala Eli, yià Hofni andǝ Finehas ka, à nda kano atà Akwati Kùrcau mala Ɓakuli.  
\v 5 Lang à yinanǝ Akwati Kùrcau mala Yahweh aɓa kàttì ka, Isǝrayila kat ɓuà-gāwàn mǝcandǝe gandǝa nzali gǝggǝli.  
\v 6 Sǝ lang amǝ'Filisti ok gì ɓuà-gāwàn ngga, à bang ama, <<Mana nda ɓá mǝnia yi gāwàn mǝcandǝe aɓa kàttì mala amǝ'Ibǝru ka?>> Lang à yi sǝlǝa ama, Akwati Kùrcau mala Yahweh yina aɓa kàttì ka,  
\v 7 ɓangciu pàkki amǝ'Filisti, acemǝnana à bang ama, <<Aɓakuli yina a kàttì malea! Caukwanban nǝ sǝm! Kǝgìr kǝla man kum sǝm a kǝ fara ɗàng!  
\v 8 Caukwanban nǝ sǝm! Yana nǝ̀ amsǝ sǝm a ɓabù aɓakuli mǝ'rǝcandǝe man? Amǝnia ka, à nda ka aɓakuli mǝnana à wal amǝ'Masar nǝ koya ulang agir'murmwana a ɓabondo ka!  
\v 9 Wu cam kàngkàng, wu duk aburana,\f + \fr 4:9 \fq wu duk aburana \ft ko <<cam wara kǝla aburana>>\f* wun amǝ'Filisti, ɓǝ̀ ana raka wun nǝ̀ duk aguro mala amǝ'Ibǝru, kǝla mana à duk aguro ma'wun ngga! Wu duk aburana sǝ wu munǝo!>> 
\p  
\v 10 Nda amǝ'Filisti munǝo, sǝ à gandǝ Isǝrayila, sǝ koya ɓwabura ka, ɓangŋa nyare a gumli male. À wal-lú amǝ'Isǝrayila kǝ̀rkǝ́r: asoje-kusǝu á-lumi-tàrú (30,000) wù a kun-munǝo.  
\v 11 Akwati Kùrcau mala Ɓakuli ka, Amǝ'Filisti é à umnǝi, sǝ amuna-burana mala Eli ɓari, yià Hofni andǝ Finehas ka, à wal-luia. 
\s1 Lú mala Eli 
\p  
\v 12 Akǝ pwari mǝno ka, ɓè ɓwabura ɓwa'Benjami ɓangŋa a kun-munǝo sǝ yiu a Shilo nǝ gìr'nggūrǝu mǝsange arǝì nǝ tú a ɓamuri.  
\v 13 Lang yi bik ka, Eli naban do yak, amúr buno male a gírí kun-nda aban sǝn njar, ɓalǝi kǝ kasǝki atàcau mala Akwati Kùrcau mala Ɓakuli. Lang ɓwabure kùtí aɓa nggea-là sǝ bangce gìr mǝnana kumban ngga, nggea-là kat so ɓua gǝu.  
\v 14 Eli ok ɓua-woi'woi sǝ ɗìban ama, <<Mana nda ɓá mǝnia yì zunggǝli mala ban ngga?>> Pǝlǝa ɓwabure larri yiu, sǝ banggi Eli cê.  
\v 15 (Eli ka ndanǝ apǝlǝa lumi-tongno-nong-ine-bwamdǝ-tongno-nong-tàrú (98), sǝ anggur-mǝsǝì wuna, acemani ka kǝ sǝnban pepè ɗàng.)  
\v 16 Ɓwabure ne Eli ama, <<Mǝ nda ɓwa mǝnana ǝn pur a kun-munǝo ka; ǝn ɓangŋa a kun-munǝo yalung.>> 
\p Eli ɗì ama, <<Mana kumban, munem?>> 
\p  
\v 17 Ɓwabure eari wi ama, <<Isǝrayila ɓangŋa a ɓadǝmba amǝ'Filisti, sǝ à wal-lú amǝ Isǝrayila nǝ nggea walban! Amuna-burana mô ɓari, Hofni andǝ Finehas ka à walnia, sǝ Akwati Kùrcau mala Ɓakuli ka, amǝ'Filisti angŋǝni!>> 
\p  
\v 18 Lang bangcau mala Akwati Kùrcau mala Ɓakuli ka, kara Eli nyare kpa nǝtakwari amúr buno male a nkanggari bankutio, myali ɓunno, sǝ wǔ, acemǝnana enà sǝ dǝmbǝrya. Eli ka nda mǝɓashi amúr Isǝrayila mala apǝlǝa lumi-ine. 
\s1 Lú mala mālá Finehas 
\p  
\v 19 Nkil Eli, mālá Finehas ka ndanǝ muna a bumi, sǝ pwari gbashi male gbashìna tù. Lang ok cau ama Akwati Kùrcau mala Ɓakuli ka à angŋǝni, sǝ nkili-mǝɓwabure andǝ burí ka à wuna ka, kara kùndǝ a nzali sǝ gbashi. Sǝama kwanban mala gbashi ɓākì.\f + \fr 4:19 \fq kara kùndǝ a nzali sǝ gbashi. Sǝama kwanban mala gbashi ɓākì. \ft ko <<kara kùndǝ a nzali sǝ gbashi, acemǝnana kwanban mala gbashi ɓākì.>>\f* 
\v 20 Sǝ lang malanǝ̀ wù ka, amamǝna mǝnana à ndaban came amurí ka à ne wi ama, <<Cè ɓangciu pàkkô ɗàng! A ɓǝlna muna-ɓwabura!>> Sǝ yì ka, nyesǝia wia kǝcau ko tsǝkiri ɗàng.  
\v 21 Pǝlǝa tsǝki mune lullǝu ama Ikabot,\f + \fr 4:21 \ft Sǝni gbal aɓa: \xt 1Sam 14:3\ft .\f* ɓālǝi ama, <<Ɓoarɓwa mala Ɓakuli nyìngŋǝ̀nà Isǝrayila.>> Pà mǝnia yi lullǝu ka acemǝnana à gbamina Akwati Kùrcau mala Ɓakuli arǝ amǝ'Isǝrayila, sǝ ace lú mala nkili-mǝɓwabure andǝ burí.  
\v 22 Bang ama, <<Ɓoarɓwa mala Ɓakuli nyìngŋǝ̀nà Isǝrayila, acemǝnana Akwati Kùrcau mala Ɓakuli ka, à gbamini.>> 
\c 5  
\s1 Akwati Kùrcau mala Ɓakuli pè amǝ'Filisti tanni 
\p  
\v 1 Anzǝm mana amǝ'Filisti angŋǝna Akwati Kùrcau mala Ɓakuli ka, à twali a Ebeneza sǝ à warini a Ashdot.  
\v 2 Pǝlǝa amǝ'Filisti twal Akwati Kùrcau mala Ɓakuli sǝ à yinǝi a ndà mala \f + \fr 5:2 \ft Sǝni gbal aɓa: \xt Akas 16:23\ft .\f*Dagon, sǝ à kya tsǝi a nkanggari Dagon.  
\v 3 Lang banfana ka, amǝ Ashdot lo nǝ dǝmbari sǝ à yi sǝni ka, Dagon kpana nǝ ɓamǝsǝi a nzali aɓadǝm Akwati Kùrcau mala Yahweh. Nda à twal Dagon sǝ à tsǝi a bancame male.  
\v 4 Sǝ lang banfana ɗǝm ngga, à lo nǝ dǝmbari sǝ à yi sǝni ka, Dagon kpana nǝ ɓamǝsǝi a nzali aɓadǝm Akwati Kùrcau mala Yahweh, ɓamur Dagon andǝ abui kǝm na aban nongŋo a bankutio, à ɓungina. Kǝ nggunrǝ Dagon na ue ka.  
\v 5 Mǝnia ka nda gìr mǝnana tsǝa sǝ apǝris mala Dagon andǝ aɓwana mana kat à kǝ kúti a ndà mala Dagon a Ashdot ka, à kǝ tsǝk kusǝia amur bankutio a ndà mala Dagon raka bà yalung. 
\p  
\v 6 Bù Yahweh sulǝ nǝ-dǝmbǝrya amúr aɓwana mana à ndanǝdo a Ashdot ka, sǝ yinǝia wia gìr'mur'mwana amúrià, sǝ koea nǝ kwano rǝu-mwarkya, nggearǝ Ashdot andǝ amuna-là male.  
\v 7 Lang aɓwana mala Ashdot sǝn gìr mǝnana kǝ̀ kumia ka, à bang ama, <<Akwati Kùrcau mala Ɓakuli mala amǝ'Isǝrayila ɓǝ̀kǝa ue a ban sǝm ɗàng, acemǝnana buì sulǝna nǝ gìr'mur'mwana kǝ̀rkǝ́r amúr sǝm sǝ amúr Dagon, ɓakuli ma'sǝm!>> 
\p  
\v 8 Nda à túrban sǝ à ramba amǝ'yálmurû kat mala amǝ'Filisti abanɓwáná, sǝ à ɗia ama, <<Mana sǝm nǝ̀ pang nǝ Akwati Kùrcau mala Ɓakuli mala amǝ'Isǝrayila?>> À ear ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ sǝm yinǝ Akwati Kùrcau mala Ɓakuli mala amǝ'Isǝrayila a Gat.>> Nda à yinǝ Akwati Kùrcau mala Ɓakuli mala amǝ'Isǝrayila abanì ka.  
\v 9 Sǝama lang à warina nǝi kano ka, bù Yahweh sulǝ amúr nggea-là mǝno gbal, mǝnana turia aɓa nggea kàrmúrû ka. Rǝu-mwarkya sakki arǝ aɓwana mala nggea-lê, amuna andǝ aɓwamǝgule kat. 
\p  
\v 10 Pǝlǝa à tasǝ Akwati Kùrcau mala Ɓakuli a Ekǝron. Sǝama lang Akwati Kùrcau mala Ɓakuli bwalǝna Ekǝron ngga, amǝ Ekǝron túr kunia a ɓua ama, <<À yinanǝ Akwati mala Ɓakuli mala amǝ'Isǝrayila aban sǝm ace wal-lú sǝm andǝ aɓwana ma'sǝm!>>  
\v 11 Nda à túrban sǝ à ramba amǝ'yálmurû mala amǝ'Filisti kat abanɓwáná sǝ à bang ama, <<Wu nyesǝ Akwati mala Ɓakuli mala amǝ'Isǝrayila ɓǝ̀ nyar a ban mǝnana pùr kam ngga, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ kǝa wal-lú sǝm andǝ aɓwana ma'sǝm ɗàng.>> Kàrmúrû mala lú yi sulǝ amur nggea-là mǝno puppup atàcau mala gir'murmwana mana yiu amúrià nǝ bù Ɓakuli ka.  
\v 12 Aɓwana mǝnana à wù raka, à bwal nǝ kwano rǝu-mwarkya, sǝ ɓua mala nggea-lê lo a kuli. 
\c 6  
\s1 Amǝ'Filisti nyesǝ Akwati Kùrcau 
\p  
\v 1 Lang Akwati Kùrcau mala Yahweh pàngŋǝ́nà azongŋo tongno-nong-ɓari a nzali mala amǝ'Filisti ka,  
\v 2 Amǝ'Filisti tunǝ apǝris andǝ amǝ'ɓángnǝ́-ɓángna sǝ à ɗia ama, <<Mana sǝm nǝ̀ pang nǝ Akwati Kùrcau mala Yahweh? Wu bangga sǝm lang sǝ sǝm nǝ̀ nyesǝ man yì Akwati Kùrcau mala Yahweh a ban mǝnana pùr kam ngga?>> 
\p  
\v 3 À ear ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ wun nǝ̀ nyesǝ Akwati Kùrcau mala Ɓakuli mala Isǝrayila ka, wu kǝa nyesǝi nǝ ɓālǝi atarǝì ɗàng; koɓǝ̀ lang le ka wu nyesǝi nǝ \f + \fr 6:3 \ft Sǝni gbal aɓa: \xt Pǝris 5:15-16\ft .\f*pàgir mala mbwegìr ace kumcau. Anggo ka, sǝ wun nǝ̀ kum twalbanì, sǝ wun nǝ̀ bwalta gìr mana tsǝa sǝ buì loapi múr wun raka.>>  
\v 4 Pǝlǝa à ɗìban ama, <<Ya ulang pàgir mala mbwegìr ace kumcau na sǝm nǝ̀ tasǝî wi?>> 
\p Apǝris andǝ amǝ'ɓángnǝ́-ɓángna nyesǝia wia ama, <<Lakkì mala amǝ'yálmurû mala amǝ'Filisti ka, à nda tongno. Acemani ka, wu tasǝ aɓǝ̀nzál mala rǝu-mwarkya mala bolo-njengǝlan tongno andǝ aɓǝ̀nzál mala ankwam mala bolo-njengǝlan tongno, acemǝnana mǝno ka, nda mwashat andǝ gir'murmwana mana kum wun andǝ amǝ'yálmurû ma'wun ngga.  
\v 5 Acemani ka, dumǝna púp wun nǝ̀ pak aɓǝ̀nzál mala rǝu-mwarkya andǝ aɓǝ̀nzál mala ankwam mǝnana à kiɗiki nzali ka. Dumǝna púp wun nǝ̀ pè Ɓakuli mala amǝ'Isǝrayila gulo. Yakǝla buì nǝ̀ pàk halku amúr wun, sǝ amúr aɓakuli ma'wun, andǝ nzali ma'wun.  
\v 6 Palang sǝ wun nǝ̀ tǝr ɓabum wun kǝla mǝnana amǝ'Masar andǝ Firona tǝr ɓabumia ka? Anzǝm mana pàngŋǝ́nia wia gìr'kwanban arǝia ka, à nying amǝ'Isǝrayila ace mǝnana ɓǝà u ka re?  
\v 7 Ado ka, wu kyane, wu pàk bǝsa keke-ndá. Wu alta andá ɓari amǝ-pakiura, mǝnana à malaká tsǝkia wia nggun-rya a myalia raka. Wu kùrî andá mǝnia ka keke-ndá arǝ nggun-rya a myalia, sǝ wu pǝr amunia ɓǝà nyare a domwan malea.  
\v 8 Sǝ wu twal Akwati Kùrcau mala Yahweh, wu tsǝi amúr keke-ndá, sǝ aɓǝ̀nzál mala bolo-njengǝlan mǝnana wun nǝ̀ tasǝia kǝla pàgir mala mbwegìr ace kumcau ka, wu tsǝia aɓa ɓè akwati a nkanggari Akwati Kùrcau. Sǝ wu tasǝta keke-ndá ɓǝ̀ ukia o male.  
\v 9 Sǝama wu tsǝkmǝsǝ wun. Ɓǝ̀ umnǝ njar Bet-Shemesh aɓa nzali male ka, lǝmdǝ ama Ɓakuli mala amǝ Isǝrayila nda mǝnana pàkka sǝm mǝnia yi nggea gìr mǝɓike ka. Sǝ ɓǝ̀ pàk anggo raka, sǝm nǝ̀ sǝlǝa ama buì nda mǝnana kok sǝm ngga ɗàng; múrɓikea na mǝnana kum sǝm ngga.>> 
\p  
\v 10 Nda aburane pàk kǝla mana à banggia wia ka. À twal andá ɓari amǝ-pakiura, à tsǝkia wia nggun-rya a myalia sǝ à kùrrì arǝ keke-ndá; osso à kasǝkun amunia a là.  
\v 11 À tsǝk Akwati Kùrcau mala Yahweh amúr keke-ndê, sǝ akwati mǝnana nǝ aɓǝ̀nzál mala bolo-njengǝlan mala ankwam andǝ rǝu-mwarkya malea ka, à tsǝì a nkanggari.  
\v 12 Pǝlǝa andê lo ò amur njargula ká Bet-Shemesh; à dǝshi kporong aban ká nǝ ɓua, sǝ ko à kyang a bu-mǝli ko bu-mǝnggare ɗàng. Amǝ'yálmurû mala amǝ'Filisti gya anzǝmia aban ká ɗār a nzong-nzali mala Bet-Shemesh. 
\p  
\v 13 A bàkú mǝno ka aɓwana mala Bet-Shemesh na aban um mǝssa-alkama malea a ɓangŋaban ace pwan-gìrɓaban. Lang à loasǝ mǝsǝia sǝ à sǝn Akwati Kùrcau mala Yahweh ka, à pàk-banɓoarnado nǝ sǝne.  
\v 14 Keke-ndê yiu a ɓaban mala Jesǝwa ɓwa Bet-Shemesh, sǝ cam abanì a nkanggari ɓè tali mǝgule. Pǝlǝa aɓwana mana abanì ka, à arki akpamgbang mala keke-ndê sǝ à pàgir mala pisǝe kǝring nǝ andê aban Yahweh.  
\v 15 Pǝlǝa amǝ'Lawi twal Akwati Kùrcau mala Yahweh andǝ akwati mana a nkanggari, mǝnana ndanǝ aɓǝ̀nzál mala bolo-njengǝlan aɓalǝi ka, sǝ à tsǝia amúr nggea tali mǝno. Sǝ amǝ Bet-Shemesh pàgir mala pisǝe kǝring andǝ apagir mala gir'nkila aban Yahweh a pwari mǝno.  
\v 16 Amǝ'yálmurû tongno mala amǝ'Filisti came sǝ à sǝn gìr mǝno kat, pǝlǝa à nyar a Ekǝron akǝ pwari mǝno. 
\p  
\v 17 Amǝnia ka, à nda ka aɓǝ̀nzál mala rǝu-mwarkya mala bolo-njengǝlan, mǝnana amǝ'Filisti yinǝi kǝla pàgir mala mbwegìr ace kumcau aban Yahweh ka: mwashat ace cauɓikea mala Ashdot, mwashat ace cauɓikea mala Gaza, mwashat ace cauɓikea mala Ashkelon, mwashat ace cauɓikea mala Gat, mwashat ace cauɓikea mala Ekǝron;  
\v 18 sǝ aɓǝ̀nzál nkwam mala bolo-njengǝlan ngga, à nda akúnì nggea-là mala amúrû tongno mala amǝ'Filisti, tite arǝ anggea-là mǝnana à kària nǝ akanggǝrang sheran aban ká arǝ amuna-là malea mana a patal ka. Nggea tali mǝnana à tsǝk Akwati Kùrcau mala Yahweh amurí ka, ndakam bà yalung a ɓaban mala Jesǝwa ɓwa Bet-Shemesh, ace kasǝɓalǝu arǝ gìr mǝnana kumban ngga. 
\p  
\v 19 Sǝama Yahweh wal-lú aɓea aburana mala Bet-Shemesh, acemǝnana à sǝn ɓá Akwati Kùrcau mala Yahweh ka. Yahweh wal-lú aburana malea lumi-tongno-nong-ɓari. Amǝ Bet-Shemesh pak-bumkiɗikea acemǝnana Yahweh wal-lú aɓwana malea nǝ nggea walban ngga. 
\p  
\v 20 Pǝlǝa amǝ Bet-Shemesh bang ama, <<Yana nǝ̀ gandǝnǝ came aɓadǝm Yahweh, yì Ɓakuli mǝfele? Sǝ aban ayan sǝ sǝm nǝ̀ tasǝì ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ upi ban sǝm ngga?>> 
\p  
\v 21 Nda à tasǝ amǝ'na-túrbân a Kiriat-Jarim, nǝ cau ama, <<Amǝ'Filisti nyesǝna Akwati Kùrcau mala Yahweh. Wu yiu wu twali, wu umnǝi a ban wun.>> 
\c 7  
\m  
\v 1 Pǝlǝa aburana mala Kiriat-Jarim yiu à yi twal Akwati kùrcau mala Yahweh; à wari nǝi a ɓala mala Aminadap mǝnana nda amúr mgbang-ban ngga. À twal muna-ɓwabura male Eleaza ɓǝ̀ do ndà mǝ'yál Akwati kùrcau mala Yahweh, ɓǝ̀ kǝ ɗenyinǝi.  
\v 2 Twal a pwari mǝno ka Akwati kùrcau mala Yahweh ue kano a Kiriat-Jarim banì sau kǝ̀rkǝ́r, pǝlǝa lumi-ɓari. Arǝ apǝlǝkia mǝno ka, amǝ Isǝrayila ɓua, ɓua keban mala alta Yahweh. 
\s1 Samuyila duk mǝɓashi amur Isǝrayila 
\p  
\v 3 Sǝ Samuyila banggi ɓala mala Isǝrayila kat ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ wun nǝ̀ nyar aban Yahweh nǝ ɓabum wun kat ka, dumǝna púp wun nǝ̀ vwakibu wun arǝ abǝri ɓakuli andǝ aɓǝ̀nzál Ashtarot, ɓǝà pùrî ɓalǝ wun.\f + \fr 7:3 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Jes 24:23\ft .\f* Wu pà ɓamur rǝ wun kat-kat aban Yahweh, sǝ wu peri abani nǝmurǝì, sǝ yì ka nǝ̀ amsǝ wun a ɓabu amǝ'Filisti.>>  
\v 4 Nda amǝ Isǝrayila yi pusǝki ankúl mala Ba'al andǝ Ashtarot à sukkia, sǝ à peri aban Yahweh nǝmurǝì ka. 
\p  
\v 5 Pǝlǝa Samuyila bang ama, <<Wu ram Isǝrayila kat a Mizǝpa sǝ mǝ nǝ pakhiwi aban Yahweh ace wun.>>  
\v 6 Lang à yi ramna a Mizǝpa ka, à tò mùr sǝ à solǝi a nzali a ɓadǝm Yahweh. A pwari mǝno kat ka, à gilmùr sǝ à bang nǝ kunia ama <<Sǝm pàngŋǝ́nì Yahweh cauɓikea.>> Samuyila yi do nda mǝɓashi amúr Isǝrayila a Mizǝpa. 
\p  
\v 7 Lang amǝ'Filisti ok ama amǝ Isǝrayila ramna a Mizǝpa ka, amurǝma mala amǝ'Filisti lo à yiu ace kánǝ munǝo arǝia. Sǝ lang amǝ Isǝrayila okce ka, ɓangciu pakkia wia arǝ amǝ'Filisti.  
\v 8 Sǝ amǝ Isǝrayila zǝmbi Samuyila ama, <<Lidǝmba nǝ ɓua ace sǝm aban Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'sǝm, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ amsǝ sǝm a bu amǝ'Filisti.>>  
\v 9 Pǝlǝa Samuyila twal muna-nzur mana nda a kúnkiura ka, pànà gir'nkila mala pisǝì kǝring nǝi a bǝsa aban Yahweh. Sǝ Samuyila ɓua aban Yahweh ɓǝ̀ bwalì amǝ Isǝrayila kàm, sǝ Yahweh ok ɓua male. 
\p  
\v 10 Lang Samuyila na aban pa gir'nkila mala pisǝe a bǝsa ka, amǝ'lwa mala amǝ'Filisti soa aban yiu nǝ munǝo arǝ amǝ Isǝrayila. Sǝama a pwari mǝno ka, Yahweh ìm arǝ amǝ'lwa mala amǝ'Filisti a kùli nǝ giu mǝcandǝe kǝla sa mala mgbarangce. Yahweh túriá aɓa múrzurǝkya, nda à ɓangŋa a ɓadǝmba amǝ'lwa mala amǝ Isǝrayila ka.  
\v 11 Sǝ aburana mala amǝ Isǝrayila purî ɓá Mizǝpa nǝ mire, à pǝrta amǝ'Filisti sǝ à kǝ wal-luia amur njar aban ká ɗār a ɓangŋaban mala Bet-kar. 
\p  
\v 12 Anzǝm mǝno ka, Samuyila twal nggea-tali sǝ yi kwaki anre Mizǝpa andǝ Shen, sǝ tunǝ lullǝ banì ama Ebeneza,\f + \fr 7:12 \fq Ebeneza \ft ka ɓālǝi ka nda <<tali mala gbasha.>>\f* acemǝnana bang ama, <<Ba ado ka, Yahweh na pakka sǝm gbasha ka!>>  
\v 13 Anggo sǝ amǝ'Filisti ka à paria, sǝ à nyare à kútí ɗǝm a nzong-nzali mala amǝ Isǝrayila ama à nǝ̀ yiu nǝ lwa ɗang. Aɓa do-yilǝmu kat mala Samuyila ka, bù Yahweh ɓìkî amǝ'Filisti.  
\v 14 Amǝ'lwa mala amǝ Isǝrayila ak anggea-là mǝnana amǝ'Filisti ea arǝ amǝ Isǝrayila ka, à nyesǝia a bu amǝ Isǝrayila, twal a Ekǝron aban ká Gat. Acili abân mana tù nǝ anggea-là mǝnana amǝ'Filisti ea ɗiɗyal ka, amǝ'lwa mala amǝ Isǝrayila nyesǝia a bu amǝ Isǝrayila. Ɗǝm ngga do-rǝpwala yi pa a nreka amǝ Isǝrayila andǝ amǝ'Amor. 
\p  
\v 15 Samuyila lidǝmba nǝ do mǝɓashi amur amǝ Isǝrayila bà lú male.  
\v 16 Koya pǝlǝa ka kǝ twal gya aban ká andǝ nyare arǝ anggea-là Betel, andǝ Gilgal sǝ Mizǝpa. Pàkkî Isǝrayila ɓashi arǝ abân mǝnia ka kat.  
\v 17 Anzǝm mana malna ka, nǝ̀ nyar a Rama, ban mǝnana ɓala male pàk kàm ngga. A Rama gbal ka nda mǝɓashi, sǝ ɓakkî Yahweh gyangŋan kàm. 
\c 8  
\s1 Amǝ Isǝrayila alta kum murǝm 
\p  
\v 1 Lang yi bwalna arǝ apǝlǝkia mala e mala Samuyila ka, tsǝk amuni ɓǝà duk amǝ'ɓashi amur amǝ Isǝrayila.  
\v 2 Lullǝ muna-dǝmba male nda Joyel, sǝ ɓaria muni ka, lullǝi nda Abija. À duk amǝ'ɓashi a Biyasheba.  
\v 3 Amuni ka, à twal kusǝi ɗàng, à kyanggî njar ace alta kume, à ak pàbunǝnzali sǝ à pūrǝ ɓashi. 
\p  
\v 4 Pǝlǝa aɓwana-mǝgule mala Isǝrayila kat, ram rǝia abanɓwáná sǝ à yiu aban Samuyila a Rama;  
\v 5 à yi ne wi ama, <<Sǝni, a ena, sǝ amunio twalkusǝo ɗàng. Ado ka, tsǝka sǝm murǝm mǝnana nǝ̀ yálmúr sǝm kǝla mala acili anzali kat ka.>>  
\v 6 Sǝama cau mǝnia à ne ama, <<Pà sǝm murǝm mǝnana nǝ̀ yálmúr sǝm>> ngga, pwasǝbum Samuyila ɗàng. Nda Samuyila pakhiwi aban Yahweh ka.  
\v 7 Osso Yahweh banggi Samuyila ama, <<Kpata gì aɓwana man, pàk gìr mǝnana kat à banggo ka, acemǝnana a nda mǝnana à ginǝo ka ɗàng, mǝ nda mǝnana à ginǝam ɓǝn nggá duk murǝm amúrià raka.  
\v 8 Kǝla mǝnana à pa, twal a pwari mǝnana ǝn pusǝia à purî ɓá Masar ba yalung ngga, à ginǝkiam, sǝ à peri aban aɓea aɓakuli ka, nda kǝgìr mǝnana à kǝ pakko gbal ka.  
\v 9 Acemani ka, kpata gia; sǝama awu nǝ nunkiria pepè, sǝ awu nǝ bǝlia wia lang sǝ murǝm mǝnana nǝ̀ yálmuria ka nǝ̀ pàngŋǝ́nǝia.>> 
\s1 Nunkiru mala Samuyila arǝ amurǝma 
\p  
\v 10 Anggo sǝ Samuyila bang acau mala Yahweh kat aban aɓwana mǝnana à alkiyita murǝm a baní ka.  
\v 11 Bang ama, <<Ani sǝ murǝm mǝnana nǝ̀ yálmúr wun ngga, nǝ̀ pangnǝ wun: nǝ̀ twal amuna ma'wun nǝ̀ tsǝia à nǝ̀ duk amǝkok awaru-pǝr andǝ apǝr male mǝnana à nǝ̀ nggǝ ɓang aɓadǝm awaru-pǝr male ka.  
\v 12 Sǝ nǝ̀ tsǝkî ɓamurì amǝ'sàrǝ̀ban amur aɓwana á-á, andǝ amǝ'sàrǝ̀ban amur aɓwana á-lumi-tongno, sǝ aɓea ka à nǝ̀ duk amǝ'rya andǝ amǝ'pwan-gìrɓaban male, andǝ amǝ'tulki agirbura mala lwa andǝ agirtúró mala awaru-pǝr male.  
\v 13 Nǝ̀ twal amuna-mamǝna ma'wun ɓǝà pǝlǝ amǝ'pakki agir pà'rǝmban-mǝɓoarne, andǝ amǝ'lamggi agirlina, andǝ amǝ'lúrǝ́gir.  
\v 14 Nǝ̀ ak aɓaban mǝɓoarne ma'wun andǝ aɓaban-anap, andǝ aɓaban mala anggun-olif ma'wun sǝ nǝ̀ pè amǝ'túró male.  
\v 15 Nǝ ak kāmbe mwashat aɓa lum mala mǝsǝsa andǝ aɓǝla-anap ma'wun, sǝ nǝ̀ pè amǝgulo andǝ amǝ'túró male.  
\v 16 Nǝ̀ twal aguro ma'wun aburana andǝ amamǝna, andǝ alaggana mǝnana à nda dwat ka, andǝ amǝdambǝriso ma'wun, sǝ nǝ̀ tsǝia aɓa túró male.  
\v 17 Nǝ̀ ak kāmbe mwashat aɓa lum mala agirkusǝu ma'wun, sǝ wun nǝ̀ duk aguro male.  
\v 18 A pwarì mǝno ka, wun nǝ̀ ɓua ace kum usǝlǝo a bù murǝm mǝnana wu tàrrî ɓamurǝ wun ngga, sǝ Yahweh pà nǝ̀ oka wun amǝno yì pwari ka ɗàng.>> 
\s1 Yahweh pè amǝ Isǝrayila zǝmba malea 
\p  
\v 19 Kat andǝ manì ka, aɓwe ginǝ okî Samuyila. À bang ama, <<Awo, ma'sǝm ngga sǝm nggǝ earce murǝm amur sǝm,  
\v 20 ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ sǝm pa kǝla acili anzali kat, sǝ ɗǝm ngga ɓǝ̀ murǝm ma'sǝm ɓǝ̀ kǝ pakka sǝm ɓashi sǝ ɓǝ̀ dupa sǝm a dǝmba, sǝ nǝ̀ lwa-lwa ma'sǝm.>> 
\p  
\v 21 Lang Samuyila ongŋǝna acau mala aɓwe ka, ɓǝsǝlǝia ɓǝ̀ Yahweh oea.  
\v 22 Sǝ Yahweh banggi Samuyila ama, <<Kpata gia sǝ wu pea wia murǝm.>> Samuyila pǝlǝa ne aburana mala Isǝrayila ama, <<Koyan ngga ɓǝ̀ nyare a nggea-là male.>> 
\c 9  
\s1 À tàr Sawul ɓǝ̀ duk murǝm 
\p  
\v 1 Ɓè ɓwa'Benjami nakam mǝnana à tunǝki ama Kish ka, muna-ɓwabura mala Abiyel, muna-ɓwabura mala Zero, muna-ɓwabura mala Bekorat, muna-ɓwabura mala Afiya, ɓwa'Benjami, mǝgǝna na.  
\v 2 Ndanǝ muna-ɓwabura mǝnana à tunǝki ama Sawul ka, lagga mǝɓoarjami. Kǝ ɓwa pà kàm aɓa Isǝrayila mǝnana ɓoarjam kútì ka ɗàng. Twal a nkpamtari aban umnǝ kuli ka, dāh'rya kútì koyan atà aɓwe. 
\p  
\v 3 A bàkú mǝno ka, aɓea mǝdambǝriso mala Kish, tár Sawul ɓwaro. Nda Kish banggi muni Sawul ama, <<Twal mwashat atà alaggana atò, sǝ wu lo, wu kya alta amǝdambǝriso.>>  
\v 4 Sǝ Sawul kùtí nǝɓa nzali múr ankono mala Ifǝrem sǝ yi kútí nǝɓa nzali Shalisha, sǝama à kumia ɗàng. Sǝ à kùtí nǝɓa nzali Sha'alim, sǝ à kumia ɗàng. Pǝlǝa à yi kútí nǝɓa nzali Benjami, sǝ à kumia ɗàng. 
\p  
\v 5 Lang à yina a nzali Zuf ka, Sawul banggi lagga male mǝnana nda atè ka ama, <<Yiu sǝm nǝ̀ nyare, ɓǝ̀ ana raka, tárrám nǝ̀ nying pàk ɗenyicau amur amǝdambǝriso, nǝ̀ kùtí a bumpina ace sǝm.>>  
\v 6 Sǝ lagga male ka banggi wi ama, <<Sǝni, ɓwa mala Ɓakuli na a nggea-là man, ɓwa na à kǝ gusǝlǝce kǝ̀rkǝ́r; gir mǝnana kat ne ka kǝ lumsǝo. Ado ka, fa sǝm nǝ̀ ká abani, earka nǝ bangga sǝm njar mǝnana sǝm nǝ̀ ká kàm ngga.>> 
\p  
\v 7 Pǝlǝa Sawul ne guro male ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ sǝm na ama sǝm nǝ̀ ká aban ɓwabure ka, mana sǝm nǝ̀ kánǝi wi? Bǝredi mǝnana aɓalǝ abuku ma'sǝm ngga malǝna. Sǝm pànǝ kǝ ɓoro mǝnana sǝm nǝ̀ kánǝi ɓwa mala Ɓakuli ka ɗàng. Mana sǝm ndani?>>  
\v 8 Laggè earî Sawul ɗǝm ama, <<Sǝni, akani ka, mǝ ndanǝ gauwe-ine mala shekel mala bolo-azǝrfa a buam, mǝ nǝ nggá pè ɓwa mala Ɓakuli ɓǝ̀ na sǝm njar mǝnana sǝm nǝ̀ ká kam ngga.>>  
\v 9 (Ɗiɗyal a Isǝrayila ka, lang ɓwa earce ɗìbancau aban Ɓakuli ka, nǝ̀ bang ama, <<Yiu, ɓǝ̀ sǝm kya aban mǝ'sǝna,>> acemǝnana <<mǝɓangnǝa>> yalung ngga à tunǝi ɗiɗyal ama mǝ'sǝna.)  
\v 10 Sǝ Sawul banggi lagga male ama, <<Cau mò na jik, fa sǝm nǝ̀ ká.>> Nda à wari a nggea-là mǝnana ɓwa mala Ɓakuli na kam ngga.  
\v 11 Lang à ndaban eau a mgbangban aban ká a nggea-lê ka, à je andǝ aɓea ansarina aban yiu ace ká to mùr, sǝ à ɗia ama, <<Mǝ'sǝna na kani le?>>  
\v 12 À earia wia ama, <<Nda kani; wu sǝni, nda kǝ ká a dǝm wun ngga. Wu fà rǝ wun. Ndo kǝ kùtí nǝ kutio a nggea-là ka, acemǝnana aɓwe nanǝ pa gìr'nkila yalung a ban-mǝdāhre.  
\v 13 Lang wu kutina ka, wun nǝ̀ kumi a kún nggea-là; kǝ umnǝ o a ban-mǝdāhre ace li girlina. Aɓwe pà nǝ̀ lìli ɗang sheɓǝ̀ yina ka, acemǝnana dumǝna púp nǝ̀ tsǝkî gìr'nkila bu; sǝ anzǝm mǝno ka, abǝri mǝnana à tunǝia ka, à nǝ̀ lìli. Ado ka, wu eau tu, wun nǝ̀ nggá kumi.>>  
\v 14 Nda à eau aban ká nggea-lê ka. Lang à nǝ̀ nggǝ kùtí aɓa nggea-là ka, à sǝn Samuyila dǝshinia, nǝ̀ eau aban ká ban-mǝdāhre. 
\p  
\v 15 Nongŋo mwashat a dǝm yiu mala Sawul ka, Yahweh angŋa-dǝmba lǝmdǝni Samuyila ama:  
\v 16 <<Li ani ka, mǝ nǝ tasǝ ɓeɓwa mala nzali Benjami a bano, awu nǝ ɗārǝi ɓǝ̀ duk múrû mala aɓwana mem amǝ Isǝrayila. Nǝ̀ amsǝ aɓwana mem a bù amǝ'Filisti. Acemǝnana ǝn sǝnǝna tanni mala aɓwana mem, sǝ ɓua malea bwalǝna banam.>>  
\v 17 Lang Samuyila sǝn Sawul ka, Yahweh banggi wi ama, <<Ɓwa mǝnana ǝn nô ce ka ndya ka! Yi nda ɓwa mǝnana nǝ̀ yálmúr aɓwana mem ngga.>>  
\v 18 Pǝlǝa Sawul gbàshìban Samuyila a tsùrú mala bankutio a nggea-là sǝ na ama, <<Ida banggam, ake sǝ ɓala mala mǝ'sǝna pa?>>  
\v 19 Samuyila earî wi ama, <<Mǝ nda mǝ'sǝnê. Fa aɓadǝmbam a ban-mǝdāhre. Wun kǝm ngga, wun nǝ̀ lìli atàm yalung, sǝ lí nǝ dǝmbari ka, mǝ nǝ nying wun, wun nǝ̀ o, sǝ gìr mǝnana kat a ɓabumo ka, mǝ nǝ nô.  
\v 20 Sǝ amur cau mala amǝdambǝriso mò mǝnana à ɓwaro nongŋo tàrú mǝnana à kùtí ka, kǝa tsǝk ɓalǝo arǝia ɗàng, acemǝnana à kumǝnia. Sǝ yana nda ɓwe mǝnana Isǝrayila kat earkiyice kǝ̀rkǝ́r ka? A nda andǝ ɓala mala tárró kat re?>>  
\v 21 Sawul pa eare ama, <<Mǝ nda ɓwa'Benjami, aɓa rítǎu mala atau mala Isǝrayila re? Sǝ nggurkwar mem ngga nda mǝkyauwe aɓalǝ anggurkwar mala tàu mala Benjami re? Sǝ palang sǝ a nam cau ani?>> 
\p  
\v 22 Pǝlǝa Samuyila warinǝ Sawul andǝ lagga male a ndà-ramba sǝ kya tsǝia à do a ban mǝɓoarne aɓalǝ aɓwana mǝnana à tunǝia, mǝnana làkkì malea na kǝla lumi-tàrú ka.  
\v 23 Sǝ Samuyila banggi mǝlamli ama, <<Yinǝàm nǝ kāmbe nyama mǝnana ǝn pô, mǝnana ǝn banggo nǝma wu tsǝi ɗàng ngga.>>  
\v 24 Nda mǝlamli twal byal nyama andǝ gir mǝnana amurí ka, sǝ tamsǝi a ɓadǝm Sawul. Sǝ Samuyila bang ama, <<Sǝnì, gìr mǝnana à tsǝì ka, nda à tamsǝo wi a ɓadǝmbo ka. Lì, acemǝnana à tsǝì aceo ace pwari mǝnia ka, twal a pwari mǝnana ǝn bang nǝma, <Mǝ ndanǝ abǝri mǝnana ǝn tunǝia ka.> >> Nda Sawul lìli atà Samuyila a pwari mǝno ka.  
\v 25 Sǝ lang à sùlǝ́nì ban-mǝdāhre sǝ à yina a nggea-là ka, à sárǝì Sawul kal-nongŋo\f + \fr 9:25 \fq à sárǝì Sawul kal-nongŋo;\ft ɓè gilǝe nǝ kún Ibǝru bang ama \fqa nacau nǝ Sawul. \f* a múr-kurǝm,\f + \fr 9:25 \fq múr-kurǝm \ft ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Nggur 22:8; 2Sam 11:2; 16:22; Nehe 8:16; Mat 24:17; Atúró 10:9\ft .\f* sǝ sarǝa nǝ̀ nong'ntullo.  
\v 26 Sǝ à lo ɗiɗyal, sǝ lang ban fana ka, Samuyila tunǝ Sawul a múr-kurǝm ama, <<Lo, ɓǝn pusǝbǝrio.>> Nda Sawul lo, sǝ yia kǝm, yì andǝ Samuyila ka, à pur amur njarɓala.  
\v 27 Lang à nda aban sulǝo à nǝ̀ ká a nzǝm-la ka, Samuyila banggi Sawul ama ɓǝ̀ banggi lagga male ɓǝ̀ kutio ɓǝ̀ fa a dǝmba. Sǝ lang kutina ka, Samuyila bang ama, <<Cam kani bǝti, ace mǝnana ɓǝn banggo cau mǝnana Ɓakuli bang ngga.>> 
\c 10  
\s1 À ɗārǝ́ Sawul duk murǝm 
\p  
\v 1 Pǝlǝa Samuyila twal du mùrú sǝ solǝi a ɓamur Sawul, kùrrì zǝp sǝ banggi wi ama, <<Yahweh ɗārǝo wu duk yalu amur aɓwana male Isǝrayila re?  
\v 2 Lang a nying banam yalung ngga, awu nǝ nggá je wunǝ aburana ɓari a ban ɓembe mala Rahila aɓa bù-nzali Benjami a Zelza; sǝ à nǝ̀ nô ama, <Amǝdambǝriso mǝnana a wari altea ka, à kumǝnia, sǝ ado ka, cau mala amǝdambǝriso na tárró nakiyice ɗǝm ngga ɗàng, a nda mǝnana bumi kǝ pi aceo, kǝ na ama, <<Mana mǝ nǝ pa ace munem le ka?>> >  
\v 3 Pǝlǝa awu nǝ lo a ban mǝno ka, awu nǝ lidǝmba aban ká sheɓǝ̀ a yina aban nggun mǝgule mala Tabo ka. Aɓwana tàrú mǝnana à nda njar aban ká [pà gir'nkila] aban Ɓakuli a Betel ka, à nǝ̀ kumǒ abanì, mwashat ka ndanǝ amuna-mbùl tàrú a buì, ɓè ka, ndanǝ agbatali bǝredi tàrú a buì, sǝ ɓè ka, ndanǝ bàng mùr-anap a buì.  
\v 4 À nǝ makkòkun sǝ à nǝ po gbatali bǝredi ɓari, mǝnana awu nǝ e a buia ka.  
\v 5 Anzǝm mǝno ka, awu nǝ ká a mǝ'nkono mala Ɓakuli a Gibiya, ban mǝnana ɓè kàttì mala amǝ'lwa mala amǝ'Filisti nakam ngga. Kutio mô aɓa nggea-là ka, awu nǝ je wunǝ nggǝsan mala amǝɓangnǝa aban súlǝì ban-mǝdāhre, nǝ amǝ'walki azangŋan, andǝ akarata-bu, andǝ adànà, andǝ amǝ'twanggi ankori aɓadǝmbia; sǝ à nǝ̀ nggǝ naki acau ɓangnǝa.  
\v 6 Pǝlǝa Bangŋo mala Yahweh nǝ̀ sulǝ amuro nǝ rǝcandǝa, sǝ awu nǝ nacau ɓangnǝa ateà, sǝ awu nǝ pǝlǝ ɓè ɓwa ɗàng.  
\v 7 Lang amǝnia yì agir-lǝmdǝa yi kumǒ ka, pàk gìr mǝnana buo kumo nǝ̀ pàk ka, acemǝnana Ɓakuli na atò.  
\v 8 Pǝlǝa awu nǝ akàmdǝmba ká a Gilgal. Sǝ sǝni, mǝ ndo mǝ nǝ sulǝ aban ká a bano ace pa agir'nkila mala pisǝe kǝring andǝ apagir mala dotarǝu ka. Awu nǝ twal anongŋo tongno-nong-ɓari aban kúndǝô, she ɓǝn yina a bano sǝ ǝn nano gìr mǝnana awu nǝ pàk ka.>> 
\p  
\v 9 Lang Sawul pǝlǝna nzǝmi nǝ̀ nying Samuyila ka, Ɓakuli pe wi, yì Sawul ɓè ɓabum. Sǝ amǝnia yì agir-lǝmdǝa ka, à yi lumsǝ kat a pwari mǝno.  
\v 10 Lang Sawul andǝ guro male yi bwalǝna Gibiya ka, kara nggǝsan mala amǝɓangnǝa yi kumi, sǝ Bangŋo mala Ɓakuli sulǝ amurí nǝ rǝcandǝa, sǝ nacau ɓangnǝ aɓalǝia.  
\v 11 Sǝ lang aɓwana mǝnana à súrǝì ɗiɗyal, sǝni aban nacau ɓangnǝa aɓalǝ amǝɓangnǝa ka, à ɗiki rǝia ama, <<Mana pur arǝ muna-ɓwabura mala Kish? Sawul gbal ka nda aɓalǝ amǝɓangnǝa le?>>  
\v 12 Sǝ ɓè ɓwabura mǝnana ndanǝdo abanì ka bang ama, <<Sǝ yana nda tárrià?>> Nda pǝlǝ caubangŋa ama, <<Sawul ka nda aɓalǝ amǝɓangnǝa gbal le?>>  
\v 13 Lang malǝna nacau ɓangnǝa ka, sǝ wari a ban-mǝdāhre. 
\p  
\v 14 Kina Sawul ɗì andǝ lagga male ama, <<A ke sǝ wu wario?>> Sǝ bang ama, <<A ban alta amǝdambǝriso. Sǝ lang sǝm kumia raka, sǝm wari aban Samuyila.>>  
\v 15 Pǝlǝa kina Sawul banggia wia ama, <<Ida, wu banggam cau mǝnana Samuyila bangga wun ngga.>>  
\v 16 Sǝ Sawul banggi kine ama, <<Bangga sǝm bwāng ama amǝdambǝriso ka, à kumǝnia.>> Sǝama amur cau mala domurǝm mǝnana Samuyila bang cè ka, banggi wi kǝ cau ɗàng. 
\s1 À hamnǝ cè duk murǝm mala Sawul 
\p  
\v 17 A bàkú mǝno ka, Samuyila tunǝ aɓwe abanɓwáná aban Yahweh a Mizǝpa.  
\v 18 Sǝ banggia amǝ Isǝrayila ama, <<Yahweh, Ɓakuli mala amǝ Isǝrayila bang ama, <Ən pusǝ wun Isǝrayila wu purî ɓá Masar, sǝ ǝn amsǝ wun a ɓabu amǝ'Masar sǝ a bu adomurǝm mǝnana kat à kǝ par wun aɓatea ka.>  
\v 19 Sǝama yalung ngga wu ginǝkina Ɓakuli ma'wun, mǝnana amsǝyi wun aɓalǝ agir'mur'mwana ma'wun andǝ agir'zunggǝliban ma'wun, sǝ wu bangŋǝ́nì wi ama, <Tsǝka sǝm murǝm amúr sǝm.> Acemani ado ka, wu lǝmdǝ rǝwun aɓadǝm Yahweh arǝ atau ma'wun, sǝ arǝ anggurkwar ma'wun.>> 
\p  
\v 20 Pǝlǝa Samuyila yinǝ atau mala Isǝrayila tù, sǝ à twal tau mala Benjami nǝ bwal-shishar.  
\v 21 Sǝ yinǝ tau mala Benjami tù arǝ anggurkwar male, sǝ à twal nggurkwar mala Matǝri nǝ bwal-shishar, sǝ à twal Sawul, muna-ɓwabura mala Kish nǝ bwal-shishar. Sǝ lang à sǝnbani ka, à kumi ɗàng.  
\v 22 Sǝ à ɗì Yahweh ɗǝm ama, <<Kǝɓwa na kam piu nǝ̀ yiu le?>> Sǝ Yahweh bang ama, <<Wu sǝni, nda sǝmbǝrǝ ɓamurì aɓalǝ atwalo ka.>>  
\v 23 Pǝlǝa à ɓangŋa à twali a banì. Sǝ lang cam aɓalǝ aɓwe ka, dāh'rya-kuti koyan kat aɓalǝ aɓwe, twal a nkpamtari aban o a kuli.  
\v 24 Sǝ Samuyila banggi aɓwe kat ama, <<Ɓwa mǝnana Yahweh twalo ɓǝ̀ duk murǝm amur wun ngga ndya ka. Aɓalǝ aɓwe kat ka, kǝ ɓwa pà kǝla yì ɗàng.>> Sǝ aɓwe kat loasǝ gia ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ yilǝmi murǝm sauwa!>> 
\p  
\v 25 Pǝlǝa Samuyila bǝli aɓwe agir mǝnana gulo-murǝm nǝ̀ tsǝia púp ɓǝà pè, andǝ amǝnana twàló na amúr murǝm nǝ̀ pè ka. Gilǝia aɓa nggú-gilǝgir sǝ nongsǝi aɓadǝm Yahweh. Pǝlǝa Samuyila mesǝ aɓwe ɓǝà o arǝ aɓala malea.  
\v 26 Sawul gbal ka, o a là male a Gibiya, sǝ akanggǝrang aburana mǝnana Ɓakuli je ɓabumia ka, à o atè.  
\v 27 Sǝama aɓea aɓwana mǝɓane bang ama, <<Làng sǝ ɓwa man nǝ̀ gandǝ amsǝ sǝm?>> À nyesǝce-ɓà, sǝ à ginǝ yinǝì nǝ kǝ ɓoro. Sǝama yi ka, kùr yinggǝli. 
\c 11  
\s1 Sawul lì amǝ'Amon a lwa 
\p  
\v 1 Nahash, ɓwa'Amon eauwe sǝ kya gumbǝli Jabesh-Gilǝyat, sǝ aburana mala amǝ Jabesh kat ne wi ama, <<Kùrcau nǝ sǝm sǝ sǝm nǝ̀ do aɓato.>>  
\v 2 Pǝlǝa Nahash ɓwa'Amon ear ama, <<Mǝ nǝ kùrcau nǝ wun amur cau mwashat, ama mǝ nǝ pusǝki amǝsǝ wun mǝli kat, sǝ anggo ka, nǝ̀ yinǝ kirsakya amur Isǝrayila kat.>>  
\v 3 Aɓwana-mǝgule mala amǝ Jabesh ne wi ama, <<Nyingga sǝm anongŋo tongno-nong-ɓari ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ sǝm tasǝ amǝ'na-túrbân arǝ alá mala amǝ Isǝrayila kat. Ɓǝ̀ kǝɓwa pà kàm nǝ̀ amsǝ sǝm raka, sǝ sǝm nǝ̀ pà ɓamur rǝ sǝm aɓato.>>  
\v 4 Lang amǝ'na-túrbân bwalna Gibiya là mala Sawul ka, à kya ne aɓwana cê à kiria, sǝ yia kat ka, à túr kunia a ɓua. 
\p  
\v 5 Kara à sǝn Sawul kǝ nyarî ɓaban aban gya atà andá-rya. Sǝ Sawul ɗiban ama, <<Mana kum aɓwe sǝ à kǝ ɓua?>> Pǝlǝa à ne wi cau mala aburana mala amǝ Jabesh.  
\v 6 Lang Sawul okcau malea ka, kara Bangŋo mala Ɓakuli sulǝ amurí nǝ rǝcandǝa, sǝ bumlulla male earki-bǝsa kǝ̀rkǝ́r.  
\v 7 Twal andá-rya ɓari, kasǝkia nyak-nyak sǝ turaban nǝia aɓa nzong-nzali Isǝrayila ɗǝɗak nǝ bù amǝ'na-túrbân ama, <<Ɓwa mǝnana kat puro yiu atà Sawul andǝ Samuyila raka, anggo sǝ à nǝ̀ pàkkî andá-rya male.>> Pǝlǝa ɓangciu mala Yahweh bwal amǝ Isǝrayila, sǝ à puro kǝla ɓwa mwashat.  
\v 8 Lang Sawul rambia a Bezek ka, làkkì mala amǝ Isǝrayila na á-gbǝman-tàrú (300,000) sǝ amǝ Yahuda ka à nda á-lumi-tàrú (30,000.)  
\v 9 Sǝ à ne amǝ'na-túrbân mana à yiu ka ama, <<Ani sǝ wun nǝ̀ ne amǝ Jabesh-Gilǝyat: <Li ɓǝ̀ pwari zǝkina ka, wun nǝ̀ kum amsǝban ma'wun.> >> Lang amǝ'na-túrbân yiu sǝ à banggi aburana mala Jabesh ka, banɓoaria wia.  
\v 10 Acemani ka, aburana mala Jabesh banggi Nahash ama, <<Li ka, sǝm nǝ̀ pur aban wun, sǝ wun nǝ̀ gandǝ pakka sǝm gìr mǝnana kat wu sǝni nda ɓoara wun ngga.>>  
\v 11 Sǝ lang ban fana ka, Sawul gau aɓwe arǝ anggǝsan tàrú; sǝ à yi ar aɓa tsùrú mala kàttì mala amǝ'Amon nǝ ban mbul-mbul, sǝ à camarǝ wal amǝ'Amon ba zǝkya mala pwari. Aɓwana mǝnana à au ka à mesǝkì tàrǝia, yale à kum aɓwana ɓari atārǝia ɗàng. 
\p  
\v 12 Pǝlǝa aburana mala amǝ Isǝrayila ne Samuyila ama, <<Ya ɓwe na bang ama <Sawul nǝ̀ duk murǝm amur sǝm le ka?> Wu yinǝ aɓwe, ɓǝ̀ sǝm wal-luia.>>  
\v 13 Sǝama Sawul bang ama, <<À pà nǝ̀ wal-lú kǝɓwa a pwari mǝnia ka ɗàng, acemǝnana yalung ngga, Yahweh yina nǝ amsǝban a Isǝrayila.>>  
\v 14 Pǝlǝa Samuyila ne aɓwana ama, <<Wu yiu, sǝm nǝ̀ o a Gilgal, sǝm nǝ̀ nggá basǝ domurǝm kano.>>  
\v 15 Osso aɓwe kat wari a Gilgal, akano sǝ à dumsǝ Sawul à murǝm aɓadǝm Yahweh a Gilgal. Akano sǝ à pà gir'nkila mala dorǝpwala aɓadǝm Yahweh, sǝ akano sǝ Sawul andǝ aburana mala amǝ Isǝrayila kat pàk-banɓoarnado kǝ̀rkǝ́r. 
\c 12  
\s1 Nacau tsǝkban-andà mala Samuyila 
\p  
\v 1 Pǝlǝa Samuyila banggi Isǝrayila kat ama, <<Wu sǝni, ǝn kpanata gì wun aɓalǝ agir mǝnana kat wu nam ngga, sǝ ǝn tsǝ́ngŋǝ̀nà wun murǝm amur wun.  
\v 2 Sǝ adyan ngga, wu ndanǝ murǝm, mǝnana nda mǝdǝmba ma'wun ngga. Sǝ mim adyan ngga, ǝn ena, nǝ mbù amuram; sǝ amuna-burana mem ngga, á nda atà wun. Mim ngga, ǝn duk mǝdǝmba ma'wun, twal a lo-ɓwa mem, ba yalung. 
\p  
\v 3 <<Mǝ ndya ǝn cam ngga, wu nakun amuram aɓadǝm Yahweh sǝ ɓadǝm ɓwa male mana twali nda murǝm ngga. Jamnda mala yani ǝn twali? Ko mǝdambǝriso mala yani na, mana ǝn twali ka? Ko yana, mǝnana ǝn ɓǝmbǝri ka? Sǝ yana, mǝnana ǝn pari ka? Ko a bù yan sǝ ǝn ak pàbunǝnzali, mana gìrki amǝsǝam ngga? Ɓǝ̀ ndakam ama ǝn pak mwashat atà agir mǝnia ka, mǝ nǝ nyesǝa wuni.>> 
\p  
\v 4 Pǝlǝa aɓwe pa eare ama, <<Awo, a ɓǝmbǝri ma, ko a par ma sǝm, ko a ak ma kǝgir a bù kǝɓwa ɗàng.>> 
\p  
\v 5 Pǝlǝa Samuyila banggia wia ama, <<Yahweh ka, nda mǝ'nakún amur gir mǝnana wu pàk ka; anggo gbal, murǝm mǝnana Yahweh twal ka, dumǝna mǝ'nakún yalung, ama, wu kum ɓè kǝgir a buam ɗàng.>> Pǝlǝa à ear ama, <<Yahweh nda mǝ'nakún.>> 
\p  
\v 6 Pǝlǝa Samuyila banggi aɓwe ama, <<Yahweh nda mǝnana twal Musa andǝ Haruna, sǝ pusǝ aká wun à purî ɓá nzali Masar ka.  
\v 7 Acemani ka, wu cam piu, sǝ mǝ nǝ kútí a ɓashi sǝnǝa wun aɓadǝm Yahweh, amur ɓealɓoarna mala Yahweh mǝnana pàkka wunia, sǝ pàkkî aká wun ngga.  
\v 8 Lang Yakupu wari a Masar, sǝ aká wun wari nǝ ɓua malea aban Yahweh ka, Yahweh tasǝ Musa andǝ Haruna, mǝnana à pusǝ aká wun à purî ɓá Masar, sǝ tsǝia à yi do a mǝnia yì ban ngga. 
\p  
\v 9 <<Sǝama, à lorǝ Yahweh, Ɓakuli malea; nda sǝ Yahweh mea a ɓabu Sǝsera,\f + \fr 12:9 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Akas 4:1-2\ft .\f* yì mǝ'sàrǝ̀ban amur amǝ'lwa mala Hazo, sǝ a ɓabu amǝ'Filisti, sǝ a ɓabu murǝm mala Mowap. Sǝ à munǝ-munǝo arǝia.  
\v 10 Pǝlǝa à ɓua aban Yahweh, aban na ama, <Sǝm pàngŋǝ̀nà cauɓikea acemǝnana sǝm nying Yahweh, sǝm kpanata aBa'al andǝ Ashtarot ka. Sǝama adyan ngga, amsǝ sǝm a bù aɓisǝm amǝbura, sǝ sǝm nǝ̀ kpato.>  
\v 11 Pǝlǝa Yahweh tasǝ Jerub-ba'al, andǝ Barak, andǝ Jefta andǝ Samuyila, sǝ amsǝ wun, ak wun a ɓabu aɓiwun amǝbura mana à do, à kàrì wun a ɓalǝu ka; nda gìr mǝnana tsǝa sǝ wu duk jam ngga. 
\p  
\v 12 <<Sǝ lang wu sǝn Nahash, murǝm mala amǝ'Amon, nǝ̀ nggǝ yiu nǝ munǝo arǝ wun ngga, nda wu banggam ama, <Awo, sǝm nggǝ earce murǝm ɓǝ̀ yálmúr sǝm,> kat andǝ amani ama, Yahweh Ɓakuli ma'wun, nda murǝm ma'wun ngga.  
\v 13 Sǝ adyan ngga, murǝm ma'wun mana wu twal ka, ndya ka, yì mana wu zǝmbace ka. Wu sǝni, Yahweh ka, tsǝ̀ngŋǝ̀nà murǝm amur wun.  
\v 14 Ɓǝ̀ wun nǝ̀ ɓanggi Yahweh, sǝ wun nǝ̀ kpate, wun nǝ̀ oki wi, sǝ pà wu nǝ̀ mgbicau arǝ nzongcau mala Yahweh raka, ɓǝ̀ wun sǝ murǝm mana yálkiyi múr wun, wunia kat, wun nǝ̀ kpata Yahweh, Ɓakuli ma'wun ngga, gir mǝɓoarne na!  
\v 15 Sǝama, ɓǝ̀ pa wun nǝ̀ okî Yahweh ɗàng, gandǝa wun nǝ̀ mgbicau, pà wun nǝ̀ kpata anzongcau mala Yahweh raka, bù Yahweh nǝ̀ pǝlǝa arǝ wun, kǝla mana buì pǝlǝa arǝ aká wun ngga. 
\p  
\v 16 <<Ado ka, wu cam piu, wu sǝn mǝnia yì gìr mǝgule, mǝnana Yahweh nǝ̀ pè a ɓamǝsǝ wun ngga!  
\v 17 Kún pwan mǝssa-alkama na ado re? Mǝ nǝ nacau nǝ Yahweh, ɓǝ̀ tasǝ sàkkya mala mgbarangce andǝ mbulo. Sǝ wun nǝ̀ sǝlǝa, wun nǝ̀ sǝni ama ɓealɓikea ma'wun mǝnana wu pè a mǝsǝ Yahweh, nǝ zǝmba ama ɓǝ̀ pa wun murǝm ngga, mǝgule na.>> 
\p  
\v 18 Pǝlǝa Samuyila zǝmbi Yahweh, sǝ a kǝ pwari mǝno ka, Yahweh tasǝ sàkkya mala mgbarangce andǝ mbulo. Nda aɓwana kat ɓanggi Yahweh andǝ Samuyila kǝ̀rkǝ́r ka. 
\p  
\v 19 Pǝlǝa aɓwana kat banggi Samuyila ama, <<Pakhiwi aban Yahweh, Ɓakuli mò, ace aguro mò, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ sǝm nggá wu ɗàng; sǝm tsǝ̀ngŋǝ̀nà ɓè cauɓikea amur amǝnana sǝm peǎ ka, nǝ zǝmbace murǝm ace ɓamur rǝ sǝm.>>  
\v 20 Sǝ Samuyila ear ama, <<Ɓangciu ɓǝ̀ kǝa pakka wun ɗàng. Mǝsǝcau na ama wu pàngŋǝ̀nà mǝnia yì ɓealɓikea kat ka; sǝama, wu kǝa pǝlǝ nzǝm wun arǝ Yahweh ɗàng, wu kpate nǝ ɓabum wun kat.  
\v 21 Wu kǝa nyar aban kpata \f + \fr 12:21 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Ir 16:19; Hab 2:18; 1Kor 8:4\ft .\f*agirɓana mǝnana à pà nǝ̀ pusǝ wun, ko à nǝ̀ amsǝ wun raka ɗàng, acemǝnana à nda ɓà.  
\v 22 Yahweh ka, pà nǝ̀ túr nzǝm aɓwana male ɗàng, atàcau mala lùllǝì mǝgule. Acemǝnana Yahweh ka, bumi kǝ pwasǝ arǝ nyesǝ wun, ɓǝ̀ wu duk aɓwana male.  
\v 23 Amur mǝno ka, ɓǝ̀ sappi banam, mǝnana ama mǝ nǝ pàkkî Yahweh cauɓikea nǝ tamsǝ pakhiwi ace wun ngga. Sǝama, mǝ nǝ nggǝ kània wun njar mǝnana ɓoaro, sǝ nda pepè ka.  
\v 24 Sǝ a dǝmba nǝ koman kat ka, wu ɓanggi Yahweh, sǝ wu kpate nǝ ɓabum wun mwashat andǝ mǝsǝcau. Wu ɗenyinǝ agir mǝgulke mǝnana peǎ ace wun ngga. 
\p  
\v 25 <<Sǝama, ɓǝ̀ wu lidǝmba nǝ pak ɓealɓikea ka, wun, wunǝa murǝm ma'wun ngga, wun nǝ̀ kìɗikì.>> 
\c 13  
\s1 Amǝ'Isǝrayila munǝ andǝ amǝ'Filisti 
\p  
\v 1 Sawul ndanǝ apǝlǝa lumi-tàrú lang duk murǝm ngga, sǝ yálmúr amǝ'Isǝrayila mala apǝlǝa lumi-ine-nong-ɓari.  
\v 2 Sawul tàr aburana á-tàrú (3,000) mala Isǝrayila; á-ɓari (2,000) aɓalǝia ka, à nda atè a Mikmash andǝ nzali múr ankono mala Betel, sǝ á-mwashat ka, à nda atà Jonatan a Gibiya, a bù-nzali mala Benjami. Sǝ acili aɓwe (1,000) ka, nyesǝia ɓǝà o a là, koyan ngga a ɓala male. 
\p  
\v 3 Jonatan gandǝ kàttì\f + \fr 13:3 \fq gandǝ kàttì \ft ko \fqa wal-lú mǝ'sàrǝ̀ban\f*\f + \fr 13:3 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt 1Sam 10:5\ft .\f* mala amǝ'lwa mala amǝ'Filisti mǝnana a Geba ka, sǝ amǝ'Filisti ok cè. Pǝlǝa Sawul twang njawe aɓa nzali kat ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ amǝ'Ibǝru ǒ.>>  
\v 4 Sǝ Isǝrayila kat oè à bangŋi ama Sawul gandǝna kàttì mala amǝ'Filisti, sǝ ɗǝm ngga ama Isǝrayila pǝlǝna gìr mǝnana à nǝ̀ ɓinǝì ka aban amǝ'Filisti. Nda aɓwana ok tunǝbanì sǝ à puro à kya kpapi ɓamuria atà Sawul a Gilgal ka. 
\p  
\v 5 Amǝ'Filisti ram rǝia ace kánǝ munǝo arǝ amǝ'Isǝrayila; à ndanǝ awaru-pǝr á-lumi-tàrú (30,000), amǝ'pǝ̀r á-tongno-nong-mwashat (6,000), sǝ anggǝsan mala amǝ'lwa mǝ'làkke kǝla lakkì mala mǝsǝsala a kún nggeamùr. À eauwe sǝ à yi tsǝk kàttì malea a Mikmash nǝ takuli mala Bet-Aven  
\v 6 Lang amǝ Isǝrayila sǝni ama tanni na amúrià, sǝ amǝ'lwa malea na aɓa nggikiban mǝcandǝe ka, à kya sǝmbǝrǝki rǝia aɓalǝ agumi andǝ akarwan, andǝ ɓong ankono, andǝ ɓalǝ afouroban a tà-nzali, andǝ ɓalǝ a'imna tūli-mùr.  
\v 7 Aɓea aɓwana atà amǝ'Ibǝru ka, à yàl a nkaring Nggeasala Jodan aban ká bu-nzali mala Gad andǝ Gilǝyat. Sǝ Sawul ka nda piu a Gilgal; amǝ'lwa puppup mǝnana atè ka, rǝia kǝ ɓǝla nǝ ɓangciu. 
\p  
\v 8 Sawul twal anongŋo tongno-nong-ɓari, ndaban kúndǝô a Gilgal, kǝla mǝnana Samuyila tsǝki wi ka, sǝ Samuyila yiu ɗàng. Aɓwana tita mesǝ arǝ Sawul.  
\v 9 Nda Sawul bang ama, <<Wu yinǝam nǝ pàgir mala pisǝe kǝring andǝ apagir mala dotarǝu.>> Pǝlǝa Sawul pà gir'nkila mala pisǝe kǝring.  
\v 10 Sǝ lang Sawul nǝ̀ mal pà gir'nkila mala pisǝe kǝring ani ka, kara Samuyila yi tusǝo. Sawul puro wario nǝ nggá kumi sǝ nǝ̀ gingsǝi.  
\v 11 Sǝ Samuyila ɗì ama, <<Mana a pa?>> Sawul eari wi ama, <<Lang ǝn sǝni aɓwe na arǝ mǝsǝ arǝàm, sǝ a yiu aɓalǝ anonggio mǝnana a tsǝa ama awu nǝ yiu nǝi raka, sǝ ɗǝm ngga amǝ'Filisti ramǝna rǝia a Mikmash ka,  
\v 12 nda ǝn bang nǝma, <Amǝ'Filisti na à nǝ̀ sulǝ aban yiu arǝàm nǝ munǝo kani a Gilgal, sǝ ǝn malaká zǝm earmúrú aban Yahweh ɗàng.> Acemani ka, ǝn tsǝk ɓamúràm púp ǝn pà gir'nkila mala pisǝe kǝring.>> 
\p  
\v 13 Samuyila banggi wi ama, <<A pángŋǝ̀nà ɓwaɓana. A kpata nzongcau mǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli mô tsǝko ka ɗàng. Ɓǝ̀ a kpanatà nzongcau mala Yahweh mǝni ka, ɓǝ́ Yahweh nǝ̀ tamsǝkusǝ domurǝm mò amur Isǝrayila tàtǝ́k!\f + \fr 13:13 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt 1Sam 15:11\ft .\f* 
\v 14 Sǝama adyan ngga, domurǝm mò pà nǝ̀ lidǝmba ɗàng. Yahweh alǝnata ɓwa mǝnana ndanǝ ulang ɓabum male ka, sǝ tsǝ̀ngŋǝ́nì wi nzongcau ɓǝ̀ yálmúr aɓwana male, acemǝnana a kpata nzongcau mala Yahweh ɗàng.>>\f + \fr 13:14 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Atúró 13:22\ft .\f* 
\p  
\v 15 Pǝlǝa Samuyila loapi Gilgal ka, wari a Gibiya a bu-nzali Benjami, sǝ acili aɓwana ka, à o atà Sawul ace kpapi ɓamuria andǝ amǝ'lwa. À loapi Gilgal ka, à wari a Gibiya a bu-nzali Benjami. Pǝlǝa Sawul ram aɓwana mǝnana à nda atè piu ka, sǝ ɓallia. Làkkì malea na kǝla gbǝman-tongno-nong-mwashat.  
\v 16 Sawul, andǝ muna-ɓwabura male Jonatan, andǝ amǝ'lwa mǝnana à nda atè ka, à ue a Geba a bu-nzali mala Benjami; sǝ amǝ'Filisti ka à tsǝk kàttì malea a Mikmash.  
\v 17 Pǝlǝa amǝ'tǝllìban purì ɓá kàttì mala amǝ'Filisti arǝ anggǝsan tàrú. Nggǝsan mwashat ka, pǝlǝ nǝ Ofǝra, aban ká a bu-nzali Shuwal;  
\v 18 ɓè nggǝsan dǝshi Bet-Horon; sǝ ɓè nggǝsan ngga pǝlǝ nǝ nzong-nzali mǝnana kǝ sǝn ɓamǝsǝarǝia andǝ Ɓangŋaban mala Zeboyim andǝ ɓabondo ka. 
\p  
\v 19 A bàkú mǝno ka, à kum kǝ mǝ'ntùl aɓa nzali Isǝrayila kat ɗàng, acemǝnana amǝ'Filisti bangŋǝna ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ ana raka amǝ'Ibǝru nǝ̀ pàkkî ɓamuria anggeabyau andǝ ankongŋo.>>  
\v 20 Nda koyan a Isǝrayila ka kǝ wari aban amǝ'Filisti ace kolǝ kún soro-gwam-nzali, andǝ adá, andǝ bero, andǝ nshiri male.  
\v 21 À mbwe gauwe ɓari aɓa tàrú mala shekel\f + \fr 13:21 \fq gauwe ɓari aɓa tàrú mala shekel \ft ko mǝsǝ bolo-azǝrfa ɓari.\f* ace kolǝ kún asoro-gwam-nzali, andǝa adá, sǝ à mbwe mwashat aɓa gauwe tàrú mala shekel ace kolǝ kún abero, andǝ kún agir pǝ̀r anda-rya.  
\v 22 Acemani ka, a pwari mala munǝo ka, à kum nggeabyau andǝ nzo a bú kǝɓwa aɓalǝ amǝ'lwa mǝnana à nda atà Sawul andǝ Jonatan ngga ɗàng; sǝama Sawul andǝ muna-ɓwabura male Jonatan ngga, à ndanǝia.  
\v 23 Amǝ'Filisti tasǝ ɓè nggǝsan mala amǝ'lwa malea ace yál njar nre ka ankono mala Mikmash. 
\c 14  
\s1 Jonatan gandǝ amǝ'Filisti nǝ munǝo 
\p  
\v 1 Ɓè pwari ka Jonatan, muna-ɓwabura mala Sawul banggi mǝ-bwali-wi agirmunǝo male ama, <<Yiu ɓǝ̀ sǝm yàl aban ká a kàttì mala amǝ'Filisti mǝnana a nkaring ngga.>> Sǝama yì ka ne tárrí ɗàng. 
\p  
\v 2 Sawul ka, nda a gumli male a tǝrta nggun mɓǝring a Migǝron, anzǝm là Gibiya. Amǝ'lwa mǝnana à nda atè ka, à nda kǝla ɓwa gbǝman-tongno-nong-mwashat (600).  
\v 3 Ahija muna-ɓwabura mala Ahitup, mǝ'eam Ikabod, muna-ɓwabura mala Finehas, mǝkà Eli, yì pǝris mala Yahweh a Shilo ka, ndakam ateà nǝ efot, \f + \fr 14:3 \fq a buì \ft ko \fqa arǝì\f*a buì. Aɓwana sǝlǝ ama Jonatan umǝna ɗàng. 
\p  
\v 4 Nreban mǝnana Jonatan nǝ kùtí kam aban ká a kàttì mala amǝ'Filisti ka, atali mǝ'dāh'rike nakam a koya nkanggari. Ɓè talî ka, à tunǝi ama Bozez, sǝ ɓè man ngga à tunǝi ama Sene.  
\v 5 Tali mǝ'dāhre mana nǝ njar-nza ka, nda aɓadǝm Mikmash, sǝ mǝnana nǝ njar-kunmur ka, nda aɓadǝm Geba. 
\p  
\v 6 Jonatan banggi mǝ-bwali-wi agirmunǝo male ama, <<Yiu, ɓǝ̀ sǝm yàl aban ká a kàttì mala amǝ'ɗwanyi-kasǝ-ɓatau man. Earka Yahweh nǝ̀ pàktúró ace sǝm; kǝgir pà kàm nǝ̀ tamsǝ Yahweh arǝ amsǝban, ko nǝ aɓwana pas ko nǝ aɓwana kpokyak ɗàng.>>  
\v 7 Mǝ-bwali-wi agirmunǝo male ne wi ama, <<Pàk gìr mǝnana nda a ɓabumo ka. Kyane, sǝ sǝni, mǝ nda atò, kǝla mǝnana ɓabumo twali ka.>>  
\v 8 Jonatan banggi wi ama, <<Sǝni, sǝm nǝ̀ yàlé ace ká a ban amǝ'Filisti, sǝ sǝm nǝ̀ pusǝ rǝ sǝm ɓǝà sǝn sǝm.  
\v 9 Ɓǝ̀ à bangga sǝm ama, <Wu kúndǝô sheɓǝ̀ sǝm yina aban wun ngga,> pǝlǝa sǝm nǝ̀ cam pikǝr abanì, pà sǝm nǝ̀ ká abania ɗàng.  
\v 10 Sǝama ɓǝ̀ à bangga sǝm ama, <Wu yiu aban sǝm ngga,> pǝlǝa sǝm nǝ̀ ká, acemǝnana Yahweh pània a ɓabù sǝm. Mǝno ka nda gìr'lǝmdǝa aban sǝm ama Yahweh pània a ɓabù sǝm.>> 
\p  
\v 11 Lang à lǝmdǝ ɓamuria yià kǝm aban amǝ'lwa a kàttì mala amǝ'Filisti ka, amǝ'Filisti bang ama, <<Wu sǝni, amǝ'Ibǝru nako à kǝ purki aɓalǝ atūli mǝnana à sǝmbǝrǝki kam ngga.>>  
\v 12 Pǝlǝa à tunǝ Jonatan andǝ mǝ-bwali-wi agirmunǝo ama, <<Wu yiu kani, sǝm nǝ̀ lǝmdǝa wun gìr arǝ wun.>> Pǝlǝa Jonatan ne mǝ-bwali-wi agirmunǝo ama, <<Yiu atàm. Yahweh túrnia a ɓabù Isǝrayila.>>  
\v 13 Pǝlǝa Jonatan kundǝkio amur abui andǝ akusǝi, eau aban ká aban amǝ'Filisti, sǝ mǝ-bwali-wi agirmunǝo ka nda atè. Jonatan wal-lú amǝ'Filisti mǝnana à nda aɓadǝmbi ka, sǝ mǝ-bwali-wi agirmunǝo gbal ka, wal-lú amana àkǝ yiu nǝ nzǝmia ka.  
\v 14 Aɓa je-munǝo mǝdǝmbe man ngga, Jonatan andǝ mǝ-bwali-wi agirmunǝo wal-lú aburana kǝla lumi-ɓari, a patal mǝnana tangŋa male na kǝla mita lumi-ɓari ka. 
\p  
\v 15 Sǝ ɓangciu bwal amǝ'Filisti mǝnana kat à nda a kàttì ka, andǝ amǝnana à nda a patal ka, andǝ amǝ'lwa malea mǝnana kat à tamsǝia ace yalban ngga, andǝ anggǝsan mala amǝ'tǝllìban; rǝia ɓǝla atàcau mala ɓangciu, sǝ nzali gǝggǝli. Mǝnia yì ɓangciu ka pur nǝban Ɓakuli. 
\p  
\v 16 Amǝ'yalban mala Sawul a Gibiya, a bu-nzali Benjami soa-mǝsǝia, sǝ à sǝni ka, ɓwabundǝa mala amǝ'lwa mala amǝ'Filisti na aban mesǝki arǝ abuban ɗàngɗáng.  
\v 17 Pǝlǝa Sawul banggi aɓwana mǝnana à nda atè ka ama, <<Wu ɓal amǝ'lwa ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ sǝm súrǝ̀ ɓwa mǝnana pa kani raka.>> Lang à ɓalkiban ngga, Jonatan andǝ mǝ-bwali-wi agirmunǝo male ka à pà abanì ɗàng.  
\v 18 Osso Sawul ne Ahija ama, <<Yinǝ Akwati Kùrcau mala Ɓakuli kani.>> A pwari mǝno ka, Akwati Kùrcau mala Ɓakuli ka, nda aban amǝ'Isǝrayila.\f + \fr 14:18 \fq <<Yinǝ Akwati Kùrcau mala Ɓakuli kani.>> A pwari mǝno ka, Akwati Kùrcau mala Ɓakuli ka, nda aban amǝ'Isǝrayila. \ft Ko \fqa Osso Sawul ne Ahija ama, <<Yinǝ efot, ace ɗibancau aban Ɓakuli amur gìr mǝnana sǝm nǝ̀ pàk.>> A pwari mǝno ka, Ahija oasǝna efot arǝì, sǝ nda aban came aɓadǝm amǝ'Isǝrayila. \f* 
\v 19 Lang Sawul na aban nacau nǝ pǝris ka, zùrǝì mǝnana aɓa kàttì mala amǝ'Filisti ka lidǝmba arǝ gulkio. Nda Sawul ne pǝris ama, <<Nying buo.>>\f + \fr 14:19 \fq <<Nying buo.>> \ft Ko \fq <<Nying buo\ft  arǝ efot (\xt Pur 28:6-30\ft .) Kǝa lidǝmba nǝ jeki amǝsǝtali-gǝna mǝnana arǝ efot, yì muna daura-múrɓì mǝfele mala Pǝris Mǝgule ka, ace súrǝ̀ nê mala Ɓakuli ɗàng.>> \f* 
\p  
\v 20 Pǝlǝa Sawul andǝ amǝ'lwa mǝnana kat à nda atè ka ramba abanɓwáná, sǝ à pur ace munǝo. \f + \fr 14:20 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Akas 7:22; 2Kpa 20:23\ft .\f*À kya kum amǝ'Filisti aɓa zùrǝì mǝgule, aban wal-lú rǝarǝia nǝ anggeabyau malea.  
\v 21 Amǝ'Ibǝru mǝnana à sanna à o atà amǝ'Filisti a kàttì malea ɗiɗyal ka, à nyare à yi kpapi ɓamúrià atà amǝ'Isǝrayila mǝnana à nda atà Sawul andǝ Jonatan ngga.  
\v 22 Lang amǝ'Isǝrayila mǝnana à sǝmbǝrǝki rǝia aɓa nzali múr ankono mala Ifǝrem ok ama amǝ'Filisti ɓangŋǝna ka, yìa gbal ka à lo pǝrtea nǝ munǝo.  
\v 23 Nda Yahweh amsǝ Isǝrayila a pwari mǝno, sǝ munǝo mesǝe kya kúti aban ká dǝmba nǝ Bet-Aven. 
\p  
\v 24 Amǝ'Isǝrayila kùtí aɓa gandǝrǝu a pwari mǝno ka, acemǝnana Sawul tsǝ̀ngŋǝ̀nà aɓwe aɓata kángìr ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ suban sulǝ amur ɓwa mǝnana lì girlina yalung bà pwarikpǝra ka, she ɓǝ̀n mbwena aɓiam-mǝbura akúnì ka.>>Acemani ka, kǝ ɓwa ateà tsǝk kǝ girlina a kúní ɗàng.  
\v 25 Lang amǝ'lwa puppup yiu aɓa ɓè ndà-nggun ngga, à kum mur-nyi kàm arǝ abân amur nzali.  
\v 26 Sǝ lang à kùtí aɓalǝ anggunì ka, à sǝn mur-nyi aban surkio, sǝ kǝɓwa lǝmdǝ buì je ama nǝ̀ kánǝi a kúni ɗàng, acemǝnana aɓwana ɓanggi súbanì. 
\p  
\v 27 Jonatan ngga, ok cau mala kángir mǝnana tárrí tsǝk aɓwana à kán ngga ɗàng. Acemani ka, lǝmdǝ kún gara male mana a buì ka, oasǝi aɓa ntòngŋò-nyì, ɗàrǝ́ mur-nyi sǝ lì. Anzǝm mana lìnì ka, kum bǝsa rǝcandǝa.  
\v 28 Pǝlǝa ɓeɓwa atà amǝ'lwa banggi wi ama, <<Tárró tsǝk amǝ'lwa à kángìr nǝ nggea kána mǝcandǝe ama, <Ɓǝ̀ suban sulǝ amur ɓwa mǝnana lì girlina aɓa pwari man yalung ngga.> Nda gìr mǝnana tsǝa sǝ amǝ'lwa yauwiki nǝ nzala ka.>>  
\v 29 Jonatan ne wi ama, <<Tárrám tsǝ̀ngŋǝ̀nà aɓwana aɓa tanni. Ida, wu sǝn rǝcandǝa mǝno nyar arǝàm atàcau mala mur-nyi mǝnia bǝti ǝn oê a kunam ngga.  
\v 30 Ɓǝ́ gìrnî ɓoarna kutini man ɓǝ̀ amǝ'lwa lina gìr mǝnana nǝ̀ karǝia yalung aɓa girlina mana à kum aɓalǝ agǝna-lwa mala aɓia-mǝbura ka. Ɓǝ́ alú mǝnana à wal atà amǝ'Filisti ka kutini man.>> 
\p  
\v 31 A pwari mǝno ka, amǝ'Isǝrayila wal amǝ'Filisti tite a Mikmash kya pur a Aijalon. Sǝ à yauwiki kǝ̀rkǝ́r nǝ nzala.  
\v 32 Nda amǝ'lwa fàkìfákya amúr gǝna-lwa, sǝ à bwalki anzur, andǝ andá, andǝ amuna-ndá, à pwangi-myalia akǝ banì sǝ à \f + \fr 14:32 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Pǝris 3:17\ft .\f*shak nyamia andǝapwale.  
\v 33 Pǝlǝa ɓeɓwa banggi Sawul ama, <<Sǝni, aɓwana nia à kǝ̀ pàkkî Yahweh cauɓikea nǝ shak nyama nǝ nkila arǝì ka.>> Sǝ Sawul na ama, <<Wun kat wu lǝmdǝna ɗwanyi domǝsǝcau; wu ɗǝnggǝliki tali mǝgule kani abanam.>>  
\v 34 Pǝlǝa nea wia ama, <<Wu mesǝ aɓalǝ aɓwana, wu banggia wia ama, <Koyan atà wun ngga, wu yinǝàmnǝ andá andǝ anzur ma'wun kani. Wu pwangi-myalia kani sǝ wu shea; sǝama wu kǝa pàkkî Yahweh cauɓikea nǝ shak nyama nǝ nkila arǝì ɗàng.> >> Nda yià kat à yinǝ andá andǝ anzur malea a buia nǝ dù mǝno, sǝ à pwangi-myalia abanì. 
\p  
\v 35 Pǝlǝa Sawul ɓakkî Yahweh gyangŋan. Mǝnia ka nda gyangŋan mǝdǝmbe mana ɓakkî Yahweh ka. 
\p  
\v 36 Pǝlǝa Sawul banggi amǝ'lwa male ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ sǝm kya loasǝtà amǝ'Filisti nǝ du sǝ ɓǝ̀ sǝm pwan gǝna-lwa ba kwaro mala bân; ɓǝ̀ sǝm wal-luia kat.>> Pǝlǝa à eari wi ama, <<Pàk gìr mǝnana a sǝni nda ɓoaro kutibanì ka.>> Sǝama pǝris ne wi ama, <<Came ɓǝ̀ sǝm ɗì Yahweh peatu.>> 
\p  
\v 37 Nda Sawul ɗì Ɓakuli ama, <<Mǝ kyan nǝ munǝo arǝ amǝ'Filisti le? Awu nǝ túriá a ɓabu Isǝrayila le?>> Sǝama Ɓakuli pe wi eare a pwari mǝno ka ɗàng.  
\v 38 Pǝlǝa Sawul banggi amúrû mala amǝ'lwa ama, <<Wu yiu kani kat, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ sǝm súrǝ̀ cauɓikea mǝnana à pè yalung ngga.  
\v 39 Mbak-kàngkàng Yahweh, mǝ'akmúr Isǝrayila nakam ngga, ɓwa mǝnana kat à kumi nǝ cau ka, dumǝna púp nǝ̀ wú, ko ɓǝ̀ muna-ɓwabura mem Jonatan na ka.>> Sǝama kǝɓwa atà aɓwana kat na kǝ cau ɗàng.  
\v 40 Pǝlǝa Sawul banggi amǝ'Isǝrayila ama, <<Wun kat ka, wu cam kanó sǝ mim sǝnǝ Jonatan ngga, sǝm nǝ̀ cam kani.>> À eari wi ama, <<Pàk gìr mǝnana a sǝni nda ɓoarô ka.>>  
\v 41 Pǝlǝa Sawul na ama, <<We Yahweh, Ɓakuli mala Isǝrayila, palang sǝ a pè guro mò eare yalung ɗàng? \f + \fr 14:41 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Ɓal 27:21; 1Sam 28:6\ft .\f*Ɓǝ̀ mim ko muna-ɓwabura mem Jonatan, nda mǝnana pàk man yì cauɓikea ka, pa eare nǝ Urim; sǝ ɓǝ̀ aɓwana mô, amǝ'Isǝrayila na à pàk man yì cauɓikea ka, pa eare nǝ Thummim.>> Pǝlǝa bwal-shishar kpa amur Sawul andǝ Jonatan, sǝ aɓwana ka à auwa.  
\v 42 Pǝlǝa Sawul bang ama, <<Wu bwal-shishar anrem sǝnǝ muna-ɓwabura mem Jonatan.>> Sǝ bwal-shishar kpa amur Jonatan. 
\p  
\v 43 Pǝlǝa Sawul ɗì Jonatan ama, <<Banggam gìr mǝnana a pàk ka!>> Jonatan ne wi ama, <<Ən oasǝ kún gara mana nda a buam ngga aɓa mur-nyi sǝ ǝn oê a kunam. Mǝ ndya ka; mǝ nǝ wǔ.>> 
\p  
\v 44 Pǝlǝa Sawul banggi Jonatan ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ Ɓakuli wal-luim, ɓǝ̀ à wal-luio raka!>> 
\p  
\v 45 Sǝama amǝ'lwa ne Sawul ama, <<Palang sǝ à nǝ̀ wal-lú Jonatan, mǝnana Ɓakuli paktúró nǝi sǝ sǝm kum mǝnia yì limurǝm mǝgule a Isǝrayila ka? Pà nǝ̀ pa anggo ɗàng! Mbak-kàngkàng Yahweh nakam ngga, ko nyang mwashat a ɓamur Jonatan pà nǝ̀ kpa a nzali ɗang. Gìr mǝnana pè yalung ngga, Ɓakuli na mǝnana bwali wi kam ngga.>> Nda amǝ'lwa man amsǝ Jonatan, à wal-luí raka. 
\p  
\v 46 Pǝlǝa Sawul nying pǝrta amǝ'Filisti, sǝ amǝ'Filisti nyar a bu-nzali malea ka. 
\p  
\v 47 Anzǝm mǝnana Sawul dumǝna murǝm mala Isǝrayila ka, lwa-lwa arǝ aɓi-mǝbura a koya buì: amǝ'Mowap, andǝ amǝ'Amon, andǝ amǝ'Edom andǝ amurǝma mala Zoba, andǝ amǝ'Filisti. Koya ban na Sawul wari a munǝo ka, kǝ kum limurǝm.  
\v 48 Sawul munǝ munǝo mala ɓwaburaɓwa, sǝ gandǝ amǝ'Amalek. Amsǝ amǝ'Isǝrayila a bù aɓwana mana à yinǝ munǝo arǝia ka. 
\s1 Amǝɓala mala Sawul 
\p  
\v 49 Amuna-burana mala Sawul ka, à nda ka Jonatan, andǝ Ishvi, sǝ Malkishuwa; sǝ ndanǝ amuna-mamǝna ɓari; mǝgule atea ka nda Merap, sǝ mǝkyauwe nda Mikal.  
\v 50 Mālá Sawul nda Ahinowam, ɓoarnsarile Ahima'az. Mǝ'sàrǝ̀ban amur amǝ'lwa mala Sawul ka, nda Abna muna-ɓwabura mala Ner, kina Sawul.  
\v 51 Tár Sawul ka nda Kish; sǝ Ner yì tár Abna ka, nda muna-ɓwabura mala Abiyel. 
\p  
\v 52 Sawul munǝ munǝo mǝcandǝe arǝ amǝ'Filisti aɓa do-yilǝmu male kat. Nda gìr mana tsǝa sǝ akoya pwari sǝ kum ɓwabura mǝnana ndanǝ rǝcandǝa andǝ mǝsǝkàng-kàngŋa ka, nǝ̀ oasǝ ɓwe aɓalǝ amǝ'lwa male. 
\c 15  
\s1 Yahweh ɓinǝ Sawul 
\p  
\v 1 Samuyila banggi Sawul ama, <<\f + \fr 15:1 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt 1Sam 9:16\ft .\f*Mǝ nda ɓwa mǝnana Yahweh tasǝam ɓǝ̀n ɗārǝo ace mǝnana wu duk murǝm amúr aɓwana male amǝ'Isǝrayila ka. Adyan ngga, kwakikiro arǝ cau mǝnana Yahweh kǝ na ka.  
\v 2 Yahweh mana Karban nǝ Gulo kat ka, bang ama, <Ən sǝnǝna gìr mǝɓane mǝnana amǝ'Amalek pàkkî amǝ Isǝrayila amur njar, lang amǝ Isǝrayila purî nzali Masar ka.  
\v 3 Adyan ngga, wu kyane wu kya wal amǝ'Amalek, sǝ gìr mǝnana kat à ndanǝi ka, wu tàrì ace Ɓakuli. Wu kǝa sǝn-mǝsǝswatǝr malea ɗàng. Wu wal-lú aburana, andǝ amamǝna, andǝ amuna, andǝ amuna-mǝkeke, andǝ andá, andǝ anzur, andǝ akalakadambi, sǝ amǝdambǝriso.> >> 
\p  
\v 4 Pǝlǝa Sawul ramba amǝ'lwa, sǝ ɓallia a Telem. Asoje-kusǝu na á-gbǝman-ɓari (200,000), sǝ aburana mala tàu mala Yahuda ka à nda á-lum (10,000).  
\v 5 Pǝlǝa Sawul andǝ aburana male wari a nggea-là mala amǝ'Amalek, sǝ à kya kumsǝ a ɓangŋaban.  
\v 6 Pǝlǝa Sawul banggi amǝ'Ken\f + \fr 15:6 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Akas 1:16; 4:11\ft .\f* ama, <<Wu o, wu nying amǝ'Amalek, ace mǝnana mǝ nggá kiɗiki wun wunǝia raka. Wun ngga, wu lǝmdǝ pěmǝɓoarne aban amǝ Isǝrayila kat lang à purî ɓá nzali Masar ka.>> Nda amǝ'Ken purî ɓalǝ amǝ'Amalek ka. 
\p  
\v 7 Pǝlǝa Sawul wal amǝ'Amalek kat twal a Havila aban ká ɗār a Shur, mǝnana nda a takuli mala Masar ka.  
\v 8 Sǝ gbami Agag murǝm mala amǝ'Amalek andǝamǝsǝi, sǝ aɓwana mala Agag ka, tària nǝ twaltea kat-kat nǝ kún nggeabyau.  
\v 9 Sǝama, Sawul andǝ amǝ'lwa male ka, à nying Agag nǝyilǝmu, sǝ à nying amǝɓoarne-katkat atà ambul andǝ anzur, andǝ andá, andǝ amuna-ndá mǝ'nyange, andǝ amuna-nzur, andǝ koya gir mǝnana mǝɓoarne na ka. À earce ama à nǝ̀ kiɗiki amǝnia yì agir ka ɗàng. Sǝ acili agirkusǝu mǝnana à ɓǝsǝkia sǝ amǝɓane na ka, à wal-luia kat. 
\p  
\v 10 Pǝlǝa cau mala Yahweh yiu aban Samuyila ama:  
\v 11 <<Ən pàk-ɓǝnsǝlǝma \f + \fr 15:11 \fq pàk-ɓǝnsǝlǝma \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Tite 6:6\ft .\f* nǝ tsǝk Sawul ɓǝ̀ duk murǝm, acemǝnana pǝlǝna nzǝmi arǝ kpatam, sǝ ɓinǝ pàk gìr mǝnana ǝn tsǝki wi nzongcau arǝì nǝma ɓǝ̀ pè ka.>> Bum Samuyila lúllô, sǝ ɓua aban Yahweh aɓa dù mǝno kat. 
\p  
\v 12 Ban fana ka, Samuyila lo nǝ dǝmbari ace ká aban Sawul. Sǝama ɓeɓwa banggi Samuyila ama, <<Sawul wari a Kamel a bân ɓakkì ɓamúrì gìr mana aɓwana nǝ̀ nggǝ ɗenyinǝi ace ka, sǝ wulina umǝna a Gilgal.>> 
\p  
\v 13 Lang Samuyila yina aban Sawul ka, Sawul ne wi ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh tsǝko bù! Ən pàngŋǝ́nà gìr mǝnana Yahweh bang ngga.>>  
\v 14 Sǝ Samuyila ɗì ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ nda anggo ka, sǝ gi mana ǝn nggǝ oè a kiram kǝla ɓua mala anzur andǝ andá?>>  
\v 15 Sawul ne wi ama, <<Amǝ'lwa pwania arǝ amǝ'Amalek sǝ à yinǝia; à nying anzur andǝ andá amǝɓoarne-katkat nǝyilǝmu ace pà gìr'nkila nǝia aban Yahweh Ɓakuli mô; sǝ acilia ka sǝm kiɗikinia kat-kat.>> 
\p  
\v 16 Pǝlǝa Samuyila banggi Sawul ama, <<Came ɓǝ̀n banggo gìr mǝnana Yahweh banggam yilung nǝ du ka.>> Sawul ne wi ama, <<Banggam.>>  
\v 17 Samuyila banggi wi ama, <<Kat andǝ mani ama, a sǝn ɓamuro ka a pa kún kǝgir raka, a nda múrû mala atau mala Isǝrayila re? Yahweh ɗārǝo a duk murǝm amúr amǝ'Isǝrayila.  
\v 18 Yahweh tasǝo kya pakki wi túrô, banggo ama, <Kyane, tària ace kiɗikia kat-kat, yià amǝ'Amalek amǝ'cauɓikea mǝno, sǝ wu munǝ-munǝo arǝia sheɓǝ̀ a twalnatea kang ngga.>  
\v 19 Palang sǝ a kpata gi Yahweh ɗàng? Palang sǝ a rufi atà gǝna-lwa, sǝ a pàk gìr mǝnana mǝɓike na ka, a sǝne mala Yahweh.>> 
\p  
\v 20 Pǝlǝa Sawul ne Samuyila ama, <<Ən kpanatà gi Yahweh. Ən warina ǝn pangŋǝ̀nà túró mǝnana Yahweh túrǎm ace ka. Ən yinanǝ Agag murǝm mala amǝ'Amalek, sǝ ǝn twalnata amǝ'Amalek kat-kat.  
\v 21 Sǝama amǝ'lwa mem pwan gǝna-lwa atà anzur andǝ andá; yià agir mǝɓoarne-katkat aɓalǝ amǝnana à tària ace kiɗikia ka; à yinǝia kani a Gilgal ace pà gìr'nkila aban Yahweh, Ɓakuli mô.>> 
\p  
\v 22 Samuyila bang ama, 
\q1 <<Mǝye nda mǝnana kǝ pwasǝbum Yahweh ka: 
\q2 Okiru na le ko apagir mala pisǝe kǝring andǝ pà agir'nkila na? 
\q1 Sǝni, okiru ka ɓoaro-kuti pà gìr'nkila, 
\q2 sǝ kwakikiru ka ɓoaro-kuti mùrú agam.\f + \fr 15:22 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Ang 40:6-8; 50:8-9; Pas 21:3; Isha 1:11-13; 1:16-17; Ir 7:22-23; Mik 6:6-8; Ib 10:6-9\ft .\f* 
\q1  
\v 23 Mgbicau ka nda kǝla cauɓikea mala monzǝo, 
\q2 sǝ twalkicau ka nda kǝla ɓealɓikea mala peri atà ankúl. 
\q1 Acemǝnana a ɓinǝ cau mala Yahweh ka, 
\q2 Yì gbal ka ɓinǝno arǝ duk murǝm.>> 
\p  
\v 24 Sawul ne Samuyila ama, <<Ən pángŋǝ̀nà cauɓikea, acemǝnana ǝn kpata nzongcau mala Yahweh andǝ cau mò ɗàng. Gìr mǝnana tsǝk ka ɓangciu na pàkkam arǝ aɓwana, sǝ ǝn kpata già ka.  
\v 25 Sǝama adyan ngga, ida twàlâm-ban cauɓikea mem, sǝ wu yiu atam, ace mǝnana mǝ peri aban Yahweh ka.>> 
\p  
\v 26 Samuyila banggi wi ama, <<Pà mǝ nǝ ká atò ɗàng. A ginǝ kpata nzongcau mala Yahweh, sǝ Yahweh ɓinǝno arǝ duk murǝm amúr Isǝrayila.>> 
\p  
\v 27 Lang Samuyila wulio nǝ̀ u ka, Sawul gbami kún nggea-daura male, kara sana.  
\v 28 Samuyila ne wi ama, <<Yahweh sanǝna domurǝm mala Isǝrayila arǝò yalung sǝ pànî ɓio ɓwa-Isǝrayila mana ɓoaro kútiǒ ka.  
\v 29 Ɓakuli mǝɓoarɓwe mala Isǝrayila ka, kǝ na nyir ɗàng, sǝ kǝ nggaɗi ɗenyicau male ɗàng. Yì ka, ɓwapǝndǝa na mǝnana kǝ nggaɗi ɗenyicau male ka ɗàng.>> 
\p  
\v 30 Pǝlǝa Sawul bang ama, <<Ən pàngŋǝ́nà cauɓikea. Sǝama, ida lǝmdǝam gulo aɓadǝm aɓwana-mǝgule mala aɓwana mem sǝ aɓadǝm amǝ'Isǝrayila. Nyare atàm ace mǝnana mǝ peri aban Yahweh Ɓakuli mô ka.>>  
\v 31 Nda Samuyila nyar atè, sǝ Sawul peri aban Yahweh. 
\p  
\v 32 Pǝlǝa Samuyila bang ama, <<Wu yinǝam nǝ Agag, yì murǝm mala amǝ'Amalek kani.>> Agag pǝlǝa yiu abani aɓalǝ ansolo, sǝ kǝ ne ɓamúrì ama, <<Mǝsǝcau, lúllô mala lú ka umǝna.>>  
\v 33 Samuyila ne wi ama, <<Kǝla mǝnana nggeabyau mô tsǝk amamǝna à ɗwanyi amuna ka, anggo gbal nggò nǝ̀ ɗwanyi munì.>> Pǝlǝa Samuyila kwarki Agag, kasǝki mgbeatuk-mgbeatuk akano a Gilgal aɓadǝm Yahweh. 
\p  
\v 34 Pǝlǝa Samuyila o a Rama, sǝ Sawul nyar a ɓala male a Gibiya.  
\v 35 Samuyila nyare sǝn Sawul ɗǝm ɗàng bà lú male. Sǝama Samuyila pàk bumkiɗikea ace Sawul. Sǝ Yahweh ka banɓiki wi mǝnana tsǝk Sawul ɓǝ̀ duk murǝm amur Isǝrayila ka. 
\c 16  
\s1 Samuyila ɗārǝ́ Dauda ɓǝ̀ duk murǝm 
\p  
\v 1 A ɓè fara ka, Yahweh banggi Samuyila ama, <<Baniò nǝ̀ sau lang sǝ awu nǝ lidǝmba nǝ pak-bumkiɗikea ace Sawul. Ən ɓinǝnace duk murǝm male amur amǝ Isǝrayila. Acemani ka, lùmsǝ njawe mò nǝ mùrú olif sǝ wu o a Betalami. A mǝno yì là ka, ɗice ɓwa mǝnana à tunǝki ama Jeshi ka, acemǝnana ǝn tarna mwashat aɓalǝ amuna-burana male ɓǝ̀ duk murǝm mem.>>  
\v 2 Sǝ Samuyila bang ama, <<Lang sǝ mǝ nǝ ká? Ɓǝ̀ Sawul okce ka, nǝ̀ wal-luem.>> 
\p Pǝlǝa Yahweh banggi wi ama, <<Bwal muna-ndǎ abuo sǝ wu bang ama, <Ən yiu ace pà gìr'nkila aban Yahweh.>  
\v 3 Tunǝ Jeshi ɓǝ̀ yiu a ban pa gìr'nkilè, sǝ mǝ nǝ lǝmdǝo gìr mǝnana awu nǝ pàk ka. Awu nǝ ɗārǝàm ɓwa mǝnana mǝ nǝ banggo ka.>> 
\p  
\v 4 Anggo sǝ Samuyila pa kǝla mǝnana Yahweh ne wi ka. Lang yi bwalǝna Betalami ka, aɓwana-mǝgule mala là pur nǝ rǝɓǝla à yi kúllì. À ɗì ama, <<Mana kumban le? A yiu jam le?>> 
\p  
\v 5 Samuyila earia wia ama, <<E, ǝn yiu aɓa rǝpwala, ace pà gìr'nkila aban Yahweh. Wu lak ɓamur rǝ wun sǝ wu yiu atàm a ban pâ gìr'nkilè.>> Pǝlǝa Samuyila lak Jeshi andǝ amuni, sǝ tunǝia ɓǝà yiu gbal ace pà mǝno yì gìr'nkila ka. 
\p  
\v 6 Lang Jeshi andǝ amuni yi bwalǝna ka, Samuyila soa mǝsǝi arǝ Eliyap sǝ na ama, <<Ɓafo, mǝnia ka nda kǝ ɓwa mǝnana Yahweh tàrì ɓǝ̀ duk murǝm ngga.>> 
\p  
\v 7 Sǝ Yahweh ka ne Samuyila ama, <<Cè ɓabumo o arǝ puro male a nggūrǝu ko dāh'rya male ɗàng. Yì ka ǝn ɓinǝni. Yahweh kǝ sǝngìr a sǝne mala ɓwapǝndǝa ɗang. Ɓwapǝndǝa kǝ sǝn pǎ mala ɓwa a nggūrǝu, sǝ Yahweh ka ɓabum na sǝngiyi ka.>> 
\p  
\v 8 Pǝlǝa Jeshi ne muni Abinadap ɓǝ̀ puro ɓǝ̀ gya a ɓadǝm Samuyila. Sǝ Samuyila ka na ama, <<Mǝnia nda ɓwa mǝnana Yahweh twal ka ɗàng.>>  
\v 9 Anzǝmi ka Jeshi tasǝ Shama. Samuyila na ama, <<Mǝnia gbal ka, nda ɓwa mǝnana Yahweh twal ka ɗàng.>>  
\v 10 Anggo sǝ Jeshi lǝmdǝì Samuyila amuni tongno-nong-ɓari. Sǝ Samuyila ne Jeshi ama, <<Yahweh twal kǝ ɓwa atà amǝnia yì amuna ka ɗàng.>>  
\v 11 Pǝlǝa Samuyila ɗì Jeshi ama, <<Kǝ amunio nia ka le?>> 
\p Jeshi eari wi ama, <<Mǝtankwang malea nakam, sǝ nda a bondo aban yál anzur andǝ ambul.>> 
\p Samuyila na ama, <<Turban atè adyan ɓǝà kya yinǝi; pà sǝm nǝ̀ dumnǝdo ɗang sheɓǝ̀ yina ka.>> 
\p  
\v 12 Jeshi pǝlǝa túrban atè sǝ yiu. Yì mǝlagga Dauda ka, pǝndǝa a nggūrǝu, ɓoarjam sǝ amǝsǝì ɓoar sǝna. 
\p Yahweh ne Samuyila ama, <<Mǝnia nda ɓwê; lo ɗārǝí.>> 
\p  
\v 13 Lang Dauda na aban came aɓalǝ amǝ'eambi ka, Samuyila twal mùrú olif mana aɓa njawe mǝnana yinǝi ka, sǝ ɗārǝ́ Dauda nǝi. Twal amǝno yì pwari aban o a dǝmba ka, Bangŋo mala Yahweh sulǝo amur Dauda nǝ rǝcandǝa. Samuyila pǝlǝa nyare o a Rama. 
\s1 Dauda walî Sawul zangŋan 
\p  
\v 14 A bàkú mǝno ka, Bangŋo mala Yahweh nyìngŋǝ̀nà Sawul, sǝ ɓè bangŋo mǝɓike mǝnana pur nǝban Yahweh ka, yinǝi wi nǝ banɓikea.  
\v 15 Amǝ'túró male yì Sawul banggi wi ama, <<Sǝni, ɓè bangŋo mǝɓike mǝnana pur nǝban Yahweh ka nda mǝnana kǝ po banɓikea ka.  
\v 16 Eara sǝm, ɓwamǝgule, ɓǝ̀ sǝm alota ɓwa mǝnana mǝ'sǝlǝ wal zangŋan na ka; sǝ lang yì bangŋo mǝɓike nǝban Ɓakuli yina amuro ka, ɓwê nǝ̀ walô zangŋan sǝ hakkilo mô nǝ̀ nongŋo.>> 
\p  
\v 17 Nda Sawul banggi amǝ'túró male ama, <<Wu alamta ɓwa mǝnana sǝlǝ wal zangŋan pepè ka sǝ wu yinǝi abanam.>>  
\v 18 Mwashat atà alaggana male eari wi ama, <<Ən sǝnǝna ɓè muna-ɓwabura mala Jeshi ɓwa Betalami, mǝnana mǝ'sǝlǝ wal zangŋan na ka. Yì ɗǝm ngga ɓwabura mǝ'ɓabum-candǝa na sǝ mǝ'lwa na. Kǝ nacau pepè sǝ ɓoarjam. Sǝ Yahweh na atè.>> 
\p  
\v 19 Pǝlǝa Sawul tasǝ amǝ'na-túrbân aban Jeshi nǝ cau ama, <<Tàsǝâm muna-ɓwabura mô Dauda, mǝnana nda atà ambul andǝ anzur ka.>>  
\v 20 Pǝlǝa Jeshi twal mǝdambǝriso sǝ tsǝki wi twalo mala bǝredi andǝ mùr-anap aɓa sambǝram a nzǝmi, andǝ muna-mbul sǝ tasǝia nǝ bú Dauda aban Sawul.  
\v 21 Dauda yiu aban Sawul sǝ yi duk mǝtúró male. Sawul earce Dauda kǝ̀rkǝ́r sǝ twali ɓǝ̀ duk mǝ'twali wi agirmunǝo male.  
\v 22 Pǝlǝa Sawul tasǝ mǝ'na-túrbân aban Jeshi nǝ cau ama, <<Ida, ɗeki Dauda ɓǝ̀ ueo aɓa túró mem, acemǝnana kumǝna earmúrú a mǝsǝam.>> 
\p  
\v 23 Twal a pwari mǝno, lang yì bangŋo mǝɓike nǝban Ɓakuli yina amur Sawul ka, Dauda nǝ̀ twal zangŋan male nǝ̀ wali. Sǝ yì bangŋo mǝɓike ka nǝ̀ o, hakkilo mala Sawul nǝ̀ nongŋo, sǝ nǝ̀ kum rǝpwala. 
\c 17  
\s1 Golaya soabum amǝ'Isǝrayila 
\p  
\v 1 A bàkú mǝno ka amǝ'Filisti ramba amǝ'lwa malea ace munǝo a Soko, ɓè là a bu-nzali Yahuda; à tsǝk kàttì malea a ban mǝnana à tunǝi ama Efes-Damim ngga, anre Soko andǝ Azeka.  
\v 2 Sawul andǝ aburana mala Isǝrayila ramba, sǝ à tsǝk kàttì malea a Ɓangŋaban Ela, a ban mǝnana à gilǝrǝia a nzong ban-je munǝo arǝ amǝ'Filisti ka.  
\v 3 Amǝ'Filisti cam amur ɓè mgbangban, sǝ amǝ Isǝrayila cam amur ɓè mǝnana soa mǝno, sǝ ɓangŋaban na gau nrea ka. 
\p  
\v 4 Pǝlǝa gbani mala amǝ'Filisti, purî ɓá kàttì mala amǝ'Filisti. Lullǝì nda Golaya; ɓwa nggea-là Gat na. Dāh'rya male bik kǝla mita tàrú.  
\v 5 Oasǝ sukuru-bolo mala bolo-bángŋá a ɓamúrí, sǝ daura-bolo mǝnana oasǝ arǝì ka, dǝmbǝrya male bik kǝla tyang lumi-tongno-bwamdǝ-tongno-nong-ɓari (57).  
\v 6 Yì ɗǝm ngga oasǝa oamsǝkan mala bolo-bángŋá arǝ akusǝì, sǝ bwal nkongŋo a mkpamtari.  
\v 7 Tondong kaɗa male nyane kǝla muna-nggun-so. Dǝmbǝrya mala mǝsǝ kaɗa male mala bolo-candǝa ka, tyang tongno-nong-ɓari na. Ɓè mǝ'lwa bwalì wi ntongŋo male sǝ kǝ gya a ɓadǝmbi. 
\p  
\v 8 Golaya came sǝ loasǝ gì arǝ amǝ Isǝrayila ama, <<Mana tsǝa sǝ wu pur kat ama wun nǝ̀ munǝo? Mǝ nda ɓwa'Filisti re, sǝ wun ngga, wu nda ka aguro mala Sawul re? Wu pusǝ ɓwa mwashat aɓalǝ wun, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ sulǝ abanam.  
\v 9 Ɓǝ̀ ɓwê gandǝ munǝ arǝàm sǝ wal-luem ngga, sǝm nǝ̀ duk aguro ma'wun; sǝ ɓǝ̀n gandǝì, sǝ ǝn wal-luí ka, wun nǝ̀ duk aguro ma'sǝm, wun nǝ̀ pàkka sǝm túró.  
\v 10 Yalung ngga ǝn ɓǝsǝki wun kat, wun amǝ'lwa mala Isǝrayila. Wu tasǝ ɓwa mwashat ɓǝ̀ pur atàm, mǝnana nǝ̀ munǝ arǝàm ngga.>>  
\v 11 Lang Sawul andǝ Isǝrayila kat ok amǝnia yì acau mala ɓwa'Filisti ka, ǝn'ò pakkia wia sǝ à dǝurǝ kǝ̀rkǝ́r. 
\s1 Jeshi túr Dauda a kàttì mala Sawul 
\p  
\v 12 A bàkú mǝno ka, ɓè ɓwabura na kam lùllǝì ama Jeshi, ɓwa'Efǝrat a Betalami, mana nda tár Dauda ka; ndanǝ amuna-burana tongno-nong-tàrú. A nza mala Sawul ka, ɓwabure enà kutsuk.  
\v 13 Amuna-burana amǝdǝmbe male tàrú ka, à o atà Sawul a munǝo. Alullǝia nda ka Eliyap muna-dǝmba, andǝ Aminadap ɓaria, sǝ tàruia nda Shama.  
\v 14 Dauda ka nda mǝtankwang. Amǝgule mǝnia tàrú ka, à o atà Sawul,  
\v 15 sǝ Dauda ka camarǝ ká aban Sawul\f + \fr 17:15 \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt 1Sam 16:21-23\ft .\f* sǝ nǝ̀ nyare ace ɗenyinǝ ambul andǝ anzur mala tárrí a Betalami. 
\p  
\v 16 Twal anongŋo lumi-ine ɓwa'Filisti mǝno camarǝ puro sǝ nǝ̀ yia came a bancame male, dǝmbari andǝ pwarikpǝra.  
\v 17 Ɓè pwari ka, Jeshi banggi muna-ɓwabura male Dauda ama, <<Kyan nǝì amǝ'eambo buku mǝssa mǝnia à kàngŋì ka, andǝ agbatali bǝredi mǝnia lum ngga; kyan nǝia akaurǝa aban amǝ'eambo a kàttì.  
\v 18 Sǝ wu twal adú kiura mǝnia lum ngga a buo wu kya pê mǝ'sàrǝ̀ban amur nggǝsan mala amǝ'lwa á-mwashat malea. Kya sǝni ko amǝ'eambo na jam, sǝ wu yinǝam nǝ \f + \fr 17:18 \fq kún-bǝri \ft ko <<cautera>>\f*kún-bǝri nǝbania mǝnana nǝ̀ lǝmdǝ ama mbak-kàngkàng à nda kam ngga.>> 
\p  
\v 19 Anggo ka, Sawul andǝ amǝ'eambu mǝnia andǝ amǝ'lwa mala Isǝrayila puppup ka, à nda aɓa Ɓangŋaban Ela, a ban munǝo andǝ amǝ'Filisti.  
\v 20 Nda Dauda lo nǝ dǝmbari ɗiɗyal sǝ nying ambul andǝ anzur a bù ɓeɓwa ɓǝ̀ tsǝkiria, pǝlǝa twal agirlina mǝno sǝ bwal-njar, kǝla mǝnana Jeshi banggi wi ka. Yi bik kàttì lang amǝ'lwa na arǝ puro à nǝ̀ ká nzong ban-je munǝo, sǝ à kǝ̀ ɓua gāwàn lwa ka.  
\v 21 Amǝ'Isǝrayila tsaɗi-akunarǝia ace munǝo, sǝ à soa ka amǝ'Filisti; sǝ amǝ'Filisti gbal ka, à tsaɗi-akunarǝia ace munǝo, sǝ à soa ka amǝ'Isǝrayila. À came sǝ à soa ɓamǝsǝarǝia, amǝ'lwa arǝ amǝ'lwa.  
\v 22 Pǝlǝa Dauda nying atwalo male a bù mǝ'tsǝkir atwalo, sǝ ɓangŋa wari a nzong ban-je munǝo sǝ makkì-amǝ'eambi-kún.  
\v 23 Lang ndarǝ nacau nǝia ka, kara sǝni ka, Golaya, gbani mala amǝ'Filisti, ɓwa'Gat, purnì nzong ban-je munǝo mala amǝ'Filisti. Nacau mǝ'mwashati kǝla mana nakiyi pwari-pwari ka, \f + \fr 17:23 \ft Sǝni a: \xt 17:8\ft .\f* sǝ Dauda oè.  
\v 24 Pwari mǝnana kat aburana mala Isǝrayila sǝni ka, yià kat à ɓanggi wi nǝ ɓangciu mǝkǝ̀rkǝ́rnì. 
\p  
\v 25 À hamnanǝi aban aburana mala Isǝrayila ama, <<Wu sǝn mǝnia yì ɓwabura mǝnana camarǝ puro ka re? Kǝ pur ace nabura\f + \fr 17:25 \fq nabura \ft ko <<soabum,>> ko <<ɓǝsǝki>> ko <<sanggi>>\f* arǝ Isǝrayila. Murǝm nǝ̀ pa gǝna mǝgule aban ɓwa mǝnana nǝ̀ wal-luí ka; nǝ̀ pe wi ɓoarnsarile ɓǝ̀ duk māmí, sǝ nǝ̀ pusǝ ɓala mala tárrí arǝ mbwe boalo-cemi!>> 
\p  
\v 26 Dauda ɗì amǝ'lwa mǝnana a baní tù ka ama, <<Mana à nǝ̀ pè ɓwa mǝnana wal-lú ɓwa'Filisti mǝnia, nǝ̀ pusǝ mǝnia yì gìr kǝsǝkya arǝ Isǝrayila ka? Yana ɗe nda mǝnia yì ɓwa'Filisti mǝ'ɗwanyi kasǝ-ɓatau, mǝnana nǝ̀ sanggi amǝ'lwa mala Ɓakuli mǝ'yilǝmui ka?>> 
\p  
\v 27 Pǝlǝa aburana mǝnia eari Dauda nǝ ɓǝsǝlǝi wi cau mǝnana à nani a dǝmba ka ama, <<E, mǝno ka nda gìr mǝnana à nǝ̀ pè ace ɓwa mǝnana wal-lú mǝno yì ɓwabura ka.>> 
\p  
\v 28 Lang Eliyap, mǝgula Dauda ok cau mǝno Dauda nakiyi aburana mǝno ka, pǝlǝa ɗì Dauda nǝ bumlulla ama, <<Mana ɗe a yiua pě kani? Amǝno yì anzur kpokyak ka yana a nyinggi wi ɓǝ̀ yália a ɓabondo? Ən súrǝ́nà rǝ twàlɓamúrû mô andǝ twalkicau mò. A yiu nǝ yiu ace sǝn amǝ'lwa a kún munǝo.>> 
\p  
\v 29 Dauda ɗiban ama, <<Mana ǝn pa ado? Mim ngga ǝn ɗiban nǝ ɗi.>>  
\v 30 Pǝlǝa nying baní kutio o aban aɓea aɓwana, sǝ ɗia kǝ ɗiban mǝ'mwashati. À nyesǝi wi eare mǝ'mwashati kǝla mǝnana a dǝmba ka.  
\v 31 Aɓea amǝ'lwa ok cau mǝno Dauda nakiyi ka, pǝlǝa à warinǝ ɗiban male aban murǝm Sawul. Pǝlǝa Sawul túrban atè ɓǝ̀ yiu. 
\p  
\v 32 Sǝ Dauda ne Sawul ama, <<Cè ɓabum kǝɓwa ɓungi atàcau mala mǝnia yì ɓwa'Filisti ka ɗàng. Mim guro mò, mǝ nǝ nggá munǝ arǝì.>> 
\p  
\v 33 Sawul ne Dauda ama, <<A pà wunǝ gandǝ ká arǝ ɓwa'Filisti man ace munǝo arǝì ɗàng, acemǝnana we ka, a nda muntulo, sǝ yì ka nggea kanggǝrang mǝ'lwa na twal a lo male ba yalung.>> 
\p  
\v 34 Sǝ Dauda ka banggi Sawul ama, <<Mim guro mò ka mǝ nda yálgír mala anzur andǝ ambul mala tárrám. A pwari mǝnana im ko biya yiu yi bwal atà anzur a domwan nǝ̀ um nǝi ka,  
\v 35 ǝn ɓang atè, ǝn wali kum, sǝ ǝn ak nzurnì a kúni. Lang pǝlǝ arǝàm ngga, ǝn gbami arǝ ankpakò-kúni, ǝn walki, sǝ ǝn wal-luí.  
\v 36 Ən wal im sǝ ǝn wal biya, anggo gbal sǝ mǝ nǝ pang nǝ ɓwa'Filisti mǝnia à kasǝ ɓate raka, acemǝnana ɓǝsǝki amǝ'lwa mala Ɓakuli mǝyilǝmui.  
\v 37 Ɓakuli mǝnana amsǝam aɓalǝ ankaulakusǝ im andǝ ankaulakusǝ biya ka, nǝ̀ amsǝam a bu mǝnia yì ɓwa'Filisti ka!>> Sǝ Sawul banggi Dauda ama, <<Kyane! Yahweh nǝ̀ pà atò!>> 
\p  
\v 38 Pǝlǝa Sawul nyesǝ agirmunǝo male pè Dauda. Oasǝi wi sukuru mala bolo-bángŋá amurí, sǝ oasǝi wi daura-bolo arǝì.  
\v 39 Dauda gyar nggeabyau mala Sawul amur agirmunǝo mǝno arǝì ka, sǝ mwam gya kàrìban nǝ̀ sǝn pǎ malea, acemǝnana yì ka malaká oasǝ a'ulang agir mǝno ka a kǝ pwari ɗàng. Pǝlǝa Dauda ne Sawul ama, <<Pà mǝ nǝ gandǝ ká aɓalǝ amǝnia yì agir ka ɗàng, acemǝnana ǝn bwalta paktúró nǝia ɗàng.>> Dauda pǝlǝa swáriǎ.  
\v 40 Twal gara-yálgìr male a buì sǝ kya tàrki amǝsǝtali tongno, amǝnana rǝia ɓùlɓùl ka, a muna-myalmur, oasǝia aɓa sambǝram-yálgìr male. Nǝ ntamso male a buì, gya aban ká, gbàshìban ɓwa'Filisti. 
\s1 Dauda wal-lú Golaya 
\p  
\v 41 Golaya pur aban yiu arǝ Dauda, mǝ'bwali wi ntongŋo male na a ɓadǝmbi sǝ kǝ gya atè. Gya kǝ sungŋo aban Dauda.  
\v 42 Lang soa mǝsǝi pèlǝ Dauda ka, ɓǝsǝki, acemǝnana sǝn Dauda ka lo-ɓwa na, ɓamǝsǝ muntulo na arǝì, pǝndǝa sǝ ɓoarjam.  
\v 43 Ne Dauda ama, <<A yiu arǝàm nǝ gara ka, mǝ nda nvwa le?>> Pǝlǝa sú Dauda aɓa lullǝ ankúl malea yià amǝ'Filisti.  
\v 44 Ne Dauda ama, <<Yiu kani, mǝ nǝ pè anyal andǝ anyam-ɓabondo nyamo.>> 
\p  
\v 45 Dauda ne yì ɓwa'Filisti ama, <<A yiu arǝàm nǝ nggeabyau, andǝ kaɗa, andǝ nkongŋo, sǝ mim ngga, mǝ ndarǝ ká arǝò aɓa lullǝ Yahweh Mǝtala Abangŋo, yì Ɓakuli mala amǝ'lwa mala Isǝrayila, mǝnana a nabura arǝì ka.  
\v 46 A pwari man yalung ngga, Yahweh nǝ̀ tasǝo a ɓabuam! Mǝ nǝ walo sǝ mǝ nǝ kasǝ ɓamuro. Yalung ngga mǝ nǝ pè anyal mǝnana a kuli ka, andǝ anyam-ɓabondo mala nzali man alú ka amǝ'lwa mala amǝ'Filisti. Sǝ ɓanza kat nǝ̀ sǝlǝ ama Ɓakuli na a Isǝrayila.  
\v 47 Sǝ koya ɓwa mǝnana a ban ramba kani ka, nǝ̀ sǝlǝ ama pà nǝ nggeabyau ko nkongŋo sǝ Yahweh kǝ amsǝ aɓwana male ɗàng. Lwa mǝnia ka mala Yahweh na, sǝ yì ka nǝ̀ tasǝ wun kat a ɓabù sǝm.>> 
\p  
\v 48 Lang yì ɓwa'Filisti lo kǝ gbàshìban je andǝ Dauda ka, Dauda tù nǝ mire aban ká a nzong ban-je munǝo ace je andǝ ɓwa'Filisti.  
\v 49 Dauda oasǝ buì aɓa sambǝram male sǝ pusǝ tali mwashat, wúlì aɓa ntamso sǝ ɓungŋǝna ɓwa'Filisti nǝi a kundǝmbi kum! Tali ar mu kundǝmbi kò aɓalǝi, kara kasǝa kpa nǝ ɓamǝsǝì a nzali. 
\p  
\v 50 Anggo sǝ Dauda limurǝm amur ɓwa'Filisti nǝ ntamso andǝ tali; kat andǝ amani ama Dauda pànǝ kǝ nggeabyau a buì raka, ɓù ɓwa'Filisti túrí a nzali wali màk. 
\p  
\v 51 Pǝlǝa Dauda ɓangŋa yi cam amur ɓwa'Filisti. Gbami nggeabyau mala ɓwa'Filisti, kwetǝi a ndè, sǝ masǝlǝi kasǝ ɓamúrí. Lang amǝ'Filisti sǝni ama gbani malea wuna ka, à pǝlǝ nǝ mire aban o. 
\p  
\v 52 Pǝlǝa aburana mala Isǝrayila lo nǝ gāwàn lwa, sǝ à pǝrta amǝ'Filisti aban ká ɗār a ɓangŋaban andǝ akún nggea-là Ekǝron. Alú ka amǝ'Filisti nonggi amur njargula Sharayim aban ká Gat andǝ Ekǝron.  
\v 53 Sǝ lang amǝ Isǝrayila nyarî pǝrta amǝ'Filisti ka, à kya pwan gǝna-lwa a kàttì mala amǝ'Filisti.  
\v 54 Dauda twal ɓamur Golaya, yì ɓwa'Filisti sǝ yinǝi a Urǝshalima, sǝ agirmunǝo male ka tsǝia aɓa gumli male. 
\s1 À yinǝ Dauda aɓadǝm Sawul 
\p  
\v 55 Lang Sawul sǝn Dauda pur aban ká munǝo arǝ Golaya ka, ɗì Abna, mǝ'sàrǝ̀ban mala amǝ'lwa ama, <<Abna, muna mala yan nda mǝno yì lagga ka wo?>> 
\p Abna eari wi ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ yilǝmo sauwa, Murǝm, ǝn sǝlǝ ɗang.>> 
\p  
\v 56 Sǝ murǝm bang ama, <<Ɗiban, yana nda tár mune.>> 
\p  
\v 57 Lang Dauda nyarǝnì wal-lú Golaya, ɓwa'Filisti ka, Abna twali, yinǝi aɓadǝm Sawul nǝ ɓamur Golaya a buì.  
\v 58 Sǝ Sawul ɗì ama, <<Lagga, a nda muna mala yana?>> 
\p Sǝ Dauda eari wi ama, <<Mǝ nda muna mala guro mò, Jeshi ɓwa'Betalami.>> 
\c 18  
\s1 Gyajam mala Dauda andǝ Jonatan 
\p  
\v 1 Lang Dauda malǝna nacau andǝ Sawul ka, kara ɓabum Jonatan o arǝ Dauda. Sǝ Jonatan earce Dauda kǝla mǝnana earce yilǝmi ka.\f + \fr 18:1 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt 1Sam 20:17; Nggur 13:6\ft .\f* 
\v 2 Tite a pwari mǝno ka, Sawul twal Dauda ɓǝ̀ do atè, sǝ eari wi nyar a ɓala mala tárrí ɗàng.  
\v 3 Pǝlǝa Jonatan kùrcau nǝ Dauda, acemǝnana earce Dauda kǝla mǝnana earce yilǝmi ka.  
\v 4 Jonatan swár nggea-daura mana arǝì ka, sǝ pè Dauda, andǝ nggeabyau male, andǝ nta male, sǝ nggur-ɓunu male. 
\p  
\v 5 Dauda ka, kǝ kum lidǝmba a koya puro male andǝ amǝ'lwa aban ká a koya ban mǝnana kat Sawul túrí kàm ngga; acemani ka, Sawul tsǝk Dauda a bancame mǝgule amur amǝ'lwa. Sǝ mǝnia ka, pwasǝbum amǝ'lwa kat andǝ amǝgulo mala Sawul. 
\s1 Sawul pàk mɓali arǝ Dauda 
\p  
\v 6 Lang amǝ'lwa na aban nyare a là, anzǝm mana Dauda walna ɓwa'Filisti ka, amamǝna purki arǝ alá mala Isǝrayila kat ace ká kúllí Murǝm Sawul nǝ nggyal andǝ nggwam. Banɓoaria wia sǝ à kǝ wal akarata-bu andǝ agir jerang malea.  
\v 7 Amamǝne kǝ pakkiɗire, sǝ à kǝ tu'nggyal ama, 
\q1 <<Sawul walna aá male, 
\q2 sǝ Dauda walna aá lum male!>> 
\p  
\v 8 Mǝnia ka tsǝk Sawul bumi lul kǝ̀rkǝ́r, sǝ earce mǝno yì nggyal ka ɗàng. Na ama, <<À ɓwangsǝ Dauda nǝ aá lum, sǝ mim ngga, kǝ aá na à ɓwangsǝam nǝi ka. Mana ue ɗǝm nǝ̀ kumô ɓǝ̀ domurǝm na raka.>>  
\v 9 Twal a pwari mǝno aban ká dǝmba ka, Sawul tsǝk mǝsǝi arǝ Dauda nǝ mɓali andǝ nusǝban. 
\p  
\v 10 Ban fana ka, bangŋo mǝɓike pùr nǝban Ɓakuli, sǝ sulǝ amúr Sawul nǝ rǝcandǝa. Sǝ kútí a pàkkiagir kǝla mǝɓanggya aɓa ɓala male, sǝ Dauda na aban wal jerang male kǝla mana pàkkiyi pwari-pwari ka. Sawul ka ndanǝ nzo male a bui.  
\v 11 Sawul pakɗenyicau a bumi ama, <<Mǝ nǝ tǝm Dauda nǝ nzo, mǝ nǝ laptǝi arǝ bum-sheran,>> pǝlǝa túr nzo arǝ Dauda. Sǝama Dauda vwaki, api wi kusǝ ɓari. 
\p  
\v 12 Sawul ɓanggi Dauda, acemǝnana Yahweh na atà Dauda, sǝ Yahweh ka nyìngŋǝ̀nà Sawul.\f + \fr 18:12 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt 1Sam 16:18\ft .\f* 
\v 13 Acemani ka, Sawul pusǝ Dauda arǝ came a ɓadǝmbi, sǝ tsǝi pǝlǝ mǝ'sàrǝ̀ban amúr amǝ'lwa á-mwashat. Sǝ Dauda gingnǝ amǝ'lwa arǝ amunǝo.  
\v 14 Dauda kum lidǝmba aɓa koya gìr mǝnana pàkkiyi ka, acemǝnana Yahweh na atè.  
\v 15 Lang Sawul sǝni ama Dauda kǝ kum lidǝmba kǝ̀rkǝ́r ka, ɓangciu pàkki wi arǝì kǝ̀rkǝ́r.  
\v 16 Sǝama Isǝrayila andǝ aɓwana mala Yahuda kat earce Dauda, acemǝnana yì nda mǝnana kǝ̀ cambia wia a dǝmba sǝ kǝ gingnǝia ace pur ká lwa andǝ nyare ka. 
\s1 Dauda al Mikal 
\p  
\v 17 Pǝlǝa Sawul banggi Dauda ama, <<Sǝni, ɓoarnsarilem, Merap nia ka. Ən nggǝ earce nǝma mǝ nǝ po wi wu ali;\f + \fr 18:17 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt 1Sam 17:25\ft .\f* kǝ gìr mana ǝn earkiyice nǝ we ka, nda mana ama wu dum nǝ mǝsǝkang-kangŋa acem, sǝ wu lwa-lwa mala Yahweh.>> Sawul bang anggo acemǝnana nana a ɓabumi ama, <<Pà mǝ nǝ wal-lú Dauda nǝ nggearam ɗàng. Ɓǝ̀ bù amǝ'Filisti pàk mǝno!>> 
\p  
\v 18 Sǝ Dauda banggi Sawul ama, <<Mǝ nda yana? Ayana nda ka aɓǝla mem ko nggurkwar mala tárrám a Isǝrayila, mǝnana mǝ nǝ duk nkil murǝm ngga?>>  
\v 19 Lang pwari pàngŋǝ́nà mǝnana à nǝ̀ pa Merap, ɓoarnsarile Sawul aban Dauda ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ ali ka, Sawul twal ɓoarnsarile pè Adǝriyel ɓwa Mehola. 
\p  
\v 20 Adyan ngga, Mikal ɓoarnsarile Sawul kǝ earce Dauda. Lang à banggi Sawul cê ka, banɓoari wi.  
\v 21 Sawul pàk ɗenyicau ama, <<Mǝ nǝ pè Dauda ɓoarnsarilem Mikal, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ duk gbǝli a baní, sǝ ɓǝ̀ bù amǝ'Filisti pǝlǝa arǝì ka.>> Nda Sawul banggi Dauda ama, <<Adyan ngga, a ndanǝ ɓaria dǝmbu mala duk nkilam.>> 
\p  
\v 22 Pǝlǝa Sawul ne amǝtúró male ama, <<Wu banggi Dauda aɓa sǝmbǝrǝa ama, <Sǝni, Murǝm ngga banɓoari wi arǝò, sǝ amǝtúró male kat ka, à kǝ̀ earceo. Adyan ngga, duk nkil murǝm.> >>  
\v 23 Sǝ amǝtúró mala Sawul wario à kya ne Dauda amǝnia yì acau ka aɓa sǝmbǝrǝa. Dauda banggia wia ama, <<Wu kǝ sǝni ama gìr mǝkyauwe na ɓǝ̀ ɓwa duk nkil murǝm le? Mim ngga, mǝ nda mǝtǝ̀r, sǝ aɓwe kǝ twalam nǝ gulo ɗàng!>> 
\p  
\v 24 Sǝ amǝtúró mala Sawul nyare, à yi ne Sawul cau mǝnana Dauda bang ngga.  
\v 25 Pǝlǝa Sawul na ama, <<Wu banggi Dauda ama, <Murǝm kǝ earce kǝ gǝna ɗang. Gìr mana murǝm earkiyice ka, nda nggú-ɓata amǝ'Filisti gbǝman-mwashat, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ duk mbweban akúnì arǝ aɓi-mǝbura mala murǝm.> >> Adyan ngga, Sawul kǝ twali ama nǝ̀ gandǝ wal-lú Dauda nǝ bù amǝ'Filisti. 
\p  
\v 26 Lang amǝtúró mala Sawul banggi Dauda amǝnia yì acau ka, banɓoari wi, sǝ ear ama nǝ̀ duk nkil murǝm. Sǝ kaniama pwari mǝnana à tsǝkî Dauda nǝ̀ yia bik ka,  
\v 27 Dauda lo wario, atārǝia andǝ aburana male, sǝ à kya wal-lú amǝ'Filisti gbǝman-ɓari. Dauda yinǝ aggú-ɓatea, sǝ yi pè murǝm, kǝla mana làkkì malea pàk ka, ace mǝnana nǝ̀ duk bura ɓoarnsarile murǝm ngga. Pǝlǝa Sawul twal ɓoarnsarile, yì Mikal, pè Dauda ɓǝ̀ duk māmí. 
\p  
\v 28 Lang Sawul sǝni sǝ sǝlǝ ama Yahweh na atà Dauda, sǝ ɗǝm ngga ɓoarnsarile Mikal earce Dauda ka,  
\v 29 ɓangciu mǝnana Sawul ndanǝi arǝ Dauda ka, yi gul kàm kpǝm; sǝ twal a pwari mǝno ka, pǝlǝ ɓibura mala Dauda aɓalǝ anonggio kat. 
\p  
\v 30 Sǝ amǝ'sàrǝ̀ban mala amǝ'lwa mala amǝ'Filisti camarǝ pur lwa arǝ Isǝrayila; sǝ a koya munǝo ka, Dauda kum lidǝmba kútì acili amǝgulo mala amǝ'lwa mala Sawul kat. Sǝ mǝnia ka, tsǝa lullǝ Dauda zǝ́kí. 
\c 19  
\s1 Sawul ɓariki nǝ̀ wal-lú Dauda 
\p  
\v 1 Pǝlǝa Sawul banggi muna-ɓwabura male Jonatan andǝ amǝtúró male kat, ama ɓǝà wal-lú Dauda. \f + \fr 19:1 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa kúrè 18 mǝsǝi 1 mala malǝmce man.\f*Sǝama Jonatan ngga kǝ̀ earce Dauda kǝ̀rkǝ́r.  
\v 2 Sǝ Jonatan ne Dauda ama, <<Tárrám Sawul kǝ alte nǝ̀ wal-luio. Acemani ka, ida tsǝkiro liwi nǝ dǝmbari. Alta ban sǝmbǝrǝa, do a banì.  
\v 3 Mǝ nǝ puro, sǝ mǝ nǝ cam a nkanggari tárrám a patal, a ban mǝnana a nda kam ngga. Mǝ nǝ banggi tárrám cau amuro. Sǝ cau mǝnana kat ǝn ok ka, mǝ nǝ banggo.>> 
\p  
\v 4 Nda Jonatan ne tárrí cau mǝɓoarne amúr Dauda ka. Banggi wi ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ murǝm ɓǝ̀kǝa pàkki guro male Dauda cauɓikea ɗàng, acemǝnana pàkkô cauɓikea ɗàng. A kún mani ka, agir mǝnana peǎ ka à yinanǝ mǝɓoarne a bano.  
\v 5 Twal yilǝmi a kún bui lang wal-lú ɓwa'Filisti, sǝ Yahweh pè Isǝrayila kat nggea limurǝm ngga. We nǝ nggearǝo ka a sǝni sǝ banɓoaro. Palang sǝ awu nǝ pàk cauɓikea arǝ nkila mala mǝ'kunpwasǝa, nǝ wal-lú Dauda mǝnana pàkkô kǝ mǝɓane raka?>> 
\p  
\v 6 Pǝlǝa Sawul kwakikiri arǝ cau mala Jonatan, sǝ kángir ama, <<Mbak-kàngkàng Yahweh nakam ngga, à pà nǝ̀ wal-lú Dauda ɗàng.>>  
\v 7 Nda Jonatan tunǝ Dauda sǝ ne wi acau mǝnia kat ka. Pǝlǝa Jonatan yinǝ Dauda aban Sawul, sǝ Dauda lidǝmba nǝ pàkkî Sawul túró kǝla mǝnana a dǝmbe ka. 
\p  
\v 8 Munǝo lo ɗǝm anre ka amǝ'Filisti andǝ amǝ'Isǝrayila. Sǝ Dauda puro oa munǝo arǝ amǝ'Filisti, sǝ walia nǝ nggea walban, gandǝa amǝ'Filisti ɓanggi wi.  
\v 9 Pǝlǝa ɓè bangŋo mǝɓike\f + \fr 19:9 \fq bangŋo mǝɓike \ft Sǝni gbal aɓa kúrè 16 mǝsǝi 14 mala malǝmce man.\f* pùr nǝban Yahweh sǝ sulǝ amúr Sawul. Sawul naban dumnǝdo a ɓala male nǝ nzo male a buì, sǝ Dauda ka ndaban wal jerang.  
\v 10 Pǝlǝa Sawul ɓariki ama nǝ̀ tǝm Dauda nǝ nzo, nǝ̀ laptǝi arǝ bumkurǝm, sǝama Dauda vwaki, sǝ putǝlì ɓadǝm Sawul, sǝ nzo wario kya tǝm bumkurǝm. Nǝ du mala pwari mǝno ka, Dauda ɓangŋa auwa. 
\p  
\v 11 Sawul tasǝ amǝ'na-túrbân a ɓala mala Dauda ace mǝnana ɓǝà tsǝkmǝsǝia arǝì, sǝ ɓǝà wal-lui nǝ dǝmbari. Pǝlǝa Mikal mālá Dauda, banggi wi ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ a ɓangŋa a amsǝ yilǝmo nǝ dù man raka, liwi ka, à nǝ̀ wal-luio!>>  
\v 12 Nda Mikal sulǝ Dauda a nzali nǝban mǝsǝkurǝm, pǝlǝa ɓangŋa o auwa. 
\p  
\v 13 Pǝlǝa Mikal twal ɓǝ̀nzál,\f + \fr 19:13 \fq ɓǝ̀nzál \ft ko <<nkúl ɓala>>\f* sǝ nongsǝi amúr kpamgbang-nongŋo. Sǝ tsǝki wi gìr-loasǝmúrû mala nyang mbul a ban ɓamuri, sǝ kumsǝi wi nggubyau.  
\v 14 Lang Sawul tasǝ amǝ'na-túrbân ɓǝà kya bwal Dauda ka, Mikal nea wia ama, <<Dauda pà jam ɗàng.>> 
\p  
\v 15 Pǝlǝa Sawul nyesǝ amǝ'na-túrbân ama ɓǝà kya sǝn Dauda nǝ nggearǝia. Banggia wia ama, <<Wu twali wu yinǝam nǝi amúr kpamgbang-nongŋo male, ace mǝnana mǝ wal-luí ka.>>  
\v 16 Lang amǝ'na-túrbân wari ka, à kum ɓǝ̀nzál na aban nongŋo amúr kpamgbang-nongŋo andǝ gìr-loasǝmúrû mala nyang mbul a ban ɓamuri. 
\p  
\v 17 Sawul banggi Mikal ama, <<Palang sǝ a swarkiam anggo, sǝ a nying ɓiam-mǝbura ɓangŋa o?>> Mikal eari wi ama, <<Dauda banggam ama ɓǝ̀n bwali wi purî ɓala raka, nǝ̀ wal-luem.>> 
\p  
\v 18 Lang Dauda ɓangŋǝna sǝ auna ka, wari aban Samuyila a Rama, sǝ ne wi gìr mǝnana kat Sawul pàkki wi ka. Pǝlǝa yì andǝ Samuyila o, sǝ à kya do a Nayot.\f + \fr 19:18 \fq Nayot \ft ko muna-là mala amǝɓangnǝa.\f* 
\v 19 Cau yiu aban Sawul ama, <<Sǝni, Dauda na a Nayot a Rama.>>  
\v 20 Nda Sawul tasǝ amǝ'na-túrbân ɓǝ̀ à kya bwal Dauda. Sǝama lang à wari ka, à kya kum nggǝsan mala amǝɓangnǝa aban nakiacau ɓangnǝa, sǝ Samuyila nakam aban came abanì kǝla ɓwamǝgule amúrià. Bangŋo mala Ɓakuli sulǝ amúr amǝ'na-túrbân mala Sawul mǝno, sǝ à nacau ɓangnǝa gbal.  
\v 21 Lang à banggi Sawul gìr mǝnana kum amǝ'na-túrbân male ka, nyare Sawul tasǝ aɓea amǝ'na-túrbân, sǝ yià gbal ka à nacau ɓangnǝa. Sawul tasǝ tàruia amǝ'na-túrbân ɗǝm, sǝ yià gbal ka à kya kútí a nacau ɓangnǝa.  
\v 22 A masǝlǝate ka, Sawul lo nǝ nggearǝì wari a Rama. Lang yi bingŋǝna ban tūli-mùr mǝgule mǝnana a Seku ka, ɗìban ama, <<Samuyila andǝ Dauda na ke?>> À eari wi ama, <<À nda a Nayot, a Rama.>> 
\p  
\v 23 Pǝlǝa Sawul wari a Nayot a Rama. Bangŋo mala Ɓakuli sulǝ amurí gbal; kǝ nacau ɓangnǝa sǝ kǝ gya aban ká she lang yina a Nayot a Rama ka.  
\v 24 Yale swárki agir-nggūrǝì, sǝ nacau ɓangnǝa aɓadǝm Samuyila. Sawul nong gbǝrangtang aɓa pwari mǝno kat andǝ dù mǝno kat. Acemani ka, aɓwana ɗiban ama, <<Sawul gbal ka, nda aɓalǝ amǝɓangnǝa le?>> 
\c 20  
\s1 Dauda andǝ Jonatan 
\p  
\v 1 Pǝlǝa Dauda ɓangŋa nying Nayot a Rama. Wari aban Jonatan sǝ ɗì ama, <<Mana ǝn pàk le? Ya cauɓikea na ǝn pa? A ya njar sǝ ǝn pàkki tárró cauɓikea mǝnana tsǝa sǝ ndaban alte ama nǝ̀ twal yilǝmem ngga?>> 
\p  
\v 2 Jonatan eari wi ama, <<Ɓakuli twalbani; a pà nǝ wù ɗàng! Tárrám kǝ banggam koya gìr mǝnana nǝ̀ pàk ka, ko mǝgule ko mǝkyauwe. Sǝ palang sǝ tárrám nǝ̀ sǝmbǝ́rǝàm cau mǝnia ka? Mǝnia yì cau ka, pa anggo ɗàng.>>  
\v 3 Sǝ Dauda na ama: <<Mǝsǝtacau ǝn kánbo, Tárró sǝlǝna ama, ǝn kumǝna earmúrú a bano, acemani ka pà nǝ̀ banggo cê ɗàng, acemǝnana ɓǝ̀ kǝa lulbumo raka. Sǝama ǝn nggǝ banggo, mbak-kàngkàng Yahweh nakam, sǝ a nda nǝyilǝmu ka, twalkusǝu mwashat na anrem sǝnǝ lú!>> 
\p  
\v 4 Jonatan ne Dauda ama, <<Gìr mǝnana a banggam ngga, mǝ nǝ̀ pàkkô wi>> 
\p  
\v 5 Dauda banggi wi ama, <<Liwi ka lamsan mala \f + \fr 20:5 \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt Ɓal 10:10; 28:11\ft .\f*Bǝsa Zongŋo na, sǝ dumǝnam púp mǝ nǝ do aban ligirlina atà murǝm a kpamgbang-lǐ male; sǝama ǝn nggǝ earce nǝma wu nyem mǝ kya sǝmbǝrǝ a patal, twal ado aban ká pwarikpǝra mala tàruia nongŋo.  
\v 6 Ɓǝ̀ tárró ɗiban amuram ngga, awu nǝ banggi wi ama, <Dauda zǝm njar abanam tsuk-tsuk ama mǝ ɗeki nǝ̀ ɓangŋa nǝ̀ ká a nggea-là male a Betalami, acemǝnana pà gìr'nkila mala koya pǝlǝa na kam ace amǝ'ɓala malea puppup.>  
\v 7 Ɓǝ̀ bang ama, <Mǝɓoarne na> ka, lǝmdǝ ama guro mo pà aɓa ká-mǝɓane ɗàng. Sǝama ɓǝ̀ bumi lul kǝ̀rkǝ́r ka, sǝlǝ ama shamna nǝ̀ pàkkam mǝɓane.  
\v 8 Ace mani ka, awu nǝ̀ lǝmdǝam, mim guro mò, pěmǝɓoarne, acemǝnana a yina nǝi aɓa kùrcau nǝ we aɓadǝm Yahweh. Ɓǝ̀ mǝ ndanǝ cauɓikea amuram ngga, we nǝ nggearǝo ka wal-luim, kǝa kyan nǝ mim aban tárró ɗàng.>> 
\p  
\v 9 Jonatan ne wi ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ Ɓakuli twalbani! Ɓǝ̀ ǝn sǝlǝ ama tárrám shamna nǝ̀ wal-luio ka, pà mǝ nǝ banggo re?>>  
\v 10 Osso Dauda ɗì Jonatan ama, <<Yana nǝ̀ banggam, ɓǝ̀ tárró nyesǝô cau nǝ bumlulla ka?>>  
\v 11 Jonatan banggi Dauda ama, <<Yiu ɓǝ̀ sǝm o a patal.>> 
\p Lang à warina a patal ka,  
\v 12 Jonatan banggi Dauda ama, <<Yahweh Ɓakuli mala Isǝrayila nǝ̀ duk mǝ'nakún mem. Liwi nǝ bu-pwari kǝla man ko liawo ka, mǝ nǝ nacau nǝ tárrám ace súrǝ̀ mana nda ɗenyicau male amuro. Ɓǝ̀ tárrám ngga ndanǝ ɓabum mala lǝmdǝo earmúrú ka, mǝ nǝ túrban nǝ cau ɓǝà banggo.  
\v 13 Sǝ ɓǝ̀ tárrám nanǝ ɓabum mala pakko mǝɓane ka, ɓǝ̀ Yahweh ɓashiam, yì mǝnana ɓǝ̀ ǝn banggo cè, sǝ ǝn tasǝo a o aɓa dorǝpwala raka. Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh pa atò kǝla mǝnana pà atà tárrám ngga.  
\v 14 Ado mǝnana mǝ ndanǝ yilǝmu piu ka, lǝmdǝam pěmǝɓoarne aɓa earcearǝu mala Yahweh; sǝ ɓǝ̀ ǝn wú ka,  
\v 15 a pà wunǝ tamsǝ lǝmdǝì ɓala mem mǝnia yì pěmǝɓoarne ka ɗàng tàtǝ́k; awo, ko anzǝm mǝnana Yahweh twalnata aɓio-mǝbura kàng a ɓanza ka, ɓǝ̀ lidǝmba.>>  
\v 16 Nda Jonatan kùrcau nǝ ɓala mala Dauda, sǝ bang ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh sulǝ ɓashi male amur aɓiu-mǝbura mala Dauda.>>  
\v 17 Jonatan nyare kùrcau ɗǝm nǝ Dauda atàcau mala earcearǝu mǝnana ndanǝi arǝì ka. Yale Jonatan earce Dauda kǝla mǝnana earce yilǝmi ka.  
\v 18 Jonatan ne wi ama, <<Liwi ka nda lamsan mala Bǝsa Zongŋo; à nǝ̀ alto sǝ à pà nǝ̀ sǝno ɗàng, acemǝnana buno mô ka nǝ̀ nong atàrǝì.  
\v 19 Liawo ka, awu nǝ̀ nyar akaurǝa awu nǝ yiu a ban mǝnana a sǝmbǝrǝ kam, a pwari mǝnana gìr mǝnia kat ka tite nǝi ka. Awu nǝ sǝmbǝrǝ a nkanggari tali Ezel.\f + \fr 20:19 \fq a nkanggari tali Ezel \ft ko <<a ban mǝnana à ramba atali ka.>>\f* 
\v 20 Mǝ nǝ̀ túr amundi tàrú a ban talî, kǝla ɓè gìr na ǝn nggǝ earce tè ka.  
\v 21 Pǝlǝa mǝ nǝ túr muna ɓǝ̀ kya alamta amundinì. Ɓǝ̀ ǝn banggi wi ama, <Sǝni, amundinì na kana atà buo man ngga, pwania, sǝ wu nyare wu yiu> ka, ndaban lǝmdǝ ama awu nǝ auwa, sǝ kǝgìr mǝɓane pà nǝ̀ peo ɗang, mbak-kàngkàng Yahweh nakam ngga.  
\v 22 Sǝama ɓǝ̀ ǝn banggi muna ama, <Sǝni, amundinì ndako a dǝmba nǝ we> ka, lo o. Mǝno ka ndaban lǝmdǝ ama Yahweh tasǝnato wu o.  
\v 23 Amúr cau mǝnana sǝm bangŋi sǝnǝ we ka, Yahweh nda mǝ'nakún anre sǝm tàtǝ́k.>> 
\p  
\v 24 Nda Dauda sǝmbǝrǝ a patal ka. Lang lamsan mala Bǝsa Zongŋo yina ka, murǝm yi dumnǝdo ace ligirlina.  
\v 25 Murǝm do a bando male mǝnana dukiyi kam pwari-pwari ka, a ban mǝnana nda arǝ bumkurǝm sǝ kǝ sǝn ɓamǝsǝarǝia andǝ bando mala Jonatan ngga; sǝ Abna ka nda a bando male a nkanggari Murǝm. Sǝama bando mala Dauda ka, kǝɓwa pà kàm ɗàng.  
\v 26 Kat andǝ amani ka, Sawul na kǝ cau a pwari mǝno ɗàng, acemǝnana pàk ɗenyicau ama, <<Earka ɓè gìr kumǝnaban mǝnana tsǝ̀ngŋǝ́nà Dauda nda aɓa ɓeami ka, ɓafo nda aɓa ɓeami.>>  
\v 27 Sǝama lang ban fana, a ɓaria nongŋo mala lamsan mala Bǝsa Zongŋo ka, bando mala Dauda ka ndakam piu atàrǝì. Sǝ Sawul ɗì muna-ɓwabura male Jonatan ama, <<Mana tsǝa sǝ muna-ɓwabura mala Jeshi yiu a ligirlina yilung andǝ yalung ɗàng?>> 
\p  
\v 28 Jonatan earî Sawul ama, <<Dauda zǝmbam tsuk-tsuk ama mǝ pe wi njar nǝ̀ ká Betalami.  
\v 29 Banggam ama, <Earâm mǝ kyane, acemǝnana amǝ'ɓala ma'sǝm ndanǝ pà gìr'nkila a nggea-là ma'sǝm, sǝ mǝ'eambǝam ɓuaki arǝàm ama mǝ kyane. Adyan ngga, ɓǝ̀ ǝn kumǝna earmúrú a bano ka, nyem mǝ kyane, ace mǝnana mǝ kya sǝn amǝ'eambǝam ngga.> Mǝnia ka, nda gìr mǝnana tsǝa sǝ Dauda yiu a ligirlina mala murǝm raka.>> 
\p  
\v 30 Bum Sawul lul arǝ Jonatan, sǝ ne wi ama, <<We muna mala mā-bwena sǝ mā-gandǝban! Ən sǝlǝ mbak ama a twalna pù'atà muna-ɓwabura mala Jeshi, ace pè nggó andǝ ɓamuro kǝsǝkya re?  
\v 31 Ɓǝ̀ muna-ɓwabura mala Jeshi lidǝmba nǝdo nǝyilǝmu a ɓanza ka, a pà wunǝ duk murǝm ko awu nǝ yálmúr kǝ domurǝm ɗàng. Ado ka, tasǝ aburana ɓǝà kya yinǝam nǝi. Acemǝnana dumǝna púp à nǝ̀ wal-lui!>> 
\p  
\v 32 Jonatan nyesǝi tárrí cau ama, <<Man tsǝa sǝ à nǝ̀ wal-lui? Mana pàk le?>>  
\v 33 Pǝlǝa Sawul túr nzo arǝ Jonatan ama nǝ̀ tǝmi. Nda Jonatan sǝlǝa ama ɓafo tárrí shamna bumi ama nǝ̀ wal-lú Dauda ka.  
\v 34 Jonatan loapi ban ligirlina nǝ bumlulla. Li girlina a ɓaria pwari mala lamsan mala Bǝsa Zongŋo mǝno ɗàng, acemǝnana bumikiɗiki ace gìr kǝsǝkya mǝnana tárrí pàk arǝ Dauda ka. 
\p  
\v 35 Nǝ dǝmbari ka, Jonatan puro andǝ muna atè, sǝ à o patal ace je male andǝ Dauda.  
\v 36 Banggi muna ama, <<Ɓangŋa, kya alta amundi mǝnana ǝn túriá ka.>> Lang muna ɓangŋa nǝ̀ ká ka, Jonatan túr ɓè mundi a dǝmba nǝ mune.  
\v 37 Lang muna bingŋǝna ban mǝnana Jonatan túr mundi sǝ mundi kpa kam ngga, Jonatan loasǝ gì ne muna ama, <<Mundinì pà a dǝmba a ɓadǝmbo re?>>  
\v 38 Jonatan loasǝ gì banggi muna ama, <<Farǝo! Kya akaurǝa! Kǝa cam ɗàng!>> Muna mala Jonatan tàrki amundinì, sǝ nyar aban mǝtala-ɓala male.  
\v 39 (Sǝama muna súrǝ̀ kǝ cau amur gìr mǝnia ka ɗàng. Kǝ Jonatan andǝ Dauda na à súrǝ̀ gìr mana kǝ u ka.)  
\v 40 Pǝlǝa Jonatan pè muna nta andǝ amundi male, sǝ ne wi ama, <<Kyane, nyesǝ agir mǝnia ka a là.>> 
\p  
\v 41 Anzǝm mǝnana mune umna ka, Dauda purî ban mǝnana sǝmbǝrǝ kam a nkanggari ban ramba mala atali ka, kūndǝ nǝ ɓamǝsǝi a nzali, sǝ timuri kusǝ tàrú. Pǝlǝa à kùr rǝarǝia zǝp, sǝ à ɓua. Ɓua mala Dauda kútì mala Jonatan.  
\v 42 Jonatan banggi Dauda ama, <<O aɓa dorǝpwala, acemǝnana sǝm kǝm ngga, sǝm kánagìr aɓa lullǝ Yahweh ama, <Yahweh nǝ̀ duk mǝ'nakún anrem sǝnǝ we, sǝ anre ka amuna sǝm andǝ amǝ'kà sǝm.> >> Pǝlǝa Dauda lo o, sǝ Jonatan nyar a là. 
\c 21  
\s1 Dauda andǝ bǝredi mǝfele 
\p  
\v 1 Pǝlǝa Dauda wari aban Ahimale pǝris mǝnana ndanǝdo a Nop ka. Ahimale pur nǝ rǝɓǝla ace kum Dauda, sǝ ɗi ama, <<Mana tsǝa sǝ a nda nǝmurǝo, sǝ kǝɓwa pà atò ɗàng?>>  
\v 2 Sǝ Dauda eari Ahimale, pǝris ama, <<Murǝm tasǝam ace túrô mǝnana ama mǝ pak ka, sǝ nam ama, <Kǝɓwa ɓǝ̀ kǝa sǝlǝce kǝ gìr amur túrô mǝnana ǝn tasǝo ace, sǝ ǝn no wu pak ka ɗàng. Alaggana mem ngga, ǝn bangŋǝnia wia ban mǝnana ɓǝà kyan kàm ngga.>  
\v 3 Ado ka, mana à ndanǝi a buo? Pam agbatali bǝredi tongno, ko gìr mǝnana kat a ndanǝi ka.>>  
\v 4 Pǝlǝa pǝris pè Dauda eare ama, <<Ən panǝ bǝredi mǝnana nda ace koyan ngga ɗàng, shekǝ bǝredi mǝnana nda ace Ɓakuli\f + \fr 21:4 \fq bǝredi mǝnana nda ace Ɓakuli \ft ko <<bǝredi mǝfele>>\f* ka. Mǝ nǝ gandǝ po, ɓǝ̀ alaggana mô nong nǝ amamǝna adyan-tù raka.>>  
\v 5 Dauda eari pǝris ama, <<Aɓa mǝsǝcau, à tamsǝ sǝm arǝ amamǝna, aɓalǝ anongŋo tàrú mǝnia ka, kǝla mǝnana sǝm pakkiyi ka. A koya pwari sǝ ǝn pur ka, alaggana mem kǝ pǝndǝki rǝia nǝ amamǝna ɗang, ko ɓǝ̀ twalbǝri ma'sǝm ngga, mǝfele na raka. Sǝ mǝnia yalung mǝnana twalbǝri ma'sǝm ngga, mala túrô mǝfele na ka, à pà nǝ̀ pǝndǝki rǝia ɗàng!>>  
\v 6 Nda pǝris pe wi bǝredi mǝfele ka, acemǝnana kǝ ɓè bǝredi pà kàm abanì ɗàng, shekǝ bǝredi mala Ɓadǝm Yahweh,\f + \fr 21:6 \fq bǝredi mala Ɓadǝm Yahweh \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt Pǝris 24:8,9\ft .\f* mǝnana à pusǝì a ɓadǝm Yahweh, a pwari mǝnana à twali sǝ à nggaɗi nǝ bǝredi mǝnana bǝsa na arǝì ka. 
\p  
\v 7 Ɓè ɓwabura aɓalǝ aguro mala Sawul na kam a banì a mǝno yì pwari ka; à kasǝkuni aɓadǝm Yahweh. Lùllǝì nda Dowe ɓwa'Edom. Nda múr ayálgír mala Sawul.  
\v 8 Dauda banggi Ahimale ama, <<A ndanǝ nzo ko nggeabyau kani a buo le? Ən yinǝ nggeabyau mem ko ɓè kǝ girbura mem ɗang, acemǝnana túrô mǝnana murǝm túrǎm ɓǝn pe ka, kǝ earce ama ɓǝà pè tsuk-tsuk.>>  
\v 9 Pǝlǝa pǝris ear ama, <<Nggeabyau mala Golaya ɓwa'Filisti mana a wal-luí a Ɓangŋaban Ela ka, ndakani; à marǝki nǝ nggurbyau sǝ à tsǝi anzǝm efot. Ɓǝ̀ a kǝ earce ka, twali, acemǝnana ɓè kǝ nggeabyau pa akani ɗang shekǝ mǝno.>> Sǝ Dauda bang ama, <<Kǝ ɓè pa kǝla yì ɗang, pami.>> 
\s1 Dauda ɓangŋa o a Gat 
\p  
\v 10 Pǝlǝa Dauda lo, ɓanggi ban Sawul a mǝno yi pwari ka. O aban Akish murǝm Gat.  
\v 11 Amǝ'túró mala Akish ne wi ama, <<Mǝnia ka nda Dauda, murǝm mala nzalinì re? Yì nda ɓwa mǝnana à \f + \fr 21:11 \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt 1Sam 18:7; 29:5\ft .\f*tu'nggyal nǝ akiarǝia aɓa nggwam, à kǝ na ama: 
\q1 <<Sawul walna á-á male, 
\q2 sǝ Dauda walna á-á lum male ka re?>> 
\p  
\v 12 Sǝ Dauda tsǝk acau mǝnia ka a ɓabumi, sǝ ɓangciu bwali kǝ̀rkǝ́r arǝ Akish, murǝm Gat.  
\v 13 Nggaɗi ɓeali aɓadǝmbia, sǝ acemǝnana nda a ɓabuia ka, ɓosǝki rǝì kǝla mǝmúrpǝlǝa, kǝ cangi rǝ akún bankutio, sǝ nying ntāra kúni kǝ solǝ a mbotakuni.  
\v 14 Pǝlǝa Akish ne amǝ'túró male ama, <<Wu sǝni, ɓwabure ka ɓanggina! Mana tsǝa sǝ wu yinǝi abanam?  
\v 15 Ən ɗwanyi amǝɓanggya sǝ wu yinǝam nǝ mǝnia yì ɓwa ka ɓǝ̀ kǝ pakki agir kǝla mǝɓanggya aɓadǝmbam le? Dumǝna púp ama mǝnia yì ɓwa ka nǝ̀ yiu a ɓala mem le?>> 
\c 22  
\s1 Dauda o a Adulam andǝ Mizpa 
\p  
\v 1 Pǝlǝa Dauda nying Gat, sǝ ɓangŋa o a npu mala Adullam. Lang amǝ'eambi andǝ amǝ'ɓala mala tárrí kat ok cè ka, à wari kano a baní.  
\v 2 Aɓwana mana kat à nda aɓata parban, ko nǝ tangna amúrià, ko amana bumia pwasǝ raka, à wario, à ram rǝia a baní, sǝ duk mǝ'sàrǝ̀ban amúrià. Ndanǝ aburana kǝla gbǝman-ine atè. 
\p  
\v 3 Sǝ Dauda loapi ban mǝno ka, o a Mizpa a nzali Mowap. Akano ka, banggi murǝm Mowap ama, <<Ida, earâm ɓǝ ǝn nying tárrám andǝ nggem ɓǝà duk kani atò, she ɓǝ̀n súrǝ́nà rǝ gir mǝnana Ɓakuli nǝ pa acem ngga.>>  
\v 4 Nda Dauda nyia à do atà murǝm mala Mowap ka; à do atè arǝ apwari mǝnana kat Dauda na aban sǝmbǝrǝ a ban-mǝcandǝe ka. 
\p  
\v 5 Pǝlǝa mǝɓangnǝa mala Ɓakuli, mana à tunǝki ama Gad ka, banggi Dauda ama, <<Kǝa duk kani a ban-mǝcandǝe ɗàng. Lo o aɓa nzali Yahuda.>> Nda Dauda nying banì, sǝ o a ndà-nggun a Heret ka. 
\s1 Sawul wal-lú apǝris a Nop 
\p  
\v 6 Adyan ngga, Sawul yi ok ama, ban mǝnana Dauda andǝ aɓwana male na kam ngga, à kumǝni. A pwari mǝno ka Sawul na aban dumnǝdo, nǝ nkongŋo a buì, a tǝr nggun zāmbo, amur ɓè mgbangban a Gibiya, atārǝia andǝ amǝgulo male kat, aban came a nkanggari.  
\v 7 Pǝlǝa Sawul banggia wia ama, <<Wu kwakikir wun, wun aburana mala Benjami! Wu kǝ sǝni kǝla muna-ɓwabura mala Jeshi nǝ̀ pè koyan atà wun ngga aɓaban-rya andǝ aɓaban mala anggun-anap le? Wu kǝ sǝni kǝla nǝ̀ tsǝk wun kat, wun nǝ̀ duk amǝdǝmba mala aɓwana á-pas andǝ amǝdǝmba mala aɓwana gbǝman-pas le?  
\v 8 Mǝnia ka, nda gìr mǝnana tsǝa sǝ wu kpapikunarǝ wun amuram ngga re? Ko kǝ ɓwa mwashat banggam, lang muna-ɓwabura mem kurkunarǝia andǝ muna-ɓwabura mala Jeshi ka ɗàng. Yale kǝ ɓwa pà kàm atà wun mana kǝ ɗenyinǝ mim, ko nǝ̀ banggam ama, muna-ɓwabura mem soakita mǝturo mem ɓǝ̀ kùmsǝ arǝàm, amur njar, kǝla mana kǝ pàk yalung ngga ɗàng.>> 
\p  
\v 9 Pǝlǝa Dowe, ɓwa'Edom, mana nda aban came atà amǝgulo mala Sawul ka, bang ama: <<Ən sǝn muna-ɓwabura mala Jeshi, yiu aban Ahimale, muna-ɓwabura mala Ahitup mana a Nop ka.  
\v 10 Pǝlǝa Ahimale ɗì Yahweh ace súrǝ̀ gir mǝnana Dauda nǝ̀ pàk ka; ɗǝm ngga pè wi girlina, andǝ nggeabyau mala Golaya, ɓwa'Filisti.>> 
\p  
\v 11 Pǝlǝa murǝm túrban ɓǝà tunǝ pǝris Ahimale, muna-ɓwabura mala Ahitup, andǝ aburana mǝnana kat amǝɓala male na, sǝ à nda ka apǝris a Nop ka. Sǝ yia kat ka, à yiu aban murǝm.  
\v 12 Pǝlǝa Sawul bang ama, <<Kwakikiro ado, we muna-ɓwabura mala Ahitup.>> Pǝlǝa yì ka, pa eare ma, <<E, ɓwamǝgule mem.>>  
\v 13 Sawul banggi wi ama, <<Palang sǝ wu kpapikunarǝ wun amuram, we, wunǝ mǝno yì muna-ɓwabura mala Jeshi ka. A pe wi girlina andǝ nggeabyau, sǝ a ɗì Ɓakuli aceì, mǝnana tsǝa longŋǝna arǝàm ace kùmsǝâm, kǝla mǝno kǝ pàk yalung ngga?>> 
\p  
\v 14 Pǝlǝa Ahimale pe murǝm eare ama, <<Yana atà amǝtúró mô kat, mǝnana ndanǝ mǝsǝcau kǝla Dauda, mana nda nkil murǝm, sǝ nda ɓwamǝgule amur amǝ'yáltò, sǝ à kǝ twali nǝ gulo a ɓala mò ka?  
\v 15 Sǝ mǝno yi pwari ka, nda pwari mana ǝn tita ɗì Ɓakuli aceì ka le? Awo, ɓǝ̀ murǝm ɓǝkǝa tsǝki guro male cau arǝì ko arǝ kǝ ɓwa atà amǝɓala mala tárrí ɗàng. Mim guro mò ka, ǝn súrǝ̀ kǝgir amur mǝnia yì gìr kat ka ɗàng, ko bǝti.>> 
\p  
\v 16 Sǝ murǝm ngga, bang ama, <<Dumǝna púp, awu nǝ wǔ, we Ahimale, andǝ amǝɓala mala tárró kat!>> 
\p  
\v 17 Osso murǝm banggi amǝ'yáltè mana à cam a nkanggari ka, ama, <<Wu pǝlǝ rǝ wun, wu wal-luia, yia apǝris mala Yahweh, acemǝnana yia gbal ka, buia na atà Dauda! À sǝlǝna ama, kǝ ɓang nǝ ɓangŋa, sǝ à banggam ɗàng.>> Sǝama, amǝtúró mala murǝm ear ama, à nǝ̀ loasǝ buia, à nǝ̀ wal apǝris mala Yahweh ɗàng. 
\p  
\v 18 Pǝlǝa murǝm banggi Dowe ama, <<Pǝlǝ rǝo, wal apǝris.>> Nda Dowe, ɓwa'Edom, pǝlǝa sǝ wal apǝris. Wal-lú aburana lumi-tongno-nong-tàrú-bwamdǝ-tongno (85), mana à oasǝ efot mala nggubyau linǝn arǝia ka.  
\v 19 Ɗǝm ngga Sawul wal-lú aɓwana mǝnana à ndanǝdo a Nop, nggea-là mala apǝris ka, nǝ kún nggeabyau: aburana andǝ amamǝna, amuna andǝ abangna-muna, andǝ andá, andǝ amǝdambǝriso, andǝ anzur andǝ ambul; yià kat ka, wal-luia nǝ kún nggeabyau. 
\p  
\v 20 Sǝama, mwashat atà amuna-burana mala Ahimale, muna-ɓwabura mala Ahitup mana à tunǝki ama Abiyata ka, ɓangŋa auwa, o atà Dauda.  
\v 21 Sǝ Abiyata kya banggi Dauda ama, Sawul walna-lú apǝris mala Yahweh.  
\v 22 Pǝlǝa Dauda banggi Abiyata ama, <<Lang ǝn sǝn Dowe, ɓwa'Edom, a mǝno yì ban a pwari mǝno ka, ǝn sǝlǝa nǝma mbak-kàngkàng, nǝ̀ nggá ne Sawul. Ado ka, mǝ nda ǝn tsǝa, sǝ à wal-lú aɓwana kat a ɓala mala tárró ka.  
\v 23 Duk kani atàm; cè ɓangciu pàkkô ɗàng. Ɓwa mǝnana kǝ earce ama nǝ̀ wal-luio ka, ndaban ɓariki nǝ̀ wal-luem gbal. We ka, awu nǝ kum auwa abanam.>> 
\c 23  
\s1 Dauda amsǝ nggea-là Keyila 
\p  
\v 1 Aɓwana banggi Dauda ama, <<Sǝni, amǝ'Filisti naban munǝo arǝ nggea-là Keyila,\f + \fr 23:1 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Jes 15:44\ft .\f* sǝ à ndaban iu mǝssa arǝ akatǝra.>>  
\v 2 Nda Dauda ɗì Yahweh ama, <<Mǝ kya munǝ arǝ amǝ'Filisti le?>> Sǝ Yahweh ne Dauda ama, <<Kyane, wal amǝ'Filisti, sǝ wu amsǝ Keyila.>>  
\v 3 Sǝama aburana mala Dauda ne wi ama, <<Sǝni, akani aɓa Yahuda ka, sǝm nda aɓa ɓangciu. Gìrnî nǝ̀ ɓikipa ɓǝ̀ sǝm o a Keyila nǝ munǝo arǝ amǝ'lwa mala amǝ'Filisti ka!>>  
\v 4 Pǝlǝa Dauda nyar ɗǝm alta nê mala Yahweh amúr cê. Sǝ Yahweh nyare banggi Dauda ama, <<Lo, kya a Keyila, acemǝnana Mǝ nǝ túr amǝ'Filisti a ɓabuo.>> 
\p  
\v 5 Nda Dauda andǝ aburana male wari a Keyila, sǝ à munǝ-munǝo andǝ amǝ'Filisti. Dauda wal amǝ'Filisti nǝ walban mǝgule, sǝ à pwan agirkusǝu malea. Anggo sǝ Dauda amsǝ aɓwana mana à ndanǝdo a Keyila ka. 
\p  
\v 6 (Adyan ngga Abiyata muna-ɓwabura mala Ahimale ka ɓangŋǝna yina aban Dauda a Keyila; yina nǝ efot a bui.)  
\v 7 Aɓwana banggi Sawul ama Dauda yina a Keyila. Pǝlǝa Sawul na ama, <<Ɓakuli túrnì a ɓabuam; acemǝnana kasǝnakun ɓamúrì nǝ kutio male a nggea-là mǝnana ndanǝ akúnla mana à peǎ nǝ agara-bolo ka.>>  
\v 8 Acemani ka, Sawul tunǝ amǝ'lwa male kat, sǝ banggia wia ama, ɓǝà kya a Keyila, ɓǝà gumbǝli Dauda andǝ aburana male. 
\p  
\v 9 Lang Dauda ok ama Sawul naban kanì mǝɓike arǝì ka, ne Abiyata pǝris ama, <<Yinǝ efot kani!>>  
\v 10 Pǝlǝa Dauda pakhiwi ama, <<We Yahweh, Ɓakuli mala Isǝrayila, mim guro mò ka, ǝn ongŋǝna ama mbak-kàngkàng Sawul naban alte nǝ̀ yiu a Keyila ace kiɗiki nggea-lê, atàcau mem.  
\v 11 Aɓwana mala Keyila nǝ̀ túrǎm a ɓabui le? Sawul nǝ̀ yiu kǝla mana mim guro mò ok ka le? We Yahweh Ɓakuli mala Isǝrayila, ida banggam mim guro mò!>> Pǝlǝa Yahweh pe wi eare ama, <<Sawul nǝ̀ yiu.>> 
\p  
\v 12 Dauda ɗì Yahweh ama, <<Aɓwana mala Keyila nǝ̀ túrǎm sǝnǝ aburana mem a ɓabù Sawul le?>> Pǝlǝa Yahweh eari wi ama, <<À nǝ̀ túr wun a ɓabui.>> 
\p  
\v 13 Nda Dauda andǝ aburana male mǝnana lakkì malea na kǝla gbǝman-tongno-nong-mwashat (600) ka, à lo sǝ à nying Keyila; à gali arǝ abân mǝnana kat à gandǝ wari kam ngga. Lang à banggi Sawul ama Dauda ɓangŋǝna nyingŋǝna Keyila ka, tamsǝ ká male abanì. 
\p  
\v 14 Dauda do aɓalǝ ampù a ɓabondo, sǝ ueo aɓa nzali múr ankono a ɓabondo Zif.\f + \fr 23:14 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Jes 15:24\ft .\f* Sawul camarǝ alta Dauda koya pwari, sǝ Ɓakuli ka, túr Dauda a ɓabuì ɗàng. 
\s1 Sawul pǝrta Dauda 
\p  
\v 15 Lang Dauda na a Horesh a ɓabondo Zif ka, ok ama Sawul purna ace alte nǝ̀ twal yilǝmi.  
\v 16 Sǝ Jonatan muna-ɓwabura mala Sawul lo wari aban Dauda a Horesh, sǝ ɓakɓabum Dauda ɓǝ̀ kum rǝcandǝa nǝban Ɓakuli.\f + \fr 23:16 \ft Sǝni gbal aɓa: \xt 1Sam 30:6\ft .\f* 
\v 17 Banggi wi ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ ɓangciu ɓǝkǝa pakko ɗàng! Acemǝnana bù tárrám Sawul pà nǝ̀ kumo ɗang. Awu nǝ yálmúr Isǝrayila, sǝ mǝ nǝ duk mǝkwaɗito. \f + \fr 23:17 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 1Sam 24:20\ft .\f*Ko tárrám Sawul nǝnggearǝì ka, sǝlǝna mǝnia ka.>>  
\v 18 Sǝ yià mǝnia ɓari ka, à kùrcau aɓadǝm Yahweh; Dauda ueo a Horesh, sǝ Jonatan o a là. 
\p  
\v 19 Pǝlǝa \f + \fr 23:19 \ft Sǝni gbal aɓa: \xt 1Sam 26:1\ft .\f*amǝ'Zif wari aban Sawul a Gibiya sǝ à ne wi ama, <<Dauda pà aban sǝmbǝrǝa aɓalǝ sǝm aɓa mpù a Horesh, a mgbangban mala Hakila nǝ njar-kunmur mala Jeshimon re?  
\v 20 Adyan ngga, sulǝo yiu, we murǝm. A pwari mǝnana kat a earce ka, sulǝo yiu, sǝ sǝm ngga, sǝm nǝ̀ pàk gìr mǝnana sǝm nǝ̀ pàk ka, sǝm nǝ̀ tasǝì a ɓabuo.>> 
\p  
\v 21 Sawul nyesǝia wia cau ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh tsǝka wun bù, acemǝnana wu lǝ́mdǝ́nàm pěmǝɓoarne.  
\v 22 Ida, wu kyane, wu ɓǝltacê pepè. Wu súrǝ̀, sǝ wu sǝn ban mǝnana kǝ wari kam ngga, andǝ yana sǝni abanì, acemana à bangŋǝ́nàm ama yì ka, mǝkutan na kǝ̀rkǝ́r.  
\v 23 Wu sǝni, sǝ wu súrǝ̀ abân-sǝmbǝrǝa mǝnana kat kǝ sǝmbǝrǝ kam ngga; sǝ wu nyar abanam nǝ mǝsǝrǝ cau. Pǝlǝa mǝ nǝ ká sǝnǝa wun. Ɓǝ̀ nda aɓa bu-nzali man ngga, mǝ nǝ bǝlkusǝi aɓalǝ anggurkwar mala Yahuda kat.>> 
\p  
\v 24 Nda aɓwana mǝno lo, sǝ à aki Sawul dǝmba aban ká a Zif ka. Adyan ngga, Dauda andǝ aburana male na a ɓabondo Mawon, a ɓawanban nǝ njar-kunmur mala Jeshimon.  
\v 25 Sawul andǝ aburana male wari a alta Dauda. Sǝ lang Dauda okce ka, ɓunno wari a ban mbisong, sǝ kya do a ɓabondo Mawon. Lang Sawul ok anggo ka, wari a ɓabondo Mawon ace pǝrta Dauda.  
\v 26 Sawul wari a buì mwashat mala nkono mana Dauda nakam ngga, sǝ Dauda andǝ aburana male ka, à nda a ɓè buì mala nkonoe. Dauda na aban farǝì nǝ̀ apî Sawul, acemǝnana Sawul andǝ aburana male ka, à ndaban ɓariki à nǝ̀ gumbǝli Dauda andǝ aburana male, ace mǝnana à nǝ̀ bwalia ka.  
\v 27 Sǝama ɓè mǝ'na-túrbân yiu aban Sawul ama, <<Yiu akaurǝa, acemǝnana amǝ'Filisti warina nǝ munǝo arǝ aɓwana aɓa nzali ma'sǝm!>> 
\p  
\v 28 Nda Sawul nying pǝ̀rta Dauda, sǝ nyare o aban munǝo arǝ amǝ'Filisti ka. Acemani ka, à tunǝ ban mǝno ama Sela Hamalekot.\f + \fr 23:28 \fq Sela Hamalekot \ft ka nda Mbisong mala Gauwa ko Àwá.\f* 
\v 29 Pǝlǝa Dauda loapi ban mǝno ka, sǝ o kya do aɓalǝ ampù a Engedi. 
\c 24  
\s1 Dauda ɓinǝ twal yilǝmi Sawul 
\p  
\v 1 Lang Sawul nyàrǝ́nì pǝ̀rta amǝ'Filisti a munǝo ka, aɓwana banggi wi ama, <<Sǝni, Dauda na a ɓabondo Engedi.>>  
\v 2 Pǝlǝa Sawul twal aburana á-tàrú mǝnana tarkia aɓa Isǝrayila kat ka, sǝ o andǝ aburana male aban alta Dauda tù a ban atali mala ambul bondo.  
\v 3 Amur njar ka, yiu a ban adomwan mala anzur, sǝ abanì ka, ɓè gumi-ɓa'tali nakam. Sawul kuti aɓalǝi ace mǝnana nǝ̀ nongŋo ace usǝlǝ aulǝa\f + \fr 24:3 \fq usǝlǝ aulǝa \ft Ibǝru bang ama ace <<kùmsǝ akusǝi>> sǝ ɓalǝi ka nda <<doagung.>>\f* ka. Sǝ a ɓaɓalǝu mala mǝno yì gumi-ɓa'tali ka, Dauda andǝ aburana male na kam aban sǝmbǝrǝa.  
\v 4 Sǝ aburana mala Dauda ne wi ama, <<Sǝni, man ngga nda pwari mǝnana Yahweh banggo ama, <Mǝ nǝ tasǝ ɓio-mǝbura a ɓabuo, sǝ awu nǝ pàkki wi gìr mana a sǝni nda ɓoarô ka.> >> Pǝlǝa Dauda lo eamdikiban sǝ kasǝ kún nggea-daura mala Sawul.  
\v 5 Nǝnzǝ́mò ka, ɓabum Dauda tùllì, acemǝnana kasǝ kún nggea-daura mala Sawul ka.  
\v 6 Dauda banggi aburana male ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh twalbani ɓǝ̀ mǝ nǝ pàkki ɓwamǝgule mem, mana Yahweh ɗārǝi ka, mǝnia yì gìr, ama mǝ nǝ loasǝ buam arǝì ka.>>  
\v 7 Anggo sǝ Dauda pwanɓabum aburana male nǝ amǝnia yì acau ka, sǝ earia wia à lo arǝ Sawul nǝ munǝo ɗàng. Pǝlǝa Sawul lo, purî gumi-ɓa'tali mǝno, sǝ bwal njar o. 
\p  
\v 8 Anzǝm mǝno ka, Dauda lo sǝ purî gumi-ɓa'tali. Loasǝ gì tunǝ Sawul ama, <<Ɓwamǝgule mem, murǝm!>> Lang Sawul pǝlǝ mǝsǝi a nzǝmi ka, Dauda ɓun amúr ankūnǝi sǝ ti múrí a nzali.  
\v 9 Dauda banggi Sawul ama, <<Palang sǝ a kǝ kwakikiro arǝ acau mala aɓwana ama, <Dauda naban alte nǝ̀ pàkkô mǝɓane?>  
\v 10 A pwari mǝnia ka, a sǝnǝni nǝ mǝsǝo ama Yahweh tasǝo yalung a ɓabuam a gumi-ɓa'tali; aɓea aɓwana bang ama ɓǝ̀n wal-luio, sǝama ǝn nyio nǝyilǝmu. Ən bang nǝma, <Pà mǝ nǝ loasǝ buam arǝ ɓwamǝgule mem ɗàng, acemǝnana yì ka Yahweh ɗārǝi.>  
\v 11 Sǝni, tárrám, kún nggea-daura mô mana ǝn kasǝi ka, ndya a buam ngga! Lang ǝn kasǝ kún nggea-daura mô ka, ǝn wal-luio ɗàng. Acemani ka, sǝlǝa sǝ ɓǝ̀ kpako ama, ǝn pà aban kanì mǝɓane ko mgbicau ɗàng. Kat andǝ amani ama ǝn pakko cauɓikea raka, a ndaban kùmsǝâm ace twal yilǝmem.  
\v 12 Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh pàk ɓashi anrem sǝnǝ we, sǝ ɓǝ̀ Yahweh mbweo akúnì amǝɓane mǝnana a pakkam ngga, sǝama mim ngga buam pà nǝ̀ jeo nǝ mǝɓane ɗàng.  
\v 13 Nda kǝla cau pasǝlǝe mǝnana ɓara-ɓara ka ama, <Ɓealɓikea kǝ pur nǝban amǝ'ɓealɓikea.> Sǝama mim ngga, buam pà nǝ̀ jeo nǝ mǝɓane ɗàng.  
\v 14 Arǝ yana sǝ murǝm mala amǝ'Isǝrayila puro nǝ̀ ká munǝo? Ya ɓwa na a kǝ pǝrte? Atà luna nvwa! Atà nkungga!  
\v 15 Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh duk mǝɓashi sǝ ɓǝ̀ kasǝcau anrem sǝnǝ we. Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh sǝngi ɓá cau mem sǝ ɓǝ̀ bǝlkunam, sǝ ɓǝ̀ amsǝam a ɓabuo!>> 
\p  
\v 16 Lang Dauda mal ne Sawul acau man ngga, Sawul na ama, <<Gio nda man le, munem Dauda?>> Kara Sawul loasǝ gì ɓua.  
\v 17 Sǝ banggi Dauda ama, <<Cauɓoarna mô kútí mem, acemǝnana a pàngŋǝ́nàm mǝɓoarne, kat andǝ amani ama ǝn pakko mǝɓike ka.  
\v 18 A bangŋǝna gìr mǝɓoarne mǝnana a pàkkam a pwari mǝnia yalung ngga; Yahweh túrǎm a ɓabuo, sǝama a wal-luim ɗàng.  
\v 19 Ɓǝ̀ ɓwa kum ɓimǝbura ka, nǝ̀ nying ɓimǝbura ɓǝ̀ u jam le? Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh mbweo akúnì nǝ mǝɓoarne ace gìr mǝɓoarne mǝnana a pàkkam, a pwari man yalung ngga.  
\v 20 Sǝni, adyan ngga ǝn sǝlǝna ama mbak-kàngkàng awu nǝ̀ duk murǝm, sǝ domurǝm mala Isǝrayila ka, nǝ̀ kum kusǝ came pepè a ɓabuo.  
\v 21 Ado ka, kánbam aɓa lullǝ Yahweh ama a pà wu nǝ̀ wal-lú amunem andǝ amǝ'kem ɗàng, sǝ a pà wu nǝ esǝki lullǝam a ɓala mala tárrám ɗàng.>> 
\p  
\v 22 Nda Dauda kánbì Sawul ka. Pǝlǝa Sawul nyare o a là, sǝ Dauda andǝ aburana male nyare à o a ban sǝmbǝrǝa malea, a mpù. 
\c 25  
\s1 Lú mala Samuyila 
\p  
\v 1 Samuyila paklú sǝ Isǝrayila kat ramba abanɓwáná, à pak-bumkiɗikea aceì, sǝ à tsǝì a ɓala male a Rama. Pǝlǝa Dauda lo wari a ɓabondo Paran.\f + \fr 25:1 \fq ɓabondo Paran \ft ngga nda ɓabondo Mawon.\f* 
\s1 Dauda andǝ Nabal sǝ Abigiyel 
\p  
\v 2 Ɓè ɓwabura nakam a Mawon mǝnana nggaliki male na a Kamel ka; ɓwabure ka mǝgǝna na kǝ̀rkǝ́r. Ndanǝ anzur á-tàrú andǝ ambul á-mwashat. A bàkú mǝno ka ndaban mwa nyang anzur male a Kamel.  
\v 3 Lullǝ ɓwabure nda Nabal, sǝ lullǝ māmí nda Abigiyel. Mǝnia yì ɓwama ka kwaro sǝ ɓoarnsari; sǝ ɓwabure ka mǝ'lullô na sǝ mǝ'ɓealɓana na. Yì ka mǝ'kà Kalip na. 
\p  
\v 4 Dauda ka nda a ɓabondo lang ok ama Nabal naban mwa nyang anzur male ka.  
\v 5 Pǝlǝa tasǝ alaggana lum, sǝ banggia wia ama, <<Wu kya a Kamel aban Nabal, sǝ wu makkìkun nǝ lullǝàm.  
\v 6 Pǝlǝa wun nǝ̀ banggi wi ama, <Ɓǝ̀ yilǝmo sauwa, sǝ ɓǝ̀ dorǝpwala pa atò, andǝ ɓala mò andǝ koman mǝnana kat a ndanǝi ka!  
\v 7 Ən ok ama aburana mò naban mwako nyang anzur mô. Mǝnana ayálgír mò na atà sǝm ngga, sǝm pàkkia wia mǝɓane ɗàng, sǝ aɓalǝ anonggio mǝnana kat à nda a Kamel ka, kǝgìr malea ɓwar ɗàng.  
\v 8 Ɗì ka alaggana mô, sǝ yià ka, à nǝ̀ banggo. Acemani ka, eare ɓǝ̀ alaggana mem kum earmúrú a mǝsǝo, acemǝnana sǝm yiu a pwari mala lilí-banɓoarnado. Ida, pè aguro mò andǝ munio Dauda gìr mǝnana a ndanǝi ado awu nǝ gandǝnǝ pea wia ka.> >> 
\p  
\v 9 Nda alaggana mala Dauda wario, sǝ à banggi Nabal acau mǝnia ka, aɓa lullǝ Dauda. Pǝlǝa à kúndǝô.  
\v 10 Sǝ Nabal earî alaggana mala Dauda ama, <<Yana nda Dauda, sǝ yana nda mǝnia yì muna-ɓwabura mala Jeshi ka? Aɓalǝ anonggio mǝnia ka, amuna-ɓala nakam pas mǝnana à ɓangŋa à nying amǝtala-ɓala malea ka.  
\v 11 Palang sǝ mǝ nǝ twal bǝredi mem, andǝ mùr mem, andǝ nyama mem mǝnana ǝn wal ace amǝ'mwa nyang nzur mem, sǝ mǝ nǝ pè aburana mǝnana ǝn súrǝ̀ ban mana à pùr kam raka.>> 
\p  
\v 12 Nda alaggana mala Dauda wulio, à o sǝ à nyare à yi banggi wi acau mǝnia ka kat.  
\v 13 Pǝlǝa Dauda banggi aburana male ama, <<Koya ɓwabura ka ɓǝ̀ kùr rǝi nǝ nggeabyau male!>> Nda sǝ koya ɓwabura ateà ka, kùr rǝi nǝ nggeabyau male. Dauda gbal ka kùr rǝi nǝ nggeabyau male. Aburana kǝla gbǝman-ine o atà Dauda, sǝ aburana gbǝman-ɓari ue ace ɗenyinǝ atwalo malea. 
\p  
\v 14 Sǝama mwashat aɓalǝ alaggana mala Nabal ne Abigiyel, mālá Nabal ama, <<Dauda tasǝ amǝ'na-túrbân mǝnana à pur a ɓabondo ka ace makki mǝtala-ɓala ma'sǝm kún, sǝ mǝtala-ɓala ma'sǝm ngga sanggia.  
\v 15 Amǝnia yì aburana ka, à pàkka sǝm mǝɓoarne kǝ̀rkǝ́r; kǝgìr mǝɓane kum sǝm ɗàng, sǝ kǝgìr ma'sǝm ɓwàr ɗàng a bàkú mǝno kat à nda atà sǝm a bondo ka.  
\v 16 Dù andǝ pwari, à dupa sǝm sheran, a bàkú mǝno kat sǝm nda atarǝ sǝm sǝnǝia aban yál anzur ka.  
\v 17 Ado ka sǝlǝa, sǝ wu pakɗenyicau amur gìr mǝnana nda ɓoaro wu pàk ka, acemǝnana gir'murmwana nakam amúr mǝtala-ɓala ma'sǝm andǝ ɓala male puppup. Sǝ yì mǝtala-ɓala ma'sǝm ngga, mǝ'ɓealɓana na, mǝnana ɓwa pà nǝ̀ gandǝnǝ nacau nǝi raka.>> 
\p  
\v 18 Nda Abigiyel farǝì, sǝ twal agbatali bǝredi gbǝman-ɓari, andǝ mùr-anap bàng ɓari, andǝ nyam anzur tongno mǝnana à lambi ka, andǝ mǝssa mǝnana à kàngŋì ka tasau tongno, andǝ dangŋanshi ɓǝla-anap mǝ'ime gbǝman-mwashat, andǝ kyak mala ɓǝla vwari gbǝman-ɓari, sǝ nongsǝia a nzǝm amǝdambǝriso.  
\v 19 Pǝlǝa ne amǝtúró male ama, <<Wu akàm dǝmba wu kyane. Mǝ nǝ kpata wun.>> Sǝama banggi burí, Nabal ɗàng. 
\p  
\v 20 Lang Abigiyel naban o a nzǝm mǝdambǝriso male sǝ yi sulǝ a ɓangŋaban anre ka ankono ka, kara sǝn Dauda andǝ aburana male ndya à kǝ sulǝ aban yiu nǝbani ka, sǝ à yi je.  
\v 21 Dauda ka bangŋǝni aburana male ama, <<Mǝsǝcau, nda ɓà sǝ ǝn yál gìr mǝnana kat mala ɓwabura mǝnia na ka a ɓabondo. Kǝɓwa iu kǝgir mǝnana male na ka ɗàng, sǝ ado ka, nyesǝnàm mǝɓike a kúnì mǝɓoarne.  
\v 22 Ɓǝ̀ Ɓakuli ɓashiam kǝ̀rkǝ́r, mim Dauda, ɓǝ̀ li nǝ dǝmbari, ǝn nying ko ɓwabura mwashat nǝyilǝmu piu, atà aɓwana mǝnana amale na ka.>> 
\p  
\v 23 Lang Abigiyel sǝn Dauda ka, sulǝî nzǝm mǝdambǝriso akaurǝa, sǝ ɓunno sǝ ti múrí a nzali aɓadǝm Dauda.  
\v 24 Kpa a kusǝ Dauda, sǝ bang ama, <<Ɓwamǝgule mem, ɓǝ̀ cauɓikê pa amuram! Sǝama ida earâm, mim guro mò, mǝ nacau nǝ we! Kwakikiro arǝ cau mem, mim guro mò!  
\v 25 Ida, ɓwamǝgule mem, kǝa tsǝkiro arǝ mǝnia yì mǝ'ɓealɓana, yì Nabal ka ɗàng, acemǝnana kǝla mǝnana lùllǝì pàk ka, anggo sǝ yì gbal ka pa. Lùllǝì nda Nabal,\f + \fr 25:25 \fq Nabal \ft ka ɓālǝi nda gǝmi.\f* sǝ gǝm ɓwa na; sǝama mim, guro mò ka, ǝn sǝn alaggana mǝnana we ɓwamǝgule mem, a tasǝ ka ɗàng. 
\p  
\v 26 <<Adyan ngga, ɓwamǝgule mem, mbak-kàngkàng Yahweh nakam, sǝ a nda kam nǝyilǝmu ka, Yahweh nda mǝnana tamsǝo arǝ sukki nkila andǝ mbweban akúnì gìr mǝnana à pàkkô ka. Acemani ka, ɓǝ̀ aɓiomǝbura andǝ aɓwana mana à kǝ alta pàkkô mǝɓane ka, pà kǝla Nabal.  
\v 27 Adyan ngga, ɓwamǝgule mem, ak mǝnia yì ɓoro, mim guro mò ǝn yinǝi ka, ace mǝnana wu pè alaggana mǝnana à nda atò ka.  
\v 28 Ida twalî guro mò ban cauɓikea male. Mǝnia ka nda acemǝnana mbak-kàngkàng Yahweh ka, nǝ̀ tamsǝkusǝ ɓala mala ɓwamǝgule mem.\f + \fr 25:28 \fq nǝ̀ tamsǝkusǝ ɓala mala ɓwamǝgule mem \ft ko <<nǝ̀ yál ɓwamǝgule mem andǝ amǝ'ɓala male tàtǝ́k>>\f* Sǝ acemǝnana ɓwamǝgule mem na arǝ munǝ amunǝo mala Yahweh ka, ɓǝà kǝa kum kǝ mǝɓike aɓalǝo ɗàng aɓa do-yilǝmu mô kat.  
\v 29 Ɓǝ̀ kǝɓwa lo ama nǝ̀ pǝrto ace twal yilǝmo ka, Yahweh Ɓakuli mô nǝ̀ mbuɓi yilǝmo aɓa luru yilǝmu male a baní. Sǝ yilǝmi aɓiomǝbura ka, nǝ̀ túrí kǝla túr tali nǝ ntamso.  
\v 30 Sǝ lang Yahweh pàngŋǝ́nì ɓwamǝgule mem koya gìr mǝɓoarne mǝnana pàcau ace amuro, sǝ twalǝno a dumǝna murǝm amúr Isǝrayila ka,  
\v 31 ɓwamǝgule mem pà nǝ̀ kum bumkiɗikea, ko múr-halǝkya ama a sukkina nkila mala amǝ'kunpwasǝa ko mala mbweban akúnì gìr mǝnana à pàkkô ka ɗàng. Sǝ lang Yahweh pano limurǝm ngga, ɗenyinǝ guro mò.>> 
\p  
\v 32 Pǝlǝa Dauda ne Abigiyel ama, <<Ɓwangsǝban ɓǝ̀ pa aban Yahweh, Ɓakuli mala Isǝrayila, mǝnana tasǝo yalung ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ sǝm yi je ka!  
\v 33 Tsǝkbu ɓǝ̀ pa amúr kwaro mò! Sǝ ɓǝ̀ Yahweh tsǝko bù, mǝnana a mgbaliam yalung arǝ sukki nkila, sǝ arǝ nyesǝ mǝɓane a kúnì mǝɓane ka.  
\v 34 Ɓǝ̀ ana raka, mbak-kàngkàng Yahweh Ɓakuli mala Isǝrayila nakam, mǝnana tamsǝam arǝ pakko mǝɓane ka, ɓǝ̀ a yiuma akaurǝa raka, ɓǝ́ kaniama ban nǝ̀ kwar ka, kǝɓwa pà kàm nǝ̀ ue nǝyilǝmu atà aburana mala Nabal ɗàng.>> 
\p  
\v 35 Pǝlǝa Dauda ak agir mǝnana Abigiyel yinǝi wi ka, sǝ ne wi ama, <<Nyare o a ɓala mò aɓa dorǝpwala. Sǝni, ǝn ongŋǝna cau mò, sǝ ǝn pano gìr mǝnana a zǝm ngga.>> 
\p  
\v 36 Lang Abigiyel nyar ka, yi kum Nabal ramna aɓwana a ɓala male aban lili-banɓoarnado, ulang lili-banɓoarnado mala amurǝma. Nabal ka ɓabumi na aɓa pakkiɗire sǝ mba-walni kǝ̀rkǝ́r. Acemani ka, Abigiyel ne wi kǝcau ɗàng she lang ban fana ka.  
\v 37 Nǝ dǝmbari lang Nabal nyarǝna aɓa hakkilo male ka, māmí Abigiyel banggi wi acau mǝnia kat; kara ɓabum Nabal tùmùr, yilǝmi o, sǝ shǐ kǝla tali.  
\v 38 Anzǝm nongŋo lum ngga, Yahweh koè, kara wǔ. 
\p  
\v 39 Lang Dauda ongŋǝna ama Nabal wuna ka, bang ama, <<Ɓwangsǝban ngga ɓǝ̀ pa aban Yahweh, mǝnana bǝlnakunam amúr gìr-kǝsǝkya mǝnana Nabal pàkkam, sǝ tamsǝnam, mim guro male, arǝ mǝɓike ka. Yahweh nyesǝ́nì Nabal túró-mǝɓike male a múrí.>> Pǝlǝa Dauda túrban sǝ bangcau nǝ Abigiyel, ace twale ɓǝ̀ duk māmí. 
\p  
\v 40 Lang amǝ'túró mala Dauda yiu aban Abigiyel a Kamel ka, à banggi wi ama, <<Dauda túr sǝm a bano, ama ɓǝ̀ sǝm kyan nǝ we a baní, wu pǝlǝ māmí.>>  
\v 41 Pǝlǝa Abigiyel lo, sǝ ɓun nǝ ɓamǝsǝi a nzali, sǝ na ama, <<Mim guro mò ka, mǝ nda mǝtúró ace lakki akusǝ amǝtúró mala ɓwamǝgule mem.>>  
\v 42 Osso Abigiyel lo akaurǝa, wario sǝ kya eau a nzǝm mǝdambǝriso, sǝ tongno atà amuna-mamǝna amǝ'túró-ɓala male o atè. Abigiyel o atà amǝ'na-túrbân mala Dauda, sǝ pǝlǝ mālá Dauda. 
\p  
\v 43 Dauda ka angŋa-dǝmba alna Ahinowam, ɓwama Jezǝril; yià mǝno kǝm ngga, à pǝlǝ amālá Dauda. 
\p  
\v 44 (Adyan ngga, Sawul twalna muna-ɓwama male, yì Mikal mǝnana mālá Dauda na ka, pànî Paltiyel\f + \fr 25:44 \fq Paltiyel \ft ko Palti.\f* muna-ɓwabura mala Layish, ɓwa Gallim.) 
\c 26  
\s1 Dauda ɓinǝ twal yilǝmi Sawul ɗǝm 
\p  
\v 1 \f + \fr 26:1 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 1Sam 23:19; Ang 54\ft .\f*Amǝ'Zif wari aban Sawul a Gibiya, sǝ à banggi wi ama, <<Dauda pà aban sǝmbǝrǝa amur muna-nkono Hakila, tù a ban Jeshimon re?>>  
\v 2 Nda Sawul lo sǝ sulǝo wari a ɓabondo Zif nǝ aburana á-tàrú mala Isǝrayila atè, ace alta Dauda a ɓabondo Zif.  
\v 3 Sawul tsǝk kàttì male amúr muna-nkono Hakila, mǝnana nda a nkanggari njargula a takuli mala Jeshimon ngga. Sǝ Dauda ka ue a ɓabondo. Lang sǝni ama Sawul yina atè a ɓabondo ace alte ka,  
\v 4 Dauda tasǝ amǝ'shenzǝban, sǝ à wario à kya bwalte ama mbak-kàngkàng Sawul yina. 
\p  
\v 5 Pǝlǝa Dauda lo sǝ wari a ban mǝnana Sawul bwal kàttì kam ngga; sǝ Dauda sǝn ban mǝnana Sawul andǝ Abna muna-ɓwabura mala Ner, yì mǝ'sàrǝ̀ban mala amǝ'lwa male nong kàm ngga. Sawul ka nong a tsùrú mala kàttì sǝ amǝ'lwa male gumbǝli.  
\v 6 Dauda nacau nǝ Ahimale ɓwa'Hitti andǝ Abishai, muna-ɓwabura mala Zeruya, mǝ'eam Jowap ama, <<Ya ɓwa na atà wun nǝ̀ ká atàm aban Sawul aɓa kàttì male?>> Abishai eari wi ama, <<Mǝ nǝ ká atò.>> 
\p  
\v 7 Nda Dauda andǝ Abishai wario sǝ à kya kúti a kàttì mala Sawul nǝ du, sǝ à sǝni ka, Sawul na a ntulo a tsùrú mala kàttì nǝ nzo male à kwaki a nzali, tù a ban ɓamuri. Sǝ Abna andǝ amǝ'lwa ka, à nongŋo à gumbǝlì aɓalǝu.  
\v 8 Abishai banggi Dauda ama, <<Yalung ngga, Yahweh túrna ɓiomǝbura a ɓabuo. Adyan ngga, ɗekiam mǝ zuɓi nǝ nzo ɓǝ̀ kya kútí a nzali, nǝ zuɓiban mwashat ɓǝ̀rɓǝ̀r, sǝ pà mǝ nǝ zuɓi ɓaria ɗàng.>> 
\p  
\v 9 Sǝama Dauda ne Abishai ama, <<Kǝa wal-lui ɗàng! Yana nǝ̀ loasǝ bui arǝ ɓwa mǝnana Yahweh tàrni ka, sǝ ɓwe nǝ̀ ɗwanyi kumcau?>>  
\v 10 Sǝ Dauda lidǝmba nǝ nacau ama, <<Mbak-kàngkàng Yahweh na kam nǝyilǝmu ka, Yahweh nǝnggearǝì nǝ̀ wali, ko ana raka lang pwari male karǝna ka nǝ̀ wǔ, ko nǝ̀ ká munǝo sǝ à nǝ̀ wal-luí kàm.  
\v 11 Sǝ mim ngga, ɓǝ̀ Yahweh twalbani mǝnana mǝ loasǝ buam arǝ ɓwa mana Yahweh tàrni ka! Ado ka, twal nzo male andǝ du-mùr male, sǝ ɓǝ̀ sǝm o!>>  
\v 12 Nda Dauda twal nzo andǝ du-mùr mǝnana à cam a múr Sawul ka, sǝ à nying ban mǝno. Kǝɓwa sǝnia ko sǝlǝce ɗàng, sǝ kǝɓwa ateà loapi ntulo ɗàng, acemǝnana \f + \fr 26:12 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Tite 2:21; 15:12\ft .\f*nggea ntulo mǝlime nǝban Yahweh yi sulǝ amúrià. 
\p  
\v 13 Pǝlǝa Dauda o a ɓè buì sǝ kya cam zak amúr mgbangban; ban mǝnana Dauda cam kam ngga tètarǝì ban mǝnana à Sawul nakam ngga.  
\v 14 Dauda loasǝ gì sǝ tunǝ amǝ'lwa mala Sawul, sǝ tunǝ Abna muna-ɓwabura mala Ner ama, <<A pà wunǝ earam re, Abna?>> Pǝlǝa Abna ear ama, <<A nda yana le, mǝnana a kǝ tunǝ murǝm ngga?>>  
\v 15 Dauda ne Abna ama, <<A nda ɓwabura re? Sǝ yana kam kǝla we a Isǝrayila? Palang sǝ a yál ɓwamǝgule mò, murǝm ɗàng? Acemǝnana ɓeɓwa yiu nǝ̀ wal murǝm, ɓwamǝgule mò.  
\v 16 Gìr mǝnia a pè ka, pànǝ ɓoaro ɗàng! Mbak-kàngkàng Yahweh nakam ngga, a karǝna ɓǝà wal-luio, acemǝnana a yál ɓwamǝgule mò mǝnana Yahweh tàrì ka ɗàng! Ado ka sǝnban! Nzo andǝ du-mùr mala murǝm mǝnana à cam a múrí ka, à nda ke?>> 
\p  
\v 17 Lang Sawul bwalta gì Dauda ka, ɗiban ama, <<Gio nda man le, munem Dauda?>> Dauda eari wi ama, <<E, giem na ɓwamǝgule mem, murǝm.>>  
\v 18 Dauda lidǝmba nǝ nacau ama, <<Palang sǝ ɓwamǝgule mem kǝ pǝrtam, mim guro male? Mana ǝn pà? Ya gìr mǝɓane na ǝn pa?  
\v 19 Adyan ngga, ɓǝ̀ ɓwamǝgule mem, yì murǝm ok acau mem, mim guro male. Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh nda mǝnana soakito arǝàm ngga, ɓǝ̀ Yahweh ak pàgir.\f + \fr 26:19 \fq pàgir \ft mala pisǝ muku gìr mala pà rǝmban mǝɓoarne ace pwasǝbum Yahweh\f* Sǝ ɓǝ̀ aɓwana na ka, ɓǝ̀ suban sulǝ amúria nǝban Yahweh; \f + \fr 26:19 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 2Sam 14:16; 20:19; 21:3\ft .\f*acemǝnana à pǝrnam yalung, ama mǝ nggá kum nzali liɓala mala Yahweh ɗàng, sǝ à bangŋǝ́nà ama, <O, kya peri aban aɓea aɓakuli.>  
\v 20 Adyan ngga, kǝa eare ɓǝà sukki nkilem a nzali mǝnana nda kuko nǝ ɓadǝm Yahweh ka ɗàng, acemǝnana murǝm mala Isǝrayila purna ace alta nkungga kǝla mana ɓwa kǝ alta nyal amúr ankono ka.>> 
\p  
\v 21 Pǝlǝa Sawul na ama, <<Ən pángŋǝ̀nà cauɓikea. Nyare, munem Dauda. Pà mǝ nǝ pakko kǝgìr mǝɓane ɗàng, acemǝnana a twal yilǝmem nǝ gulo a pwari man yalung ngga. Ən pángŋǝ̀nà ɓwaɓana, sǝ ǝn ɓwarkina kǝ̀rkǝ́r!>>  
\v 22 Sǝ Dauda ear ama, <<Nzo mala murǝm nia ka! Tasǝ mwashat atà alaggana ɓǝ̀ eauwe ɓǝ̀ yi e.  
\v 23 Ɓakuli kǝ mbwe koyanale ka tangnakusǝi, ace ɓealɓoarna andǝ domǝsǝcau male; Yahweh ka, túrǒ a ɓabuam yalung, sǝ ǝn ɓinǝ loasǝ buam arǝ ɓwa mǝnana Yahweh ɗārǝi ka.  
\v 24 Kǝla mǝnana ǝn pè yilǝmo gulo yalung ngga, ɓǝ̀ yilǝmem kum gulo a mǝsǝ Yahweh, sǝ ɓǝ̀ amsǝam ɓǝn purî ɓá koya ulang tanni.>>  
\v 25 Pǝlǝa Sawul banggi Dauda ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh tsǝko bù, munem Dauda! Awu nǝ̀ pàkki agir mǝgulke, sǝ awu nǝ kum lidǝmba aɓa komǝyenani le ka!>> Nda Dauda bwal njar male o, sǝ Sawul nyar a ɓala male ka. 
\c 27  
\s1 Dauda ɓangŋa wari aban amǝ'Filisti 
\p  
\v 1 Pǝlǝa Dauda pakɗenyicau a ɓabumi ama, <<Akǝ fara ka, Sawul na nǝ̀ kiɗikiam ngga. Acemani ka, gìr mǝnana ɓoaribani ka, nda mǝnana ama mǝ nǝ ɓangŋa mǝ nǝ o a nzali mala amǝ'Filisti.\f + \fr 27:1 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa; \xt 1Sam 26:19\ft .\f* Anggo ka, Sawul nǝ̀ aulǝa arǝ altam aɓa bù-nzali mala Isǝrayila, sǝ mǝ nǝ api ɓabuì.>>  
\v 2 Nda Dauda lo sǝ wari andǝ aburana gbǝman-tongno-nong-mwashat (600) mǝnana à nda atè ka, aban Akish muna-ɓwabura mala Mawok,\f + \fr 27:2 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa; \xt 1Sam 2:10\ft .\f* murǝm Gat.  
\v 3 Pǝlǝa Dauda kya do a Gat, yì andǝ aburana male, koyan ngga andǝ amǝɓala male atè, sǝ Dauda gbal ka andǝ amāmí ɓari, Ahinowam ɓwama Jezǝril, andǝ Abigiyel ɓwama Kamel,\f + \fr 27:3 \ft Ɓalli aɓa; \xt 1Sam 25:42-44\ft  .\f* yì mā-lú mala Nabal.  
\v 4 Sǝ lang à banggi Sawul ama Dauda ɓangŋǝna umǝna a Gat ka, Sawul nyare alte ɗǝm ɗàng. 
\p  
\v 5 Pǝlǝa Dauda ne Akish ama, <<Ida, ɓǝ̀ ǝn kumǝna earmúrú a bano ka, ɓǝà pàm bân aɓa mwashat atà alá mǝnana a liro ka, ace mǝnana mǝ duk kam ngga. Ace mana sǝ mim guro mò ka mǝ nǝ do atò a là-murǝm?>>  
\v 6 Nda Akish pe wi Zikǝlag\f + \fr 27:6 \fq Zikǝlag \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa; \xt Jes 15:31; 19:5; Nehe 11:28\ft .\f* akǝ̀ pwari mǝno ka. Acemani ka, Zikǝlag na a bu amurǝma mala Yahuda bà yalung.  
\v 7 Anonggio mǝnana Dauda pa aɓa do male a nzali mala amǝ'Filisti ka, pǝlǝa mwashat nǝ azongŋo ine na. 
\p  
\v 8 Arǝ anonggio mǝno ka, Dauda andǝ aburana male wario sǝ à tǝlli amǝ'Geshur, andǝ amǝ'Girǝz, andǝ amǝ'Amalek. (Twal arǝ anza ɓara-ɓara aɓwapǝndǝa mǝnia ka à sauna nǝdo aɓa nzali mǝnia, tite a Shur aban ká ɗār a nzali Masar.)  
\v 9 A koya pwari Dauda wari nǝ munǝo arǝ ɓè bu-nzali ka, pà nǝ̀ ɗeki kǝ ɓwabura ko ɓwama nǝyilǝmu ɗàng, sǝ nǝ̀ gbǝwi anzur, andǝ andá, andǝ amǝdambǝriso, andǝ akalakadambi, sǝ agir-nggūrǝu. Pǝlǝa nǝ̀ nyar aban Akish.  
\v 10 Sǝ lang Akish nǝ̀ ɗiban ama, <<A ya ban sǝ wu wari ace tǝlliban yalung ngga?>> Dauda nǝ̀ ear ama, <<A ban njar-kunmur mala Yahuda,>> ko <<A njar-kunmur mala Jerameel,>> ko <<A njar-kunmur mala amǝ'Ken.>>  
\v 11 Dauda ɗeki kǝ ɓwabura ko ɓwama nǝyilǝmu mǝnana nǝ̀ yinǝi a Gat ka ɗàng, nǝ ɗenyicau ama, <<Cè à yi oasǝkimur sǝm, ama, <Ani sǝ Dauda pǎ.> >> Mǝnia ka nda gìr mǝnana Dauda pakkiyi pwari-pwari, lang ndaban do aɓa bù-nzali mala amǝ'Filisti ka.  
\v 12 Anggo sǝ Akish earnǝ Dauda, sǝ kǝ twali ama, <<Tsǝngŋǝ̀nà aɓwana male amǝ'Isǝrayila à ɓinǝnamǝsǝi; acemani ka, nǝ̀ duk mǝtúró mem tàtǝ́k.>> 
\c 28  
\s1 Sawul andǝ mǝɗikalú mala En-dor 
\p  
\v 1 Arǝ anonggio mǝno ka, amǝ'Filisti ram amǝ'lwa malea ace lwa-lwa arǝ Isǝrayila. Pǝlǝa Akish ne Dauda ama, <<Sǝlǝa ama we wunǝ aburana mô ka wun nǝ̀ o atàm atà amǝ'lwa.>>  
\v 2 Dauda pǝlǝa eari Akish ama, <<E, akàm sǝ awu nǝ sǝni nǝnggearǝò gìr mǝnana guro mò nǝ̀ gandǝ pè ka.>>Pǝlǝa Akish banggi Dauda ama, <<Acemani ka, mǝ nǝ tsǝo awu nǝ duk mǝ'yáltàm bà.>> 
\p  
\v 3 Adyan ngga, Samuyila angŋa-dǝmba pàngŋǝ̀nà-lú, sǝ amǝ Isǝrayila kat angŋa-dǝmba à ɓuanì sǝ à tsǝ̀ngŋǝ̀nì a Rama, yì là male.\f + \fr 28:3 \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt 1Sam 25:1\ft .\f* Sǝ Sawul angŋa-dǝmba pǝrna amǝ'ɗikalú andǝ amǝ'nggár, à purni ɓá nzalî.\f + \fr 28:3 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pǝris 19:31; 20:27; Nggur 18:10-11\ft .\f* 
\p  
\v 4 Amǝ'Filisti ramba sǝ à yi bwal kàttì a Shunem. Sǝ Sawul ram Isǝrayila kat, sǝ à bwal kàttì a Gilbowa.  
\v 5 Lang Sawul sǝn amǝ'lwa mala amǝ'Filisti ka, ɓangciu pàkki wi, sǝ gǝggǝli kǝ̀rkǝ́r.  
\v 6 Sǝ lang Sawul alta nê mala Yahweh ka, Yahweh pè wi kǝ eare ɗang, ko aɓa lòrǝo, ko nǝban Urim, ko nǝban amǝɓangnǝa.\f + \fr 28:6 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pur 28:30; Ɓal 27:21; 1Amur 3:5\ft .\f* 
\v 7 Pǝlǝa Sawul banggi amǝtúró male ama, <<Wu alamta ɓwama mǝnana mǝɗikalú na ka, ace mǝnana mǝ kya ɗibancau a baní ka.>> Pǝlǝa amǝtúró male eari wi ama, <<Sǝni, ɓè mǝɗikalú nakam a En-dor.>> 
\p  
\v 8 Anggo sǝ Sawul ɓosǝki rǝì, oasǝ aɓea agir-nggūrǝu ɗàng, sǝ wario, yì andǝ aburana ɓari atè. À yi bik ban ɓwame nǝ du. Sǝ Sawul bang ama, <<Ida, ɗikamban atà alú, sǝ wu tunǝâm ɓwa mǝnana mǝ nǝ banggo lullǝi ka, ɓǝ̀ lǝmdǝ rǝì.>>  
\v 9 Sǝ ɓwame banggi wi ama, <<Ɓafo a sǝlǝnace gìr mǝnana Sawul pàk ka, mǝnana pǝr amǝ'ɗikalú andǝ amǝ'nggár à purî là man ngga. Ace mana sǝ a kǝ tsǝkam gbǝli mǝnana nǝ̀ kánǝ yilǝmem a lú ka?>>  
\v 10 Sǝama Sawul kánbi wi ama, <<Mbak-kàngkàng Yahweh nakam ngga, kǝ ɓè patanni pà nǝ̀ yiu amuro ace gìr mǝnia ka ɗàng!>>  
\v 11 Pǝlǝa ɓwame ɗì ama, <<Yana mǝnana mǝ nǝ tunǝô wi ka?>> Sǝ ne ɓwame ama, <<Tunǝâm Samuyila.>>  
\v 12 Lang ɓwame sǝn Samuyila ka, sà'ɓua bang-bang. Sǝ ɓwame ne Sawul ama, <<Ace mana sǝ a swarkiam? A nda Sawul!>>  
\v 13 Murǝm pǝlǝa banggi wi ama, <<Ɓangciu ɓǝ̀kǝa pakko ɗàng. Mana ɗe a sǝna?>> Ɓwame ne Sawul ama, <<Ən sǝn ɓè lú aban puro nǝ ɓá nzali.>>  
\v 14 Sawul ɗi ama, <<Lang sǝ puro male pa?>> Eari wi ama, <<Jamgula na puro kǝ yiu ka! Mbuɓiki rǝì aɓa nggea-daura.\f + \fr 28:14 \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt 1Sam 15:27\ft .\f*>>Pǝlǝa Sawul sǝlǝ ama Samuyila na, pǝlǝa ɓunno sǝ ti múrí a nzali. 
\p  
\v 15 Pǝlǝa Samuyila banggi Sawul ama, <<Mana tsǝa sǝ a tanninǝ mim aban tunǝam ɓǝn yiu?>> Sawul ear ama, <<Mǝ nda aɓa nggikiban mǝkǝ̀rkǝ́rnì, acemǝnana amǝ'Filisti yinǝ lwa arǝàm, sǝ Ɓakuli ka pǝlǝnàm nzǝmi, sǝ yale kǝ pam eare ɗǝm ɗàng,\f + \fr 28:15 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt 1Sam 28:6\f* ko nǝban amǝɓangnǝa ko aɓa lòrǝo. Acemani ka, ǝn alte nǝma ɓǝà tunǝo wu yiu wu banggam gìr mǝnana mǝ nǝ pàk ka.>> 
\p  
\v 16 Sǝ Samuyila banggi Sawul ama, <<Ace mana sǝ awu nǝ ɗiem, mǝnana a sǝlǝna ama Yahweh pǝlǝno nzǝmi, sǝ dumǝna ɓiomǝbura ka?  
\v 17 Yahweh pàngŋǝ́nò kǝla mǝnana nam sǝ ǝn banggo ka; sanǝna domurǝm a ɓabuo sǝ pànî ɓio mǝ'murkala, yi Dauda.\f + \fr 28:17 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt 1Sam 15:28\ft .\f* 
\v 18 Acemǝnana a oki Yahweh ɗàng, sǝ a lumsǝ nggea bumlulla male mǝ'earke amur amǝ'Amalek raka,\f + \fr 28:18 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt 1Sam 15:1-9\ft .\f* nda Yahweh pàkkô gìr mǝnia yalung ngga.  
\v 19 Amur mani ka, Yahweh nǝ̀ tasǝ Isǝrayila sǝ we gbal a ɓabù amǝ'Filisti! Lí ka, we wunǝ amuna-burana mô, wun nǝ̀ pà atàm.\f + \fr 28:19 \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt 1Sam 31:2\ft .\f* Ɗǝm ngga Yahweh nǝ̀ tasǝ amǝ'lwa mala Isǝrayila a ɓabù amǝ'Filisti!>> 
\p  
\v 20 Kara Sawul kpa a nzali sárǝ́ pǝrapǝra, ɓangciu pakki wi kǝ̀rkǝ́r ace acau mala Samuyila. Rǝcandǝa malì rǝì kat acemǝnana lì kǝgir ɗàng, dù kat andǝ pwari kat.  
\v 21 Pǝlǝa ɓwame yiu aban Sawul, sǝ lang sǝn ɓiki gǝggǝlya mǝnana gǝggǝli ka, ɓwame banggi wi ama, <<Sǝni, mim guro mò ka ǝn kpanata cau mò. Ən twal yilǝmem a kún buam sǝ ǝn pak gìr mǝnana a banggam ngga.  
\v 22 Ado ka, we gbal ka, kwakikiro arǝàm, mim guro mò. Earam mǝ yinǝo nǝ girlina bǝti, ace mǝnana wu li, sǝ wu kum rǝcandǝa mala bwal njar ma'wun aban o ka.>>  
\v 23 Sawul ɓinǝe, sǝ bang ama, <<Pà mǝ nǝ lìli ɗang.>> Sǝama aguro male andǝ ɓwame ɓuakiarǝi, pǝlǝa kpata cau malea. Nda loapi nzali sǝ dumnǝdo amur gyangŋan-nongŋo ka.  
\v 24 Ɓwama man ngga ndanǝ muna ndá-lǝsǝa a ɓala, pǝlǝa bwali sǝ pwanmyali akaurǝa. Sǝ ɗàrǝ́ muku, karki dyar bǝredi, sǝ lurǝi burè pà arǝì ɗàng,  
\v 25 sǝ tsǝki Sawul andǝ aguro male aɓadǝmbia, sǝ à li. Nda à lo sǝ à o, a kǝ dù mǝno ka. 
\c 29  
\s1 Amǝ'Filisti ɓinǝ Dauda 
\p  
\v 1 Adyan ngga, amǝ'Filisti angŋa-dǝmba à ramna amǝ'lwa malea kat abanɓwáná a Afek,\f + \fr 29:1 \fq Afek \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt 1Sam 4:1; Jes 12:18\ft .\f* sǝ amǝ'Isǝrayila ka à tsǝk kàttì malea a nkanggari mgbeaɗe-mùr mǝnana nda a Jezǝril ka.  
\v 2 Lang \f + \fr 29:2 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Jes 13:3\ft .\f*amǝ'yálmúrû mala amǝ'Filisti gya aban kutio andǝ aburana malea mǝnana à gau rǝia arǝ agbǝman sǝ arǝ aá ka, Dauda andǝ aburana male gbal ka à gya aban kutio anzǝm murǝm Akish. 
\p  
\v 3 Amǝ'sàrǝ̀ban mala amǝ'Filisti ɗìban ama, <<Mana amǝ'Ibǝru man pakkiyi kani?>> Akish earia wia ama, <<Mǝnia ka nda Dauda, mǝtúró mala murǝm Sawul mala Isǝrayila. Nda kani nǝdo atàm kútínì pǝlǝa mwashat. Sǝ twal a pwari mana nying Sawul ba ado ka, ǝn kumi nǝ ɓekǝ ɓwarkio ɗàng.>> 
\p  
\v 4 Sǝama bum amǝ'sàrǝ̀ban mala amǝ'Filisti lul arǝ murǝm Akish, sǝ à banggi wi ama, <<Nyesǝ ɓwabura mǝna ka ɓǝ̀ o a ban mǝnana a pe wi ɓǝ̀ duk kàm ngga. Yì ka pà nǝ̀ ká atà sǝm a kún munǝo ɗàng, ace mǝnana ɓǝkǝa pǝlǝ ɓi'sǝm mǝbura a kún munǝo raka. Ya njar na ɗe ndakam nǝ̀ kumo, mǝnana ɓoaro-kutibanì, mala gilǝki-nre andǝ mǝtala-ɓala male ka, mǝnana ɓǝ̀ pà nǝ́ twal aɓamur aburana ma'sǝm raka?  
\v 5 Mǝnia ka nda Dauda mbo, mǝnana aɓwana tu'nggyal nǝ nggwam amurí ama, 
\q1 << <Sawul walna aá male, 
\q2 sǝ Dauda walna aá lum male ka?> >>\f + \fr 29:5 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 1Sam 18:7; 21:11\ft .\f* 
\p  
\v 6 Pǝlǝa Akish tunǝ Dauda sǝ ne wi ama, <<Mbak-kàngkàng Yahweh nakam ngga, a nda mǝ'ɓealɓoarna, sǝ puro mô andǝ kutio mô atàm aɓalǝ amǝ'lwa ka ndanǝ ɓoaro a mǝsǝàm. Ən kumô nǝ ɓekǝ mǝɓike ɗàng, twal a pwari mǝnana a yiu nǝi abanam ngga, bà yalung. Kat andǝ amani ka, amǝ'yálmúrû earnǝ we ɗàng.  
\v 7 Acemani ka, nyar ado, o aɓa rǝpwala, ace mǝnana wu kǝa zurǝi ɓabum amǝ'yálmúrû mala amǝ'Filisti raka.>> 
\p  
\v 8 Dauda banggi Akish ama, <<Mana ǝn pa? Mana a kumi arǝàm, mim guro mò, twal a pwari mǝnana ǝn yiu nǝi aɓa túró mô bà yalung, mǝnana nǝ̀ tsǝa sǝ pà mǝ nǝ ká munǝo arǝ aɓiu-mǝbura mala ɓwamǝgule mem murǝm raka?>>  
\v 9 Akish pa'eare ama, <<Ən sǝlǝna ama a nda ɓwa mǝ'mǝsǝcauì a mǝsǝàm kǝla mǝturonjar mala Ɓakuli! Sǝama amǝ'yálmúrû mala amǝ'Filisti bangŋǝna ama, <Dauda pà nǝ̀ ká atà sǝm a munǝo ɗàng.>  
\v 10 Adyan ngga, lo nǝ dǝmbari ɗiɗyal wunǝ amǝtúró mala mǝtala-ɓala mò mǝnana à yiu atò ka, sǝ lang banfana ka, wu bwal njar wu o.>> 
\p  
\v 11 Nda Dauda andǝ aburana male lo nǝ dǝmbari ɗiɗyal, sǝ à bwal njar aban o a nzali mala amǝ'Filisti ka, sǝ amǝ'Filisti ka, à eau aban ká Jezǝril. 
\c 30  
\s1 Dauda gandǝ amǝ'Amalek nǝ munǝo 
\p  
\v 1 Lang Dauda andǝ aburana male yina a \f + \fr 30:1 \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt 1Sam 27:6; 29:4,11\ft .\f*Zikǝlag a tàruia pwari ka, à yi sǝni ka amǝ'Amalek yina nǝ tǝlliban amur Negev andǝ Zikǝlag. À lina Zikǝlag nǝ munǝo, à pisǝni nǝ bǝsa,  
\v 2 sǝ à bwalkina amamǝna andǝ koyan mǝnana aɓalǝi ka bwalban-guro, amuna-mǝkeke andǝ aɓwana-mǝgule. À wal-lú kǝɓwa ateà ɗàng, sǝama à pwanǝnia, à umá nǝia. 
\p  
\v 3 Lang Dauda andǝ aburana male yiu a nggea-lê ka, à yi kumi ka à pisǝni. Amālia andǝ amuna-burana malea, andǝ amuna-mamǝna malea ka, à pwanǝnia à umǝna nǝia.  
\v 4 Pǝlǝa Dauda andǝ aburana mana atè ka, à ɓua kǝ̀rkǝ́r she lang rǝcandǝa malea malǝna ka.  
\v 5 Amālá Dauda kǝm ngga à umǝna nǝia, yià Ahinowam, ɓwama Jezǝril andǝ Abigiyel, ɓwama Kamel, mā-lú mala Nabal.  
\v 6 Ɓabum Dauda zurǝì kǝ̀rkǝ́r, acemǝnana aburane kǝ earce ama à nǝ̀ ɓukki nǝ atali; koya ɓwabura ka, bumikiɗiki kǝ̀rkǝ́r ace amuna-burana male andǝ amuna-mamǝna male. Sǝama Dauda ɓakɓabumi nǝban Yahweh Ɓakuli male. 
\p  
\v 7 Pǝlǝa Dauda banggi pǝris Abiyata, muna-ɓwabura mala Ahimale ama, <<Yinǝam nǝ efot.>> Nda Abiyata yinǝ efot aban Dauda ka.  
\v 8 Dauda ɗì Yahweh ama, <<Mǝ pǝrta amǝnia yì amǝ'tǝllìban ngga le? Mǝ nǝ kasǝmurià le?>> Yahweh eari wi ama, <<Pǝrtea, acemǝnana mbak-kàngkàng awu nǝ̀ kasǝmurià, sǝ mbak-kàngkàng awu nǝ̀ amsǝ aɓwana, sǝ awu nǝ ak agir mana à pwania kat ka.>> 
\p  
\v 9 Nda Dauda lo aban ká andǝ aburana gbǝman-tongno-nong-mwashat (600) mǝnana atè ka. Lang à yi bingŋǝna myalmúr Beso ka, aɓea aɓwana atea mǝnana à nda anzǝ́mò ka à ue abanì.  
\v 10 Dauda andǝ aburana gbǝman-ine (400) lidǝmba nǝ pyangnǝatau; acili aburana gbǝman-ɓari (200) ka, à ɓiki aulǝa à gandǝnǝ yálì myalmúr Beso ɗàng, nda à ueo abanì ka. 
\p  
\v 11 Pǝlǝa à kya kum ɓè ɓwa'Masar a patal, sǝ à yinǝi aban Dauda. À pè wi bǝredi shè, sǝ à pè wi mùr nu.  
\v 12 Ɗǝm ngga à pè wi agbatali kyak ɓari mala ɓǝla vwari andǝ adangŋanshi ɓǝla-anap mǝ'ime ɓari. Lang linia ka, yilǝmi nyar arǝì; ɓwabure ka pàngŋǝ̀nà anonggio tàrú, du andǝ pwari li kǝgìr ɗàng.  
\v 13 Dauda ɗì ama, <<Yana nda mǝtala-ɓala mò? Sǝ a pur nǝ kǝshe?>> Pǝlǝa ear ama, <<Mǝ nda lagga ɓwa'Masar, muna-ɓala mala ɓwa'Amalek. Mǝtala-ɓala mem o ɗekiam, acemǝnana ǝn nong rǝkwana anongŋo tàrú mǝnia à kùtí ka.  
\v 14 Sǝm wari a tǝlliban a njar-kunmur mala bù-nzali mala \f + \fr 30:14 \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt 2Sam 8:18; 15:18; 20:7; 23; 1Amur 1:38; 1Kpa 18:17\ft .\f*amǝ'Keret, aɓa nzong-nzali mala Yahuda, andǝ njar-kunmur mala nzong-nzali Kalip; sǝ sǝm pisǝ Zikǝlag nǝ bǝsa.>>  
\v 15 Dauda ɗì ama, <<Awu nǝ gandǝ kánǝ mim aban nggǝsan mala amǝ'tǝllìban man le?>> Pǝlǝa ear ama, <<Kánbam nǝ Ɓakuli ama a pà wunǝ wal-luem, ko awu nǝ túrǎm a ɓabù mǝtala-ɓala mem ɗàng, sǝ mǝ nǝ umnǝ we aban nggǝsan mala amǝ'tǝllìban man.>> 
\p  
\v 16 Nda warinǝ Dauda a banì ka, sǝ à kya kumia à mesǝna a koya ban a nzali. À ndaban li andǝ nu, andǝ pe ɓamúrià banɓoarnado ace nggea gǝna-lwa mǝnana à pwani aɓa nzali mala amǝ'Filisti, sǝ aɓa bù-nzali Yahuda ka.  
\v 17 Pǝlǝa Dauda soa arǝia nǝ munǝo, twal a ban-mbul'mbul aban ká pwarikpǝra mala ɓè pwari. Kǝɓwa ateà au ɗàng, shekǝ alaggana gbǝman-ine (400) mǝnana à ɓangŋa a nzǝm akalakadambi, à au ka.  
\v 18 Dauda ak agir mǝnana kat amǝ'Amalek pwania ka, andǝ amāmí ɓari.  
\v 19 Kǝgìr ɓwàr ɗàng, ko mǝkyauwe ko mǝgule. Ak amuna-burana, andǝ amuna-mamǝna, andǝ gǝna-lwa, andǝ koya gir mǝnana kat amǝ'tǝllìban mǝno pwania ka; Dauda nyesǝ agir kat.  
\v 20 Ɗǝm ngga Dauda pwan adomwan mala anzur andǝ ambul, andǝ mala andá, sǝ pǝria aban yiu a ɓadǝm acili agirkusǝu, sǝ bang ama, <<Mǝnia ka gǝna-lwa mala Dauda na!>> 
\p  
\v 21 Pǝlǝa Dauda nyar a ban aburana gbǝman-ɓari mǝnana aulǝa tsǝia à gandǝnǝ o atè raka, yì aɓwana mana à nyia a myalmúr Beso ka. À pur ace ká kúllí Dauda andǝ aɓwana mana atè ka. Lang Dauda bingŋǝna tù abania ka, pǝlǝa makkia-wia-kún.  
\v 22 Sǝama amǝ'ɓealɓikea andǝ amǝ'ɓealɓana aɓalǝ aburana mǝnana à o atà Dauda ka, à bang ama, <<Acemǝnana à o atà sǝm raka, pà sǝm nǝ̀ pè kǝɓwa ateà kǝgìr aɓa gǝna-lwa mǝnana sǝm nyesǝia ka ɗàng! Kǝ amālia andǝ amunia nda sǝm nǝ̀ pea wia ka, sǝ koyan ngga ɓǝ̀ bwal amale ɓǝà o.>> 
\p  
\v 23 Sǝama Dauda na ama, <<Wun amǝ'eambǝam, wu kǝa pak anggo nǝ gìr mǝnana Yahweh pa sǝm ngga ɗàng! Yahweh yál sǝm sǝ tasǝ amǝ'tǝllìban mǝnana à yiu arǝ sǝm ngga, a ɓabù sǝm.  
\v 24 Yana nǝ̀ kwakikiri arǝ wun amúr cau man? Kāmbe mala ɓwa mǝnana wari a munǝo ka, nǝ̀ duk mwashat andǝ mala ɓwa mǝnana ue a ban atwalo ka.>> 
\p  
\v 25 Twal a pwari mǝno bà yalung ngga, mǝnia ka duk nzongcau andǝ nggurcau aban amǝ'Isǝrayila.  
\v 26 Lang Dauda bingŋǝna Zikǝlag ka, tasǝ aɓa gǝna-lwa mǝnana pwan ngga, aban aɓwana-mǝgule mala Yahuda, mǝnana à nda ka agyajam male ka, nǝ cau ama, <<Ɓoro nia ka ace wun, aɓa gǝna-lwa mǝnana sǝm pwan arǝ aɓibura mala Yahweh ka!>>  
\v 27 Aɓoronì ka, à nda ace aɓwana mǝno arǝ alá mǝnia ka: ace amǝno yì aɓwana a Betel, andǝ Ramot Negev, andǝ Jattir ka;  
\v 28 ace aɓwana mǝno a Aruwa, andǝ Sifmot, andǝ Eshtemowa,  
\v 29 andǝ Rakal ka; ace aɓwana mǝno arǝ anggea-là mala amǝ'Jerameel andǝ amǝ'Ken ngga;  
\v 30 ace aɓwana mǝno a Horma, andǝ Bor Ashan, andǝ Atak,  
\v 31 andǝ Hebǝron ngga; sǝ ace aɓwana mǝno arǝ acili abân mǝnana kat Dauda andǝ aburana male ging kam ngga. 
\c 31  
\s1 Lú mala Sawul andǝ amuna-burana male 
\r (1 Acau Kpa 10:1-12) 
\p  
\v 1 Adyan ngga amǝ'Filisti naban munǝo arǝ amǝ'Isǝrayila; sǝ amǝ'lwa mala Isǝrayila ɓangŋa aɓadǝm amǝ'Filisti; à wal-lú amǝ'Isǝrayila amúr Nkono Gilbowa.  
\v 2 Amǝ'Filisti pǝrta Sawul andǝ amuna-burana male, à kya kasǝmurià, sǝ à wal-lú amuna-burana male, yià Jonatan, andǝ Abinadap, andǝ Malkishuwa.  
\v 3 Munǝo yi candǝ arǝ Sawul; amǝ'sǝlǝ túr mundi ta Sawul nǝ mundi, à tsǝki wi penye kǝ̀rkǝ́r. 
\p  
\v 4 Sawul ne mǝ-bwali-wi agirmunǝo male ama, <<Pusǝ nggeabyau mô sǝ wu zuɓiam nǝi, ɓǝ̀ ana raka, amǝ ɗwanyi kasǝ-ɓatau man nǝ̀ yia zuɓiam sǝ à nǝ̀ ɓangginǝ mim.>> Sǝama mǝ-bwali-wi agirmunǝo male ɓinǝe, acemǝnana ɓangciu pàkki wi kǝ̀rkǝ́r. Nda Sawul twal nggeabyau male sǝ kpa amurí ka.  
\v 5 Lang mǝ-bwali-wi agirmunǝo male sǝni Sawul wuna ka, kara yì gbal ka kpa amúr nggeabyau male sǝ wù atà Sawul.  
\v 6 Anggo sǝ Sawul andǝ amuna-burana male tàrú, andǝ mǝ-bwali-wi agirmunǝo male andǝ aburana male mǝnana atè kat ka, à wù akǝ pwari mǝ'mwashati. 
\p  
\v 7 Lang amǝ'Isǝrayila mǝnana à nda a buì njar-nza mala Ɓangŋaban Jezǝril andǝ amana a takuli mala Nggeasala Jodan sǝni ama, aburana mala amǝ'Isǝrayila ɓangŋǝna, sǝ Sawul andǝ amuna-burana male wukina ka, à ɓangŋa à nying alà malea; sǝ amǝ'Filisti yiu à yi do aɓalǝia. 
\p  
\v 8 Lang ban fana ka, amǝ'Filisti yiu ace pwan agirbura mala aɓwana mana à wuna ka, kara à yi kum lú Sawul andǝ alú amuna-burana male tàrú amúr Nkono Gilbowa.  
\v 9 À kasǝ ɓamur Sawul, sǝ à swár agirmunǝo male. À tasǝ amǝ'na-túrbân aɓa nzali mala amǝ'Filisti kat ɓǝà hamnǝ bǝsacê a ndàmǝgule mala ankúl malea, sǝ aban aɓwana malea.  
\v 10 À tsǝk agirmunǝo mala Sawul a ndàmǝgule mala \f + \fr 31:10 \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt Akas 16:23-24\ft .\f*Ashterot, sǝ à gyar luí arǝ sheran mala Bet Shan. 
\p  
\v 11 Lang aɓwana mǝnana nǝdo a Jabesh-Gilǝyat ok gìr mǝnana amǝ'Filisti pàkki Sawul ka,  
\v 12 kara akanggǝrang amǝ'lwa malea kat lo, sǝ à gya aɓa dù mǝno kat. À kya twal lú Sawul andǝ alú amuna-burana male mǝnana arǝ sheran mala Bet Shan ngga, sǝ à yiu a Jabesh, à kya pisǝia kàm.  
\v 13 À pwan amuia, sǝ à lumsǝia a tǝrta nggun zāmbo a Jabesh; sǝ à gilmùr anonggio tongno-nong-ɓari.